\id LUK - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG Luke 01 22/2/91 Macnaughtan
\h LUKU
\toc1 Lukumaęž‰ wape pieke Pi Seliapoe
\toc2 Luku
\toc3 Luku
\mt1 Lukumaęž‰ wape pieke Pi Seliapoe
\c 1
\s1 Lukumaęž‰ Diopilusi paęž‰taęž‰ tameiyaęž‰ tapaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Diopilusio. Mo niki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali wotumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone honkopu wotu hao wape lao wilimime.
\v 2 Mo ambaęž‰ hande pieke ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ kini pea handaa walemeke haliwekimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ la kimi tupaęž‰ kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ikaęž‰ wapemanu paęž‰taęž‰ laemekeme.
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ epeke some Diopilusio. IĚ±maęž‰ do hau manunaęž‰ kini paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ sembepela hone na u pitaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ nakaęž‰eki make tikitiki yao wape lao wiaasotaęž‰ epolo piaęž‰me laa loaęž‰me.
\v 4 IĚ±maęž‰ dupiki hautaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ waleke pimanu paeyaonaęž‰ teke handoelenaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me.
\s1 Dioni mondulu pieke ekinaęž‰ pi la haleekeeki
\p 
\v 5 Mo Diudia nane hande kini hali Hetodi hayeke pitaęž‰ yeni peao hayeke hali homeke Sekataiya make hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke Abaisia tapake halie. Ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Elisaęž‰bedi make mo hande yeni peao haemeke Etoni tapake wandaęž‰e.
\v 6 Mo wandaęž‰ hali yaapotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ tikitiki yao hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu paeyao opu haepekeme.
\v 7 Kutu pu haepekepate weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hatuku haepekeme. Pa ekipeke mo Elisaęž‰beditaęž‰ kenohali hayekeme. Kutupa ipilikitaęž‰ koke tooli haepekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Sekataiyataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapake haliwekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ hande yeni peao haemeke nate epeeke handaataęž‰
\v 9 mo yeni peao haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ pu haemeke tupaęž‰ Sekataiyamaęž‰ mo hande totopo piki ale mo olodanaęž‰ yankaenaęž‰yeke mimikime.
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande totopo piki ale yankeeke pitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane hataęž‰ yeni pitolo haenaęž‰ Sekataiyataęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba peekepate
\v 11 mo hande totopo piki ale oloda yanko hayeke popeke nanemaęž‰ kiki nane Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolo homeke aęž‰pa hayekeeki handeekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa Sekataiyamaęž‰ mo enisolo hando haotaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ make kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 13 Kutu piekepate mo enisolomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Sekataiyao. Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ yeni pieki opu haotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Elisaęž‰bedimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki mendiaenaęž‰ lelieke. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Dioni lapeke laataęž‰
\v 14 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo pelepatetaęž‰ mo weki mendiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wotu homilimikie. Kutupa
\v 15 mo weki daeya hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ hali tieke halieke laataęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo waini ikali make mo hoke ikali make na nelieke. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ inkikinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitinaęž‰ kone mo Holi Sipitidi tumbaalieke.
\v 16 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰hali wopu pa hatuku ikaęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pelimikie.
\v 17 Ipikitaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ tapaaliaęž‰ hali pua hataęž‰taęž‰ hande Elaidia tupaęž‰ honkopu hao wele pitolo hataęž‰ kutupa wekiwandiki ateke ameda titi make paa mea apaęž‰taotaęž‰ mo hande pi na opueleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ tikitiki piki hone winaęž‰yeke mea laęž‰kaęž‰laotaęž‰ mo hande Tekehalinaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰yeke ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mea tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ lelieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Sekataiyamaęž‰ mo enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ekie laa ekipa hone wionope laataęž‰ Ya wandaęž‰ diki telipinaęž‰ koke ya halopaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Mo hande enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Keipitelee laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hao halome. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do pi seliapo neke paęž‰taęž‰ lonoyeke IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰me.
\v 20 Do IĚ±maęž‰ mea epolo pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ nate epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ yaalo paęž‰laęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ na opueleme laataęž‰ Kotaęž‰ do alo pi na opiki handaa neketaęž‰ pi na leke kake aęž‰mba halipikie. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ do laęž‰ witolo pi otaęž‰ yaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ kake paa lombaa pi lelipikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Koto pi alo haepekepate mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane hataęž‰ Sekataiya epenaęž‰ handeteke haemekepate aĚ±iĚ± na epeeke handaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ wimikime.
\v 22 Kutupa Sekataiya opolu bao hamaęž‰ nane epeekepate mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ lapeke na yeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ handolo piaęž‰me la hone wimikime. Kutupa Sekataiyamaęž‰ pi lapeke na yaalo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki homeke wankeaaso hataęž‰ kikimaęž‰ kone waleekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Sekataiyamaęž‰ mo hande tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e poko hayeke natemanu paeyeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paa laęž‰kaęž‰la peekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa koto hoki nanetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Elisaęž‰bedimaęž‰ weki loke lombeeketaęž‰ sumbaęž‰ yunki hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da na minaęž‰paęž‰lake pa pitiekeme.
\v 25 Elisaęž‰bedimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ ame do tupaęž‰ tambaęž‰ maęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ yokaęž‰ mea baalaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesu mondulu pieke ekinaęž‰ pi la haleekeeki
\p 
\v 26 Kutupa Elisaęž‰bedimaęž‰ weki loke lomba haenaęž‰ sumbaęž‰ yunki mindiki aęž‰pa opeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hande enisolo Keipitele mo Kaęž‰lili nane hayeke da Naęž‰saęž‰tete da paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 27 Mo hande ambaęž‰ hayeke kini hali Deipidinaęž‰ tapake hali Diosepenaęž‰ da polo pieke wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulu penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Mo wandikinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Metie.
\v 28 Mo hande enisolomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Keiyae. Neketaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ otaęž‰ ambaęž‰ epeaalaęž‰ wandikie. Neke yaapo halaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Metimaęž‰ koto pi opiekepate Eki hau pulu polo ekinaęž‰ alaęž‰pe laa ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ mo pi teke wotu weiyekeme.
\p 
\v 30 Mo hande enisolomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Metio. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke laataęž‰
\v 31 Neketaęž‰ weki loke lombaataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ hali weki mendilipikimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Yesu lapeke.
\v 32 Kutupa ipiki daeyaataęž‰ hali tieke halieke. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ Otaęž‰ Manda Halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke lelimikie leekeme. Kutupa mo hande Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ kini hali Deipidinaęž‰ kilu tombuao hayekeeki ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ minaęž‰ lelieke.
\v 33 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ Dieikope tapake wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini hali hao hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kilu tombuao halo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na paelieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Koto leeketaęž‰ Metimaęž‰ mo enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotoeki pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipape. IĚ±taęž‰ halinaęž‰ da aĚ±iĚ± na polome leekeme.
\p 
\v 35 Mo hande enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo Holi Sipitidi neke paęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke. Kutupa make Otaęž‰ Manda Halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pitilieke. Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mondulu pele yako piki weki ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekee lelimikie.
\v 36 Nakaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰ Elisaęž‰bedi paęž‰taęž‰ hone wiaęž‰peke. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Weki kenohali wandaęž‰e lo halemepatetaęž‰ ame ipikitaęž‰ koke wandaęž‰sikimaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ weki loke lombeeke sumbaęž‰ yunki mindiki hataęž‰ ambaęž‰ opaęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰
\v 37 Hau paeyao kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 38 Koto leeke handaa Metimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokao halo wandikie. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ witele tupaęž‰ pinaęž‰e leekeme. Kutupa mo enisolotaęž‰ mo wandiki minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme.
\s1 Metimaęž‰ Elisaęž‰bedinaęž‰ da kimisu peekeeki
\p 
\v 39 Koto pitaęž‰ kone Metitaęž‰ tiao Diuda nane peiyene wieke paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya peekeme.
\v 40 Puaataęž‰ Sekataiyanaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua Elisaęž‰bedi paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi pua leekeme.
\v 41 Metimaęž‰ leeke pi Elisaęž‰bedimaęž‰ opitolo haenaęž‰ kone mo ipikaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitieke weki laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ piekeme. Kutupa Elisaęž‰bedimaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tumba pitinaęž‰ pi
\v 42 anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰weki polunaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke mea epeaalaęž‰me laataęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mondulu pele weki make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ epeaalaęž‰me.
\v 43 Yaka Tekehalinaęž‰ amaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± handolo epele ekitaęž‰ do hau tiekenaęž‰ pa ekipeke epelepe leekeme.
\v 44 Nakaęž‰ keiyae pi leeki opitolo hano kone ya weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ wekimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ tia liaeyaęž‰me.
\v 45 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Tekehalimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ opua otaęž‰ pilieke hone tula ale ekimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilipikie leekeme.
\s1 Metimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ homolo laęž‰laęž‰ emeli
\p 
\v 46 Koto leeketaęž‰ Metimaęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Yaka pukimaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ pi laasome.
\q1 
\v 47-48 IĚ± Mea Daęž‰taasaęž‰ Hali Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaaso wandaęž‰siki paęž‰taęž‰ kone hone ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yaka temokomaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 49 Hande Wele Pitaęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hau tiekemanu pealaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ame make wetepe make wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeaalaęž‰ wandaęž‰e lelimikie.
\b
\q1 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ bikitaęž‰ yakopiki bikie.
\q1 
\v 50 Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make koto wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ weki wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo halaęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 51 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ kiki tindipaotaęž‰ mo hakoko liteleme wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ dupumanaęž‰e laa amu piteleme alemanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea winaęž‰yeke laęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 52 Wele piteleme kini haliwekimanu make manda pitimikipate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki mea lopaęž‰niao mo hande pa haleme haliweki mea aęž‰meiyalaęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 53 Teaęž‰maęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ epeke napeke alemanu mea tumbaeyekepate pa mo hamoko wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ kiki hameke tapaeyekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 54 Nikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ apaęž‰mei paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pi manutaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ yao piekeme.
\q1 Ipikaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali Isulai paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tambaęž‰ mulu epeekeme.
\q1 
\v 55 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ hoki nane wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make hoto paeyao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo halueke hone wiekeme laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 56 Koto laa Metitaęž‰ Elisaęž‰bedi ameĚ±leĚ± sumbaęž‰ tepo haotaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipikaęž‰ da peekeme.
\s1 Bapitaisi peao halo pieke hali Dioni mendiekeeki
\p 
\v 57 Kutupa Elisaęž‰bedimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki mondulu pieke nate epeeke handaataęž‰ haliweki mendiekeme.
\v 58 Kutu pieke handaa ipikaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki otaęž‰ epeaeyekeeki handaataęž‰ peaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ make Elisaęž‰bedimaęž‰ make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.
\p 
\v 59 Pula homeke paeyeketaęž‰ mo weki sekemesaisi hau pealuekemaęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ biki kone Sekataiya loluekemaęž‰ pimikipate
\v 60 ipikaęž‰ inkikimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Dionie leekeme.
\v 61 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto biki lolo polomaęž‰patetaęž‰ nakaęž‰ tapake hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ koto biki leke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hayaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 62 Koto laa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kiki wankeaaso hataęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ta wekitaęž‰ eki biki lomanaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\v 63 Koto ekinaęž‰ Sekataiyamaęž‰ wape puluekemaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰ honke laa dupa wape piekeme. Do wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Dioni alome laa wape piekeme. Kutu pieke handaa mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime.
\v 64 Kutu pieketaęž‰ kutaa kone Sekataiyanaęž‰ kake lumbieketaęž‰ pi lapeke yalo hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laeyekeme.
\v 65 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme. Kutupa mo pieke ekimanu mo Diudia nane peiyene paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke da sunu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰manu laęž‰tia pomimikime.
\v 66 Mo pi opimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ opua hone witolo alotaęž‰ Do wekitaęž‰ ekipiki hali haliaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikime. Tekehalinaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki mo weki paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao pitiekeeki handolo hataęž‰ lemekeme.
\s1 Sekataiyanaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke ekimanu
\p 
\v 67 Mo wekinaęž‰ ateke Sekataiyamaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi tumba pitinaęž‰ hataęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰
\q1 
\v 68 Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ mulu aęž‰paataęž‰ iki tonkaalaęž‰ alemanu kaęž‰laęž‰pa walaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laamanaęž‰e.
\q1 
\v 69 Ipikaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali Deipidinaęž‰ tapake hali kone niki Mea Daęž‰taalo Paęž‰laęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ Hali ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyawalaęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 70 Ame do yaaso hataęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰mea halo haemeke yako piki haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiaenaęž‰yeke leekeme.
\q1 
\v 71 Niki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ liteleme haliwekimaęž‰ make leke tankemaęž‰ handeleme haliwekinaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ make niki bepolaapaęž‰naęž‰ niki mea tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 72 Kutupa nikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolueke laa Yaka yako piki pi laęž‰ ulueki make hone uluekee leekeme laataęž‰
\q1 
\v 73-74 Nikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hayeke hali Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi tieke laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ leeketaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi dupa laęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke
\q1 
\v 75 yaka e pokao hataęž‰ yako piki wandaęž‰hali make tikitiki yao haleme wandaęž‰hali make IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ bapi paeyao koto tupaęž‰ hamenaęž‰yeke ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliwekimaęž‰ iki bepolaapaęž‰naęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ mulueke laa pi laęž‰ wiekeme leekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 76 Koto ekinaęž‰ ya wekio. Neketaęž‰ Otaęž‰ Manda Halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰mea halo halaęž‰ hali haleme laa lelimikie.
\q1 Kutupa Tekehali wetepenaęž‰ epenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ potaęž‰ tikitiki yawaluekemaęž‰ ambaęž‰la pelipikie.
\q1 
\v 77 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lelipikie.
\q1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu paeyaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ iki mea daęž‰taalieke laa lelipikie.
\q1 
\v 78 Pa ekipeke. Nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ yopu hao hataęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo halaęž‰me. Da panake kaęž‰laęž‰polo hataęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kilieke.
\q1 
\v 79 Kutupataęž‰ mo homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ timbaęž‰ laęž‰pa paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tuĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ oli ya nane hataęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peanialieke. Nikitaęž‰ mo puki lopaęž‰niao pulaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ pomonoyeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ potaęž‰ walolo hataęž‰ do haumanu pilieke laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 80 Kutupa mo wekitaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ daeyaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ temoko make daeyatia pulu hataęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ handeteke hataęž‰ mo hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ hao hayekeme.
\c 2
\s1 Yesu mendiekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 1ęž‰18-25)
\p 
\v 1 Mo Sisa Okasitasimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kilu tombuao hayeke da wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ bikimanu wape pinaęž‰yeke mombaęž‰lapaęž‰peke laa leekeme.
\v 2 Koto titinaęž‰ biki mimiki pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo Sitia nane handeteke hayeke kapomani tieke halitaęž‰ Kuliniasi hayekeme.
\v 3 Koto leeke handaa wandaęž‰hali paeyao biki minaęž‰yeke ikaęž‰ da teke paęž‰taęž‰manu pemekeme.
\v 4 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Diosepetaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane hayeke da Naęž‰saęž‰tete da minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ mo Diudia nane hayeke da Betelehaęž‰maęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Koto dataęž‰ hande kini hali Deipidi mendieke dae. Diosepetaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ tapake hali hayekeeki yaalo koto da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Meti yaapo biki minaęž‰yeke pepekeme.
\v 6 Metitaęž‰ weki loke lomba pitinaęž‰ pepekepate mo Betelehaęž‰maęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pua hataęž‰ Meti weki hoki neekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ mupeke weki mendiataęž‰ hokulupeke dau manumaęž‰ ambulataęž‰ kimisu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hambo haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ peliaęž‰peke da diaęž‰yeke handa kao maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ ne halo haemeke uĚ±luĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua wiekeme.
\s1 Enisolotonu pitaęž‰ sipisipi handeteke haemeke haliweki yaapo
\p 
\v 8 Kutupa mandane sipisipi handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ koto dataęž‰ pa ambu hapeke nane ikaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ titi timba handeteke haemekepate
\v 9 Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolo homeke iki paęž‰taęž‰ opolo epeekeme. Kutupa mo Tekehali ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki dupaeyekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ wopu homemekepate
\v 10 mo enisolomaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pepee. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke pi seliapo loluekemaęž‰ epolome. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaalieke.
\v 11 Ame do timbataęž‰ oni hande Deipidinaęž‰ da teke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ daęž‰taalo paęž‰laęž‰ Tekehali ambaęž‰ mendiaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ Tekehali Ketisoe.
\v 12 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alomaęž‰ handolo pupe. Mo wekitaęž‰ daumaęž‰ ambula bao mo kao maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰ ne no haleme uĚ±luĚ±naęž‰ ulaęž‰maęž‰ handolo pupe laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Koto kone oli hepeni nane haemeke enisolo titi wopumaęž‰ mo hande enisolo homeke ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao aęž‰pa pambo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 
\v 14 Oli ya manda halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi lapaęž‰peke.
\q1 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ haleme haliwekinaęž‰ puki lopaalaęž‰me laa lemekeme.
\s1 Sipisipi handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu handolo pemekeeki
\p 
\v 15 Mo hande enisolo tapake pa laęž‰kaęž‰la ya nane pemeke hoki nane mo maęž‰naęž‰ handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ pi hotiolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ oni Betelehaęž‰maęž‰ da nane paęž‰laęž‰eki handomanaęž‰ bape lemekeme.
\v 16 Kotoeki laa aĚ±iĚ±ya puataęž‰ Meti Diosepe yaapo handaęž‰ wiataęž‰ uĚ±luĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hande weki wiekeeki handemekeme.
\v 17 Mo maęž‰naęž‰ handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mo weki handolo hataęž‰ hande enisolomaęž‰ mo wekimaęž‰ pulu piekeeki iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kiekeeki manutaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ la halemekeme.
\v 18 Kotaęž‰ koto haliwekimaęž‰ la halemeke ekimanu opimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime.
\v 19 Kutupa Metimaęž‰taęž‰ hande pi paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hone wopu u pitiekeme.
\v 20 Kutupataęž‰ mo hande maęž‰naęž‰ handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ pa laęž‰kaęž‰la pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ mo enisolomaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ kone hande hau paeyao handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki minaęž‰liaaso hataęž‰ pi laatia pemekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ biki halemekeeki
\p 
\v 21 Kutupa pula homeke paeyeketaęž‰ mo weki paęž‰taęž‰ sekemesaisi hau peaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki Yesu lemekeme. Mo weki aĚ±iĚ± na pitiki haenaęž‰ hande enisolomaęž‰ lahaleeke biki kone lemekeme.
\s1 Yesu tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pepekeeki
\p 
\v 22 Hande Mosesinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki manunaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo ankulaęž‰ epeaalo pieke nate epeeke handa mo wekitaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ Diosepe Meti yaapomaęž‰ ipiki hatuku Diutuseleme da pemekeme.
\v 23 Tekehalinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ dupa wape pea ulaęž‰me. Mupeke nanemaęž‰ mendilimi weki paeyao Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 24 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ make dupa wape paęž‰laęž‰me. Homupiki ba yaapo o melipu panake ba yaapo lia halaęž‰peke laa wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ba yaapo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lia haluekemaęž‰ pepekeme.
\s1 Simionimaęž‰ piekeeki
\p 
\v 25 Kutupa mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ koke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Simioni hayekeme. Koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homa hataęž‰ epeke hau pitolo hataęž‰ make mo Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ daęž‰taalo pieke nate epenaęž‰ handeteke hao hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi yaapo hayekeeki yolo hataęž‰
\v 26 mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na homeke pa halenaęž‰ kone mo Tekehalimaęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ hali ipilieke. Mo Ketiso kone handilipikie laa pi laęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 27 Kutupataęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ Simioni hatuku mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Kutupa mo hande pi wiekeeki puluekemaęž‰ Diosepe Meti yaapomaęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande weki Yesu hatuku pepekepate
\v 28 Simionimaęž‰ mo weki meataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 
\v 29 Tekehalio. Ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hande pi laęž‰ wili ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaaleme. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokaaso halinaęž‰ puki lopao pono lae.
\q1 
\v 30 Do ekinaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ hande wandaęž‰hali daęž‰taalo paęž‰laęž‰ hali ame yaka lekemaęž‰ handolome.
\q1 
\v 31 Do hautaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ handolo haenaęž‰ piteleme.
\q1 
\v 32 Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki haluekemaęž‰ make Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ biki tieke winaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ make pilieke laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Koto pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo Simionimaęž‰ mo weki paęž‰taęž‰ leeke pi opuaataęž‰ mo ateke inkiki yaapomaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomipikime.
\v 34 Simionimaęž‰ iki epeaotaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ inkiki Meti paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Isulai wandaęž‰hali wopu mea daęž‰taaluekemaęž‰ make hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do weki mea haenaęž‰ laa paęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 Ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tombo leke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi la la pitolo hataęž‰ make
\q1 
\v 35 ikaęž‰ hone aęž‰mbao witaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu peneme yao lelimikie. Kutupa kaęž‰ndaęž‰ pikieki maęž‰ndaęž‰ make kepete ne haake ekimaęž‰ leke nakaęž‰ puki awilieke laa leekeme.
\s1 Aęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ piekeeki
\p 
\v 36 Mo Aęž‰sea tapake hali Paęž‰nuele ipikaęž‰ waneke Aęž‰naęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰mea halo hayeke wandaęž‰ hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ haliki yaapotaęž‰ bapi watake hataęž‰ hao haliki homeekeme.
\v 37 Ipikitaęž‰ koke wandaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bapitaęž‰ 84 yeekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo tembolo da na minaęž‰paęž‰lake timba make natenaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao hataęž‰ ne pi wiaęž‰tiki pea yeni pu hatiki pu hayekeme.
\v 38 Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ koto pitaęž‰ kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ opolo puataęž‰ mo weki handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Diutuseleme wandaęž‰hali daęž‰taenaęž‰yeke handeteke haemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ opinaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ pi wotu leekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰ hau paeyao pu paeyaepeketaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane otaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ haepeke da Naęž‰saęž‰tete nane paa pepekeme.
\v 40 Kutupa mo wekitaęž‰ daeya hataęž‰ honkopu hao hataęž‰ make hone wopu u hayeketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeatiki piekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ weki hataęž‰ tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ piekeeki
\p 
\v 41 Bapi paeyaotaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ yaapotaęž‰ Diutuseleme nane mo Lombei Pupa Yapeeke nate miaęž‰tiki pieke handaa puaęž‰tiki pipikime.
\v 42 Yesutaęž‰ bapi kiki yaapo paeya ankenaęž‰ yaapo mieke natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo ne pambaęž‰laęž‰ nane ikaęž‰ pu haemeke tupaęž‰ kone pemekeme.
\v 43 Mo hande ne pamba paeyeketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da poluekemaęž‰ yeke pemekepate Yesutaęž‰ Diutuseleme da pa hapelia hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ do ekitaęž‰ hone na wipikime.
\v 44 Ipilikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo hande ikaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ pemeke wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± ambaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me hone wipikime. Kutupa nate homekenaęž‰ potaęž‰ ipu hao welealo nane ipilikaęž‰ tapake make ipilikaęž‰ yankekemanu pitimiki alenaęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa Yesu weimea pominolo hataęž‰ lotaęž‰ putia pomipikime.
\v 45 Kutu pipikipate Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ na handaęž‰ u haotaęž‰ Diutuseleme nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pulu hataęž‰ weiyaęž‰tiki pepekeme.
\v 46 Nate tepo peaotaęž‰ oli yeni pu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu pitiekeeki handaęž‰ wipikime. Yesutaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi walo hayeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi opitolo hataęž‰ make lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu pitolo pitimikime
\v 47 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ tandapiki hombo peatiki pieke ekinaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ pi opimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime.
\v 48 Ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu hando haotaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomipikime. Kutupa Yesunaęž‰ amaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya wekio. Ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ diki paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki hau pea pelepe. Neke weitolo hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰ dikanaęž‰maęž‰ pomomaęž‰ wotu homopaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 49 Yesumaęž‰ inkikinaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ekipeke ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± weiyaęž‰ mea pomua pelepepe. IĚ±taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pitoloeki ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hone na wipipaęž‰ laa loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 50 Koto leekepate ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peayeke pinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ hone na wipikime.
\p 
\v 51 Kutupataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ pi opua Naęž‰saęž‰tete nane mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ pi nate paeyao opua homu pea hayekeme. Kutu piekepate ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande lemeke pimanu paeyaotaęž‰ hone na yonkaęž‰lake hone pa wia hayekeme.
\v 52 Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ epeke honemaęž‰ tumbaęž‰tia daetolo hataęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make daeyekeme.
\c 3
\s1 Mo bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionimaęž‰ pi waleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 3ęž‰1-12, Maka 1ęž‰1-8, Dioni 1ęž‰19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Mo Lomaęž‰ Kapomani titinaęž‰ You hali Sisa Taibitiasi ipikaęž‰ bapi 15 peao handeteke hayeke da yu paeyaotaęž‰ pa handeteke hayekeme. Koto pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ leeke Kapomani you haliweki manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ handeteke hatia epenaęž‰ leeke kenke manutaęž‰ dupa handeteke haemekeme. Pontiasi Paileditaęž‰ Diudia kenke handeteke hayekeme. Hetoditaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili kenke handeteke hayekeme. Kutupa Hetodinaęž‰ hameke Pilipitaęž‰ Idulia make Dataęž‰kenaidisi koto kenke yaapo handeteke hayekeme. Laisaniasitaęž‰ Abilini kenke handeteke hayekeme.
\v 2 Koto pitaęž‰maęž‰ kone Aęž‰nasi Kaiyaęž‰pasi yaapotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ yeni peao haepeke you hali haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ hayeke hali Sekataiyanaęž‰ eiyeke Dioni paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi epeekeme.
\v 3 Kutu pieke handaataęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ mo Diodani ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ wieke yu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi latiki pomuolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halio. Iki paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ pimi haumanu make ikaęž‰ honemanu make laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ minaataęž‰ bapitaisi peano lapaęž‰peke. Koto haumanu otaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimi haumanu paeyaosiki paeyaaso hataęž‰ paa na niminaalieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Koto Dionimaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi la halo hayeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Aisaya ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ bukanaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa laęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hapupapeke alenaęž‰ hataęž‰ wi laa dupiki pi alaęž‰me.
\q1 Tekehalinaęž‰ potaęž‰ tikitiki yao wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\q1 Ipiki epeke tupaęž‰ epenaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ potaęž‰ wamo peao mea tikitiki yao epeapaęž‰peke.
\q1 
\v 5 Kutupataęž‰ mo hawete manutaęž‰ mea tumbapaęž‰peke.
\q1 Mo yu elimanu make mo potemanu make paeyao ao tumbaotaęž‰ mandake pinaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke.
\q1 Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ mo potaęž‰ hoihoi paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ mea epeaaso hataęž‰
\q1 mo hanaęž‰manu potaęž‰naęž‰ wekilaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ tikitiki yao epeapaęž‰peke.
\q1 
\v 6 Kutu pimikinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki handilimikie laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wotumaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ iki bapitaisi peaenaęž‰yeke paeyao epemekeme. Kutu pimiki handaa Dionimaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ ketomanue. Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ lolo paęž‰laęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wonduluekemaęž‰ hamenaęž‰ laa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ pindipa pelimiki pitaęž‰ epimaęž‰ kinki paęž‰laęž‰pe.
\v 8 Ikaęž‰ pimi hoke haumanu paeyao ambaęž‰ hoki waleme ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handenaęž‰ mo epeke kiliki aęž‰elaęž‰ timaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki pinaęž‰ epeke haumanu peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Nikaęž‰ meitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰e laa kutupiki pimanu na lapaęž‰peke laataęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opuaęž‰pe. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do toopimanu meaataęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ mondu sembaęž‰lalaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali anaęž‰naęž‰ wepia haenaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me alome.
\v 9 Hande hapulaęž‰ ti manunaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ pokuluekemaęž‰ mandaęž‰ meaowaęž‰me leekeme. Epeke kiliki na aęž‰eyaęž‰laęž‰ timanu paeyao siki poko lopaotaęž‰ ti talo halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paeyao siki mu yankilieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Do pimanu opua mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ eki hau peomonope lemekeme.
\v 11 Dionimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau yaapo wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo dau diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ natehali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰peke. Kutupa make ne napekeeki wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ne diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halimanu paęž‰taęž‰ telipea halaęž‰paęž‰pekee leekeme.
\v 12 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo mandane dakisi mani mu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ iki bapitaisi peaenaęž‰ ipiki aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ halio. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ eki hau piomonope laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 13 Koto lemeke Dionimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ dakisi mani mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao na miki mo Kapomaninaęž‰ Lo pimaęž‰ tombo ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ miaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 14 Mandane ami haliwekimaęž‰ make aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ekipiki haumanu peomonope lemekeme. Koto lemeke Dionimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mani pake muluekemaęž‰ paalaęž‰ tiao o yayapiki ekinaęž‰ pa hameke laęž‰ tiaasaęž‰eki otaęž‰ na peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa ikaęž‰ e pokaasemeke kitaęž‰laęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰me hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto haumanu paeyao handaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke ale tialu baeyeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone eleke eleke witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ do Dionitaęž‰ hande Ketiso pateyaęž‰laęž‰me laa hone wimikime.
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ bapitaisi peao halopate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ ipiliaęž‰ halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ honkopu wotu halaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ ipiki yaapo anaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ anke dake holaapeke make IĚ±taęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi pitaęž‰ ti uleke yaapomaęž‰ bapitaisi pealieke leekeme.
\v 17 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande widi kilikinaęž‰ ambuku napeke yaapo putupa alu puluekemaęž‰ panaęž‰pulu paęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰sataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ miniki halaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ widi kiliki epekeeki paeyaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ widi napeke u halaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la wilieke. Pate mo ambuku paeyaotaęž‰ tinaęž‰ panaęž‰pu yankilieke. Koto titaęž‰ na paeyeke pa to halieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Mo wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu hoki wala puki hone lekelenaęž‰yeke Dionimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapomanu otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ la halaęž‰tiki pominolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali sutiatia puaęž‰tiki pomiekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate Dionimaęž‰ mo kapomani hali tieke Hetodi paęž‰taęž‰ la halolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hoke haumanu peleme laa la haleekeme. Ekipeke. Hetodi ipikaęž‰ hamekenaęž‰ weteke Hetodiasi pa ipikaęž‰ handaęž‰mea make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ti teke wotu yokaęž‰tiki pomieke handa leekeme.
\v 20 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ Hetodi ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dioni dipula mea lopaeyeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ pieke hoke haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ koto ekimaęž‰ lu ankula yeekeme.
\s1 Dionimaęž‰ Yesu bapitaisi peayekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 3ęž‰13-17, Maka 1ęž‰9-11)
\p 
\v 21 Kutupa Dionimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao siki bapitaisi hau peaotaęž‰ wetepe nane Yesu make bapitaisi hau peayekeme. Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ yeni pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ oli hepeni lumba
\v 22 mo Holi Sipitiditaęž‰ ba melipumaęž‰ handekeeki holaęž‰paęž‰niao Yesunaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ aęž‰pa holopeekeme. Kutaa oli ya nanemaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make homekemaęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaka puki piki wekie. Yaka pukimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wotu homolome leekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ apaęž‰meinaęž‰ bikimanu
\r (Maęž‰tiu 1ęž‰1-17)
\p 
\v 23 Yesu ipikaęž‰ bapitaęž‰ hali tieke homeke paeyao kiki yaapo bapimanu tupaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e kinipea pokeekeme. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ eiyekee hone wimikime.
\q1 Diosepe ipikitaęž‰ Helinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 24 Helitaęž‰ Madadinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Madaditaęž‰ Lipaenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Lipaetaęž‰ Melaęž‰kinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Melaęž‰kitaęž‰ Diaęž‰nainaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Diaęž‰naitaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 25 Diosepetaęž‰ Mataatiasinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Mataatiasitaęž‰ Amosinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Amositaęž‰ Nahuminaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Nahumitaęž‰ Eselinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Eselitaęž‰ Nakainaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 26 Nakaitaęž‰ Maadinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Maaditaęž‰ Mataatiasinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Mataatiasitaęž‰ Semeninaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Semenitaęž‰ Diosekinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Diosekitaęž‰ Diodanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 27 Diodataęž‰ Dioananinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Dioananitaęž‰ Etesanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Etesataęž‰ Setubabelenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Setubabeletaęž‰ Sieletielinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Sieletielitaęž‰ Netinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 28 Netitaęž‰ Melekinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Melekitaęž‰ Aęž‰dinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Aditaęž‰ Kosaminaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Kosamitaęž‰ Elemadaminaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Elemadamitaęž‰ Aęž‰etaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 29 Aęž‰etaęž‰taęž‰ Diosuanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Diosuataęž‰ Aęž‰liesanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Aęž‰liesataęž‰ Diotamanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Diotamataęž‰ Madadinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Madaditaęž‰ Lipaenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 30 Lipaetaęž‰ Simioninaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Simionitaęž‰ Diudanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Diudataęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Diosepetaęž‰ Dionamenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Dionametaęž‰ Elaiaęž‰kiminaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 31 Elaiaęž‰kimitaęž‰ Meleanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Meleataęž‰ Menanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Menataęž‰ Madadanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Madadataęž‰ Neidaninaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Neidanitaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Deipiditaęž‰ Diesinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 32 Diesitaęž‰ Obedinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Obeditaęž‰ Boaęž‰sinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Boaęž‰sitaęž‰ Saęž‰limoninaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Saęž‰limonitaęž‰ Naęž‰sioninaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 33 Naęž‰sionitaęž‰ Aminaęž‰daęž‰benaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Aminaęž‰daęž‰betaęž‰ Aęž‰daęž‰mininaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Aęž‰daęž‰minitaęž‰ Aninaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Anitaęž‰ Hesotononaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Hesotonotaęž‰ Petesenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Petesetaęž‰ Diudanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 34 Diudataęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Dieikopetaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Titanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Titataęž‰ Neihonaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 35 Neihotaęž‰ Setakonaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Setakotaęž‰ Eteyunaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Eteyutaęž‰ Pelekenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Peleketaęž‰ Ebenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Ebetaęž‰ Silanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 36 Silataęž‰ Keinaninaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Keinanitaęž‰ Apaęž‰kaęž‰saęž‰dinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Apaęž‰kaęž‰saęž‰ditaęž‰ Siemenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Siemetaęž‰ Noanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Noataęž‰ Lamekenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 37 Lameketaęž‰ Madiuselanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Madiuselataęž‰ Inokanaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Inokataęž‰ Diaęž‰tedinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Diaęž‰teditaęž‰ Mahalalielinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Mahalalielitaęž‰ Kenaninaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 38 Kenanitaęž‰ Inosinaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Inositaęž‰ Sedenaęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Sedetaęž‰ Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke hayekeme.
\c 4
\s1 Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu la handeeke ekimanu
\r (Maęž‰tiu 4ęž‰1-11, Maka 1ęž‰12-13)
\p 
\v 1 Yesutaęž‰ mo Diodani ikali minaęž‰paęž‰lao paa epeeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ tumbiekeme. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ hapupapeke alenaęž‰ hatuku peekeme.
\v 2 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ nate hali tieke yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu aęž‰pa la handaęž‰tiki piekeme. Koto hali tieke yaapo nate manunaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ siki make otaęž‰ na neeke ekimaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Kutupa Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do toopi kone palaowa au lapeke leekeme.
\v 4 Yesumaęž‰ mo Sadaninaęž‰ pi litolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Halimaęž‰ palaowa homeke naa na hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutupa mo Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu oli manda hatuku pua mo kenkenaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰ ekimanu paeyao siki ti tekele pea ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ waleekeme.
\v 6 Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ mo Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰pate yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haloaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo kilu tombuao halaęž‰ ekimanu paeyao pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hamoko alemanu paeyao telipinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke halenaęž‰ neke kuluekemaęž‰
\v 7 neketaęž‰ ya biki laaluekemaęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ nakaęž‰eki yelieke leekeme.
\v 8 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Baibolomaęž‰ dupa laęž‰laęž‰me. Tekehali nakaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke yeni pu hataęž‰ e poko hapeke laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 9 Pa mo Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu mo Diutuseleme nane yeni pu haemeke da tiekenaęž‰ holu manda hatuku pua haenaęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do alenaęž‰ hao oni kenkenaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone lopaęž‰niae.
\v 10 Kutu pikinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo tonumaęž‰ neke epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ laa pi lelieke laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 11 Kutupa mo Baibolomaęž‰ paa laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ Koto enisolo tonumaęž‰ toopi ponekemaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke awaamaęž‰naęž‰yeke ikaęž‰ kiki manumaęž‰ neke miniliao handeteke halimikie laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 12 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi litolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Baibolo pimaęž‰taęž‰ do laęž‰laęž‰me. Tekehali nakaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ na la handaęž‰peke laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 13 Mo Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hoke la handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu ane mone eki paeyao siki peaataęž‰ pa hosiki minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ emanu kini piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 4ęž‰12-17, Maka 1ęž‰14-15)
\p 
\v 14 Mo Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ honkopumaęž‰ Yesu handeteke haenaęž‰ laa Yesu mo Kaęž‰lili nane paa peekeme. Kutupa koto da yu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki kende tupaęž‰ winaęž‰ lemekeme.
\v 15 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hotu haemeke damanu paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pea wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi walaęž‰tiki pomieke handaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki mea miniliatiki pimikime.
\s1 Naęž‰saęž‰tete da wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu kiaemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰53-58, Maka 6ęž‰1-6)
\p 
\v 16 Kutupa Yesu ipikaęž‰ daeyeke da Naęž‰saęž‰tete da paęž‰taęž‰ pua ipikaęž‰ pu hayeke tupaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoto pitu haemeke natenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Baibolo buka yataęž‰puluekemaęž‰ yeke tiao hayekeme.
\v 17 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ potopede hali Aisayamaęž‰ wape pu wieke buka Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme. Kotaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo buka lombaataęž‰ handaęž‰tiki pua pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa laeyekeeki handaęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ yataęž‰peekeme.
\q1 
\v 18 IĚ±maęž‰ natehali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰manu mo Pi Seliapomanu laanoyeke mo IĚ± mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Sipitidi IĚ± yaapo halaęž‰me.
\q1 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo dipula pilaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao halememe lono make mo leke holupiki wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke manumaęž‰ paa handilimikie laa lonoyeke tapaalaęž‰me.
\q1 Kutupa make mo ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ manumaęž‰ kone tekepaęž‰taęž‰ hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapawano make
\v 19 wandaęž‰hali wotu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate aęž‰pa halaęž‰me laa lono yeke IĚ± tapaalaęž‰me laa leekeeki yataęž‰peekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Yesumaęž‰ mo buka yataęž‰paataęž‰ ambaęž‰ bukamanu handeteke hayeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ paa halaęž‰ moneao pitiniaeyekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyao sikimaęž‰ Yesu handolo hataęž‰ yolaęž‰ pambemekeme.
\v 21 Kotaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do yataęž‰pa kuaęž‰ hande Baibolo pitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opitolo hamenaęž‰ kone otaęž‰ ame do kone yayaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 22 Ipikaęž‰ leeke pi manumaęž‰ tende pieke handaa iki paeyao siki leke opa penkiliputia pominolo hataęž‰ make haleke lomba mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikinaęž‰ do pi lemekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ eiyeke diaęž‰yekea laa ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone lotaęž‰ pu alu alu pimikime.
\p 
\v 23 Koto lemeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ loaęž‰me laa Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ lomaęž‰ lomaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me pi siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa lelimikie. Dokeda halio. Nakaęž‰ yenitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone mea epeapeke lelimikie. Kutupa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ make IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lelimikie. Hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ mo Kapeneami teke da nane hataęž‰ pi hande hau manutaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ opumaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ do nakaęž‰ otaęž‰ teke da paęž‰taęž‰ make kutupiki homeke haumanu kone pie laa lelimikie laataęž‰
\v 24 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰ potopede hali ipikaęž‰ teke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki hone wotu na wilimikie.
\v 25 Opuaęž‰pe. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo Elaidia hayeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ kineke wandaęž‰ sunutaęž‰ wotu aneke hapu mo Isulai da yu paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme. Koto natenaęž‰ bapi teponaęž‰ sumbaęž‰ yunki mindiki hataęž‰ lako otaęž‰ na aęž‰paataęž‰ da yu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki wotu aneke hapu epeekeme.
\v 26 Kutu piekepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Elaidiataęž‰ Isulai da yu paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na tapaeyekepate ipikitaęž‰ mo Saidoni da yu tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke teke da Saęž‰tepaęž‰di hayeke kineke wandaęž‰ homeke paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 27 Kutupa make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halo hayeke hali Elaisa hayeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ kindi yeni homo haemeke wandaęž‰hali wotu anekemaęž‰ mo Isulai da yu paęž‰taęž‰ haemekepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo na mea epeaeyekepate pa Sitia da yu paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke hali Neimanaęž‰ homeke mea epeaeyekeme leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto pi leekeeki opua ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mineke tieke wotu pankemekeme.
\v 29 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tiao Yesu minaa ikaęž‰ teke da minaęž‰paęž‰lao hama nane yolaa pemekeme. Mo ikaęž‰ teke dataęž‰ pote elinaęž‰ hayekeeki yaalo Yesu mo pote elinaęž‰ hatuku pua oni paeleke alenaęž‰ poneke wato lopaaluekemaęž‰ hatuku pemekeme.
\v 30 Kutu pimikipate Yesutaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kone pa paęž‰nkaęž‰pa peekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ hoke temoko baenaęž‰ leekeeki
\r (Maka 1ęž‰21-28)
\p 
\v 31 Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili da yu paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke teke da Kapeneami nane peekeme. Puaataęž‰ mo hoto pitu haemeke natenaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi waleekeme.
\v 32 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ waleekeeki opuaataęž‰ leke opo handake wimikime. Pa ekipeke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ halimaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ waleeke handaa pimikime.
\v 33 Mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitieke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekeme. Koto halimaęž‰ Yesu handaataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ wi aneke hapu la alotaęž‰
\v 34 Ae. Yesu Naęž‰saęž‰tete da halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± eki puluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pipaęž‰ laataęž‰ Neke epele ekitaęž‰ niki paeyao mea hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pipe. Neketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone witolome. Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tapaeyaęž‰ yako piki hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme.
\v 35 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo hoke temoko paęž‰taęž‰ tandapiki pi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ koto hali otaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao nakaęž‰ pi na leke aĚ±iĚ± hosiki yaęž‰laęž‰naęž‰ kone yopue leekeme. Koto pi leekeeki opua mo hoke temokomaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke taapunaęž‰ mo hali mea wato lopao yopusiki hama nane opolu baeyekepate mo halinaęž‰ loke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mea hoeyaeyekeme.
\v 36 Koto eki handaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao sikimaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomua ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi la alu alu pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ ekipiki pimanu alaęž‰pe laataęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ you hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ leke nono pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu paęž‰taęž‰ dupi dupi aleke handaa hama ipulimime lemekeme.
\v 37 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali manumaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekimanu handaataęž‰ da yu maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰manu kendetia pomimikime.
\s1 Wandaęž‰hali wopu Yesumaęž‰ epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰14-17, Maka 1ęž‰29-34)
\p 
\v 38 Yesu mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ Saimononaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Saimononaęž‰ meiyeke wandaęž‰taęž‰ titipu yeni tiekemaęž‰ homaęž‰pa wieke handaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ yeni hayeke tupaęž‰ la halemekeme.
\v 39 Kotaęž‰ ipiki pua mo wandaęž‰ homaęž‰pa wieke alenaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰liki nane pua tiao hataęž‰ mo hande titipu yeni hayeke ekimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laenaęž‰ tanda piki pi leekeme. Kutupiki pi leeke handaataęž‰ mo yenimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao tandelaęž‰pa yapeeke handaataęž‰ koto kone mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ mo tapakenaęž‰ ne wamo peayekeme.
\p 
\v 40 Nate ambaęž‰ pambeeke hoki nanetaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yankeke sunu ane mone yeni manumaęž‰ homaęž‰pa wiaęž‰tiki pimiki yeke handaa Yesu teke paęž‰taęž‰ mea epemeke handaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki iki manda wiaęž‰tiki pieke handaa paeyao mea epeatiki piekeme.
\v 41 Kutupataęž‰ mo hoke temoko manumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali aneke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pita eĚ± laęž‰tiki yopulu hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyekee lemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo hoke temoko manumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ laamaęž‰naęž‰ pi takaęž‰lake leekeme. Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ hone wimikipate ipikitaęž‰ hande Mesaya yeke handaa pimikime.
\s1 Hotu haemeke damanu paęž‰taęž‰ pi waleekeeki
\r (Maka 1ęž‰35-39)
\p 
\v 42 Da panake kelepolo haenaęž‰ Yesu ipikitaęž‰ koto teke da minaęž‰paęž‰lao wandaęž‰hali na halaęž‰ da yu maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honumake siki peekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu ipiki pu moneaekeeki weitia pomu hao ipiki hayeke paęž‰taęž‰ pua handaęž‰ witolotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ piki ekitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki na kiao penaęž‰ hone wia saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ taapemekeme.
\v 43 Koto hau pimikipate Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Pi Seliapo mandane teke da maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make walono yeke IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 44 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo da yu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰manu pomu lopaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pimanu walao hayekeme.
\c 5
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki miekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 4ęž‰18-22, Maka 1ęž‰16-20)
\p 
\v 1 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Kenesatete ikali leke wieke ikali teaęž‰ nane haenaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali aneke wopumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opuluekemaęž‰ yeke ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pendilatia pulu hataęž‰ titi ataęž‰taęž‰ pimikime.
\v 2 Yesumaęž‰ mo ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ kawaso yaapo wiekeeki handeekeme. Mo kawaso teke haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kawaso yaapo minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tenkinumanu tandepolo pitimikime.
\v 3 Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ Saimono ipikaęž‰ kawasonaęž‰ opaęž‰liao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Saimono paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kawaso mo ikali hounaęž‰ hosiki siki mo pate leke mea pue laa mo kawasonaęž‰ pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pimanu waleekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Koto hande pi walo paeyao wetepe nanetaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Saimono paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ kawaso mo ikali nokaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alenaęž‰ leke pendila moneae laataęž‰ Neke make nakaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni tonu ameĚ±leĚ± ikaęž‰ tenkinu paeyao do ikali paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰peli muemenaęž‰ lopape leekeme.
\v 5 Koto leeke handaa Saimonomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi litolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Do timba andusaęž‰naęž‰ niki paeyaomaęž‰ e tieke pokomaęž‰pate taęž‰peli otaęž‰ homeke siki aęž‰ndaęž‰ make na mumaęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ aleke handaataęž‰ mo tenkinu paeyao paa ikali paęž‰taęž‰ lopanoe leekeme.
\v 6 Kotoeki pimiki dinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰peli otaęž‰ wotu aneke hapu mimiki yeke handaataęž‰ mo hande tenkinu paeyaotaęž‰ tumbulu baasotaęž‰ tunkuluekemaęž‰ taapeekeme.
\v 7 Kutu pieke handaa mo kawaso maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pitimiki haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni tonumaęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ mulu epenaęž‰ yeke kiki wanke pitolo hataęž‰ ipupaęž‰ laa lemekeme. Iki aęž‰paataęž‰ mo taęž‰pelimanu paeyao siki mo kawaso yaaponaęž‰ mea wimiki ekimaęž‰ mo hande kawaso yaapotaęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰ honki loluekemaęž‰ taapepekeme.
\v 8 Kutu piekeeki handaataęž‰ Saimono Pidamaęž‰ Yesu teke paęž‰taęž‰ tumiki yotuao alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. IĚ±taęž‰ hoke hau polo somemaęž‰ IĚ± kiao pue leekeme.
\v 9 Saimono ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke haliweki ikaęž‰ tenkinu paeyao siki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰peli wotu anekemaęž‰ mu wimikieki handaataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime.
\v 10 Saimono ipikaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pieke hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ Sepedinaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo Diaęž‰mesi Dioni yaapomaęž‰ make penkilipaęž‰tia pomipikime. Yesumaęž‰ Saimono paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke laataęž‰ Ekipeke ame do kini peaataęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pa haliweki mealipikie leekeme.
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo kawaso yolaęž‰ mea mo ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ mea wiataęž‰ ikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao minaęž‰paęž‰lao Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane teli mea pemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰1-4, Maka 1ęž‰40-45)
\p 
\v 12 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo kindi yenimaęž‰ loke paeyao tumbieke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayeke daoni maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme. Koto halimaęž‰ Yesu handaataęž‰ ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa oni kenkenaęž‰ lopolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± mea epeapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 13 Koto leeke pi opua Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipao mo halinaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ wataaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ya hone paęž‰laęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ loke epenaęž‰e. Koto leeke handaataęž‰ koto kone mo kindi yeni hayekeeki tandelaęž‰pa peekeme.
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ pi honkopu hao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do pitolo ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na leketaęž‰ pa mo yeni peao halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la nakaęž‰ yeni otaęž‰ paelaęž‰pe laa handenaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke. Kutaataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenitaęž‰ otaęž‰ paelaęž‰me hone winaęž‰ mo hande Mosesimaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke tupaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lia halaęž‰laęž‰ ale lia halaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 15 Koto pi leeke patetaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekimanu da yu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰tiki pomimikime. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali aneke hapumaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ leeke pimanu opua make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ yenimanu mea epeaenaęž‰ yeke epemekeme.
\v 16 Kutu pimikipate Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali na hayeke alenaęž‰ pua Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ puaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\s1 Kiki anke lupa wiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 9ęž‰1-8, Maka 2ęž‰1-12)
\p 
\v 17 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mandane Paęž‰tisi haliweki make mo Lo Pimanu walaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki make pitimikime. Koto haliwekitaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili kenke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ daonimanu make Diudia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ daonimanu make mo Diutuseleme teke da paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰pa pitimikime. Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo yeni homemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyao Yesumaęž‰ mea epeaenaęž‰ mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰naęž‰ weletaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aneke hapu hayekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kiki anke lupa wiki some maęž‰ndaęž‰ tilinaęž‰ mea tia aęž‰paataęž‰ ipiki mo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ tia pua Yesunaęž‰ leke tonkonaęž‰ pua tu uluekemaęž‰ taapemekeme.
\v 19 Kutu pimikipate polo pimiki potaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wotu aneke hapumaęž‰ tumbieke handaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ tia puaęž‰peke potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ hande da holunaęž‰ mea opaęž‰liao kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ mea wiao ipikaęž‰ loketaęž‰ tilinaęž‰ wia mo wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ Yesu hayeke alenaęž‰ uniaemekeme.
\v 20 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo haliwekinaęž‰ hone tulaemekeeki handaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo kiki anke lupa wiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kame. Nakaęž‰ hande pi hoke hau manutaęž‰ pa paeyaasaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 21 Koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ mo Lo Pimanu walaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki make mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi pi alo alotaęž‰ Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki hoeyaaso pimanu alaęž‰ halitaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hoke hau manutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homeke anaęž‰naęž‰ paeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰taa lemekeme.
\v 22 Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ hone wimiki ekitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hone wia iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ do honemanu witelemepe laa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰
\v 23 Do pi yaaponaęž‰ yapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handoeki kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Nakaęž‰ hokeeki paęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ pa paeyaasaęž‰me laa laęž‰laęž‰eki yapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe o Tiao pue aloeki yapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe laa
\v 24 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ hoke haumanu paeyaapeke wele wia halo ekitaęž‰ ame peneme yanomaęž‰ handaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo hande kiki anke lupa wiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Ame tiao. Nakaęž‰ tilitaęž‰ da pa mea tia pue leekeme.
\v 25 Koto tomonaęž‰ kone mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mo hande hali tiao mo ipiki pelieke tili mea tia ipikaęž‰ da nane pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea miniliatia peekeme.
\v 26 Kutupa koto piekeeki handaataęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰hali manutaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomua ikitaęž‰ pututumaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea miniliaaso alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ na handeke epeke haumanu wotu handomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Lipae miekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 9ęž‰9-13, Maka 2ęž‰13-17)
\p 
\v 27 Wetepenaęž‰ Yesu hama opolu bao pulu hataęž‰ dakisi mani mu hayeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki Lipae handeekeme. Koto halitaęž‰ mo dakisi mani mu hayeke opisi paęž‰taęž‰ pitiekeme. Yesumaęž‰ Lipae paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea epoe leekeme.
\v 28 Koto ekinaęž‰ Lipae tiao ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao siki kiao Yesu teliaęž‰ mea peekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Kutupa Lipaemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ aneke ne maęž‰ndaęž‰ pambaeyekeme. Lipaemaęž‰ wi leeke epemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo dakisi mani mu haemeke haliweki aneke hapu make pa mandane haliweki make ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pitimikime.
\v 30 Kutupa mandane Paęž‰tisi haliweki manumaęž‰ make iki ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰taemeke mandane Lo Pi walaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ piki pimanu lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo dakisi mani mu haleme haliweki make mo hoke haumaęž‰ haĚ±iĚ± pieke handaa minaęž‰paęž‰laemeke wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ ne ikalimanu ekipeke nalemepe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 31 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ yeni na homemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ dokeda haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ na pu halemepate otaęž‰ yeni homo haleme wandaęž‰hali homeke dokeda hali paęž‰taęž‰ pu halememe.
\v 32 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la winaęž‰yeke wi loluekemaęž‰ na epoaęž‰pate pa hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali wi loluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Nee pi wiaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 9ęž‰14-17, Maka 2ęž‰18-22)
\p 
\v 33 Kotaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lemekeme. Dioninaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki make mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekinaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki make nate paeyao nee pi u moneaaso hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peaęž‰tiki pu halemepate pa nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikali ne manutaęž‰ pa no halememe lemekeme.
\v 34 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰ panake mea pitaęž‰ ne pambolo hataęž‰ mo wi leeke epemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± pa mandake pitu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ne na neke pi wipe leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ opilimikipe. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me.
\v 35 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo wandaęž‰ panake minaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hatuku puaęž‰peke nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nee pi wiaęž‰tiki pu halimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 36 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa leekeme. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ sinkipiki ambaęž‰ sedi maęž‰ndaęž‰ epeaaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ panake sedi tunkulu mea mo ambaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ na tombilieke. Koto hau piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ panake sedi tunkulieke make mo panake akaęž‰taęž‰ tunkulu mieke mo ambisanake sedi mandakenaęž‰ apaęž‰tao tombiliaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mandake na pilieke.
\v 37 Koto tupaęž‰ kone hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ambisanake maęž‰naęž‰ yonkelekemaęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ipi kanake paęž‰taęž‰ panake waini ikali na holo pambilieke. Koto hau piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo panake waini ikalimaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ yonkelekemaęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ambaęž‰ ipi kanaketaęž‰ sinkipa hoelo baalieke leekeme. Kutupa mo maęž‰naęž‰ yonkeleke make hoeyaalieke leekeme.
\v 38 Diaęž‰me. Mo panake waini ikalitaęž‰ mo panake maęž‰naęž‰ yonkelekemaęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ipi kanakenaęž‰ holo pambilieke.
\v 39 Kutupa mo ambaęž‰ waini ikali ambaęž‰laęž‰ nalaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo panake waini ikali napeketaęž‰ kialieke. Ekipeke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ waini ikalitaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lelieke leekeme.
\c 6
\s1 Hoto pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰1-8, Maka 2ęž‰23-28)
\p 
\v 1 Yesutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoto pilaęž‰ nate homekenaęž‰ mo konimaęž‰ handeke ale widi emanu paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo widi kilikimanu hondaęž‰ mea ikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minaęž‰ bepia kilikimanu homeke nemekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa mo mandane Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Lo Pi manumaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ na peaęž‰paęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipeke pitolo pimipe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Deipidi ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke haliweki hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Deipidimaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ na yataęž‰pemepe.
\v 4 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba puaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halemeke palaowa pua mea neekeme. Kutupa ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke haliweki make mea haleekeme. Kutu piekepate mo wape pea ulaęž‰ Lo Pi manumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do palaowataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na napaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate otaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke da handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ homeke napaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰
\v 5 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi lo paeyaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hoto pilaęž‰ natetaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ kiki hoke hali epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰9-14, Maka 3ęž‰1-6)
\p 
\v 6 Mo hoto pilaęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekinaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi waleekeme. Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ mo popeke nane kiki hapueke endiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekeme.
\v 7 Mo wape pea ulaęž‰ Lo Pi walo haemeke haliweki make Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ make Do nikaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea epeaaliaęž‰pe laa handaęž‰hake wimikime. Yesumaęž‰ pi yambaęž‰leaęž‰me loluekemaęž‰ yeke pimikime.
\v 8 Kutu pimikipate Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ mo haliwekinaęž‰ hone wimikieki ambaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ mo kiki hapueke endiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiao. Do wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popeleke nane epoe leekeme. Mo halitaęž‰ tiao mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popeleke nane tiao halo yapeekeme.
\v 9 Kutu pieketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolome. Mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ eki peaęž‰paęž‰peke la laęž‰laęž‰pe. Pa tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ o hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰pe. Mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ halaęž‰eki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰pe o hoeyaaluekemaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 10 Kotoeki laataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leke takaęž‰lakemaęž‰ mo haliweki handaęž‰ mone mone pitolo hataęž‰ mo some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kiki tindipae leekeme. Koto leeke mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipaeyeketaęž‰ paa epeekeme.
\v 11 Kutu pieke handaa mo Lo Pi walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mineke pankolo hataęž‰ titipu tieke aęž‰meiyeke handaa Yesu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki pumanaęž‰pe laa aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ 12 Aposolo haliweki miekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 10ęž‰1-4, Maka 3ęž‰13-19)
\p 
\v 12 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰yeke pote maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰meiya peekeme. Koto timba andusaęž‰naęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ yeni paa pitolo ombu pitinaęž‰taęž‰ da paa kelepeekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa nate teeketaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliweki paeyao wi leekeme. Koto haliweki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ kone 12 haliweki maĚ±leke litolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ yaka Aposolo haliweki hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 14 Mo haliwekinaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ Saimono Yesumaęž‰ leeke biki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Pida ipikaęž‰ hameke Aęž‰ndutu make Diaęž‰mesi Dioni Pilipi Badolomiu make
\v 15 Maęž‰tiu make Tomasi make Aęž‰lopiaęž‰sinaęž‰ eiyeke Diaęž‰mesi make Saimono ipikaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Seloti make
\v 16 Diaęž‰mesinaęž‰ eiyeke Diudasi make Isekatiotinaęž‰ eiyeke Diudasi ipikitaęž‰ hande Yesu baęž‰saęž‰ pulu yapolo pieke some hayekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wamo piekeeki pitaęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo
\r (Maęž‰tiu 4ęž‰23-25)
\p 
\v 17 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo Aposolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo hande potenaęž‰ hao holaęž‰paęž‰niao ikitaęž‰ epeke hawete epeekenaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliweki paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ tiao hayekeme.
\v 18 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ Diudia da yu paeyaonaęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali make Diutuseleme daoni wandaęž‰hali make epemekeme. Kutupa mo dawala ikali teaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke teke da yaapo Taiya pitaęž‰ Saidoni da yu paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali make epemekeme. Ikitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ waleeke pi opuluekemaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ yeni taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ hayekeeki mea epeaenaęž‰yeke make aęž‰pa mombelemekeme. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke temokomaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mea peatiki pimiki wandaęž‰hali make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epemeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ mea epeaeyekeme.
\v 19 Mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yenimanu mea epeapeke honkopu tieke Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hao yapeeke handaa mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki wataluekemaęž‰ taapemekeme.
\s1 Taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰pekeeki make eĚ± lapekeeki yaapo
\r (Maęž‰tiu 5ęž‰1-12)
\p 
\v 20 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliweki handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Natehali wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ekie.
\v 21 Ame teaęž‰maęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰hali iki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe. Ikitaęž‰ weleke tieke telieke. Ame eĚ± aleme wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe. Ikitaęž‰ kitelimikie.
\v 22 Ikitaęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke tolu halemeke handaa mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homao make tanda ku make ikaęž‰ biki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ hoke baęž‰saęž‰ pitolo yayapiki pimanu saęž‰mbaęž‰lao pitolo haenaęž‰ kone
\v 23 pa pinaęž‰maęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pa epeke puki haaso hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo make pita ponkaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke ikaęž‰ mulu peleme yenki tieketaęž‰ oli hepeni nane wiawalaęž‰me. Ambaęž‰ hande haemeke potopede haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make ikaęž‰ apaęž‰meimaęž‰ pimieki kone pitolo pitelememe.
\v 24 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate aiyo ame do hamoko haaseme wandaęž‰halio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke ipulaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hao paęž‰limi ekitaęž‰ ame homeke minelememe.
\v 25 Aęž‰pei. Ame do weleke tumbao halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halio. Kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke ipulaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homilimikie. Aęž‰pei. Ame kitaleme wandaęž‰halio. Kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke ipulaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ eĚ± tieke alo hataęž‰ eĚ± pankeke lopenaęž‰ lelimikie.
\p 
\v 26 Aęž‰pei. Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ haunaęž‰ pi laemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke ipulaęž‰me. Ekipeke ambaęž‰ kiake koto wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ apaęž‰meimaęž‰ mo makeaaso potopede haliweki tonu paęž‰taęž‰ lo haemeke tupaęž‰ kone alo alememe leekeme.
\s1 Aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 5ęž‰38-48, 7ęž‰12)
\p 
\v 27 Pate ame ya pi opiteleme wandaęž‰hali iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ dupa alome. Ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa iki paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pu haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ epeke hau homeke pu hapaęž‰peke.
\v 28 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ keke pi aleme tapake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pukipiki pi homeke lapaęž‰peke. Kutaa make iki hoeyaaseme tapake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ yeni peawapaęž‰peke.
\v 29 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ pakenaęž‰ liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mandane pakenaęž‰ make linaęž‰ lapeke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ kosaęž‰ akaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ sedi make minaęž‰ lapeke.
\v 30 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ kie laa honke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰peke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Yaka ale paa kie laa paa na miaęž‰peke.
\v 31 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pinaęž‰e hone u haleme tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make mandake hau pu hapaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 32 Iki pukimaęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ homeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa ekipeke ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ milimipe. Hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo halememe.
\v 33 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke haumanu piteleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ homeke paa epeke haumanu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipeke kilieke yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Mo hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali make koto hau koto tupaęž‰ kone pu halememe.
\v 34 Kutupa make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ paa kilimikie hone witolo hataęž‰ tondiki halemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipa milimikipe. Mo hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ haleme tupaęž‰ paa muluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke hau pu haleme yankeke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ kone halo halememe.
\v 35 Diaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homa iki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau homeke pu hapaęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ tondiki halemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ paa muluekemaęž‰ hone na u hapaęž‰peke. Kutu pu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ yenki aneke hapu meataęž‰ oli Kodaęž‰ Manda Halaęž‰ Tiekenaęž‰ eiyeke titi halimikie. Ekipeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ epeke haumanu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰e pi na lo haleme wandaęž‰hali make mo hoke haumanu wotu pu haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make epeke hau pu halaęž‰me.
\v 36 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ mu halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ mu hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 7ęž‰1-5)
\p 
\v 37 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu kiaapaęž‰naęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu na halaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ na teli pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make iki na teli pilieke. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pelemeeki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa paeyaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make ikaęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ pa paeyaalieke.
\v 38 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pa hameke kone halemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki epetolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ anekehapu tumbao iki paęž‰taęž‰ wendiao kilieke. Ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mandaęž‰ meao haleleme tupaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ mandaęž‰ meao kone kilieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa leekeme. Leke holupiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ leke holupiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hatuku puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipiliki telipinaęž‰ ikali hankaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua lopilipikie.
\v 40 Sukulu pitaęž‰laęž‰ weki o wandikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ disa some lombei peao na halaęž‰me. Pate mo wekiwandikimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ sukulu pitelemeeki paeyaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo disamaęž‰ handilimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 41 Ekipeke nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ dokolo siki hone wopu witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ lekenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ ti takaęž‰laęž‰pake tieketaęž‰ hone na u halepe.
\v 42 Mo ti takaęž‰laęž‰pake tieke nakaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ pa winaęž‰ alo hataęž‰taęž‰ ekipa nakaęž‰ kame paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Nakaęž‰ leke ulaęž‰ dokolo siki meanoe lelipikipe. Aa. Makeaasaęž‰ hau pu halaęž‰ someo. Titinaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ ti takaęž‰laęž‰pake kiake ambaęž‰laęž‰ mea baekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ dokolo siki meawaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ epeke handilipikie leekeme.
\s1 Tinaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kilikinaęž‰ hau yaapo
\r (Maęž‰tiu 7ęž‰16-20, 12ęž‰33-35)
\p 
\v 43 Ipi saosao liki ti maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hoke kiliki na aęž‰ilieke. Kutupa make hakaęž‰teke ti maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ epeke kiliki na aęž‰ilieke.
\v 44 Ti paeyaotaęž‰ dupiki ti yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiliki aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ peneme yao la kilieke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nose kiliki taluekemaęž‰taęž‰ sutekenaęž‰ na talimikie. Kutupa mo waini kiliki taluekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo taolaęž‰ punaęž‰ na talipikie leekeme.
\v 45 Epeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ epeke hau manutaęž‰ hama nane koto epeke haumanu homeke peneme yao walieke. Hoke halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ hoke hau manutaęž‰ hama nane koto hoke haumanu homeke peneme yao walieke. Ipikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰ pi manunaęž‰ teke tieketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Hali yaapomaęž‰ da yaapo aęž‰eyalu pipikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 7ęž‰24-27)
\p 
\v 46 Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalio. Tekehalio alo hataęž‰ pu halemepe.
\v 47 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ IĚ± teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa yaka pi opua pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ dupiki halie laa mandaęž‰ meanoe.
\v 48 Ipikitaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da aęž‰eluekemaęž‰taęž‰ yu ambaęž‰la aowaęž‰tia pua toopi handaęž‰ witolotaęž‰ pinkimanu koto toopi manda nokopo halaęž‰ hali tupaęž‰e. Ikali tieke ta ipulu hataęž‰ hande da aęž‰pa wataa hande hande piekepate hande dataęž‰ na lombeekeme. Pa ekipeke mo dataęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ aęž‰eyeke handaa piekeme.
\v 49 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ yaka pi opuaataęž‰ na pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo kenke toopi na handaęž‰ wiki hataęž‰ kone pa hameke pinki nokopo halaęž‰ hali tupaęž‰e. Mo hande ikali tieke ta aęž‰pa mo hande da wataa hande hande pieke paęž‰taęž‰ kone lombeekeme. Hande da lombolo hataęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ lombeekeme leekeme.
\c 7
\s1 Ami you halinaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ some epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰5-13)
\p 
\v 1 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ koto pimanu lo paeyaotaęž‰ mo Kapeneami daoni nane peekeme.
\v 2 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ mo Lomaęž‰ ami haliwekinaęž‰ you hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekeme. Koto halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tieke homeeke e pokao hayeke hali teke paęž‰taęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ taapeekeme.
\v 3 Kutu pieke handaa mo ami you halimaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekimanu opuaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo mandane Diunaęž‰ tondiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ e pokao hayeke some aęž‰pa epeawaenaęž‰ yeke handaa mulu pupe laa tapaeyekeme.
\v 4 Koto tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa otaęž‰ meme piki honke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke tambaęž‰ miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ halie. Pa ekipeke.
\v 5 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali teke paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ wotu homo halaęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ siki kone nikaęž‰ pi hotu halomaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰eyaeyaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Kotoeki opuaataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pua mo da teke paęž‰taęž‰ polueke alo pulu haenaęž‰ mo ami you halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke tonumaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pimanu lenaęž‰yeke tapaeyekeme. Tekehalio. Pinaęž‰ pae.
\v 7 Neke ya da paęž‰taęž‰ epoelenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epeke hali diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ na ipilipikie laa Neke hale alenaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke make otaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yeni pa paenaęž‰e pi homeke lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ya e pokaasaęž‰ sometaęž‰ tialieke.
\v 8 Pa ekipeke. IĚ±taęž‰ mandane ami you hali oto paęž‰taęž‰ halome. Kutaa IĚ± oto paęž‰taęž‰ make mandane ami haliweki halememe. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Pue loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pelieke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make Epoe loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke. Kutupa yaka pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ some paęž‰taęž‰ Do e pokae loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ pealieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Koto leekeeki Yesumaęž‰ opuolotaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ mo hande ipiki telimiki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneao handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Dupiki hone tulaake some homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ± na handolome. Mo Isulai tapake tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ kone otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ ulume.
\v 10 Kutupa mo tapaeyaęž‰ haliweki paa laęž‰kaęž‰la mo ami you halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo hande e pokao hayeke halitaęž‰ pa epeke tupaęž‰ tiao pitiekeeki handemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kinekenaęž‰ weki mea tiaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 11 Hosiki siki haotaęž‰ wetepe nane Yesu ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki make wandaęž‰hali wotu anekehapu ameĚ±leĚ± Neini daoni paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 12 Ipiki pua mo teke da anekenaęž‰ wieke daoni potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ opolo polueke alo pulu haenaęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ mo homeeke hali toko mea hoilu poluekemaęž‰ yeke tia ipulu pitimikime. Mo homeeke halitaęž‰ kineke wandaęž‰ siki maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ homeke weki siki yeekeme. Mo teke da aneke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ mo kineke wandaęž‰ siki ameĚ±leĚ± ipulu pitimikime.
\v 13 Tekehalimaęž‰ mo hande kineke wandaęž‰ handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ E na lapee leekeme.
\v 14 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo toko tia epemeke bokosi teke paęž‰taęž‰ pua wataeyekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo hande hali toko timiki haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ pa tupaleke handeteke haemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wekio. IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ lomaęž‰ tiae leekeme.
\v 15 Mo hande homeeke wekitaęž‰ paa tiao pitaęž‰taęž‰ pimanu lombo leekeme. Kutu pieke Yesumaęž‰ mo hande wekitaęž‰ inkiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ moneayekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ dupiki hau hando hao pututumaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea miniliaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ aneke potopede maęž‰ndaęž‰ niki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ yeke aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 17 Do hande Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekinaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ koto kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make mo kenke honiki honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰manu latia pomimikime.
\s1 Dionimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke hali yaapo
\r (Maęž‰tiu 11ęž‰2-19)
\p 
\v 18 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekimanu paeyao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ la halemekeme. Koto leeke Dionimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali yaapo wi laęž‰mea
\v 19 alotaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ pua dupa lotaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Neketaęž‰ hande Dionimaęž‰ Ipilieke leeke niki paeyaomaęž‰ yu wia halomaęž‰ hande hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe o hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epenaęž‰ yu wia hamonope laa Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 20 Mo hande hali yaapotaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Mo bapitaisi peao halaęž‰ hali Dionimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ diki tapaeyeke handaa epopaęž‰me. Neketaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ hande ipilieke leeke yu wia halomaęž‰ hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe o paa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epenaęž‰ yu wia hamonope laa lotaęž‰ pitolopaęž‰me lepekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Koto tomonaęž‰ kone Yesumaęž‰ yeni taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ hake wandaęž‰hali make hoke temoko pitieke wandaęž‰hali wopu make leke holu piki wandaęž‰hali make paeyao mea epeatiki piekeme.
\v 22 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo Dionimaęž‰ tapaeyeke hali yaaponaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipiliki paa laęž‰kaęž‰la puaataęž‰ do handepe ekimanu make do opipieki paeyaotaęž‰ Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ pua la halaęž‰paęž‰peke. Dupa lapaęž‰peke. Mo leke holu piki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ paa handelememe. Mo anke dolaęž‰pake piki wandaęž‰hali make ametaęž‰ potaęž‰ pulimime. Kutupa mo kindi yeni halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make ametaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ halememe. Mo katake pokaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make ametaęž‰ pi anaęž‰naęž‰ opitelememe. Otaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali make ametaęž‰ paa mea tiao epeke tupaęž‰ halememe. Kutupa maketaęž‰ mo hande Pi Seliapotaęž‰ mo natehali wandaęž‰hali sunu paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰
\v 23 IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone yaapo yaapo lo na wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe laa lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Mo hande hali yaapo Yesu minaęž‰paęž‰lao pepeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ pi dupa laeyekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hapupapeke alenaęž‰ Dioni handuluekemaęž‰ pemeke hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ aleke handuluekemaęž‰ pemepe. Pomaęž‰ mo ambu mea anemone pea mekeaasaęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ pemepe.
\v 25 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto alenaęž‰ otaęž‰ aleke handuluekemaęž‰ pemepe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ epeke hamoko akaęž‰manu pambao haliaęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ pemepe. Kutupiki akaęž‰manu yama haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hamoko hali leke hataęž‰ kini haliwekinaęž‰ aneke da epeke paęž‰taęž‰ homeke halimikie.
\v 26 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± la kipaęž‰e. Aleke handuluekemaęž‰ pemepe. Potopede hali handuluekemaęž‰ pemepe. Aowe. Otaęž‰e. Kutu pimipate ipikitaęž‰ mo potopede haliweki paeyao otaęž‰ ankulake hali handememe.
\v 27 Koto ekitaęž‰ mo hande Baibolo bukamaęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ piekeeki dupa lao ulaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na epeke halenaęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ya pimanu mea epenaęž‰yeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapalueke. Titinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ potaęž‰ pilawalieke laa laęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opuaęž‰pe. Dioni ipikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ haemeke haliweki paeyao lu ankulalaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ oto paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hali ipikitaęž‰ Dioni lu ankulao halaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto pi opuaataęž‰ iki make mo dakisi mani mu haemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± paeyaotaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ iki bapitaisi peaenaęž‰ laataęž‰ ame dotaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi opitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ tikitiki yaęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 30 Pate mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki pitaęž‰ Lo Pi walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ kiaasotaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ iki bapitaisi peaapaęž‰naęž‰yeke kiaemekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ aleke tupaęž‰ mandaęž‰ meanope o ikitaęž‰ alekemaęž‰ handelemepe.
\v 32 Koto wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ mo makedi hama pa pitu haleme wekiwandikimaęž‰ handelememe. Mo tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ pa mo tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wi laęž‰moneaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki samaęž‰ puemenaęž‰yeke tapeke lumaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ samaęž‰ na piki kiaememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa homaęž‰ emelimanu laomaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ eĚ± na leke kiaememe laa lemekeme.
\v 33 Mo hande bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionimaęž‰ hoto paeyaotaęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ nee pi wiaęž‰tiki piekeeki make waini ikali na naęž‰tiki pieke ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ hoke temoko pilaęž‰ halie lememe.
\v 34 Koto lemepate mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke ipiki aęž‰paataęž‰ ne make ikali aęž‰pa naęž‰tiki pieke handaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hali handaęž‰paęž‰ ikali ne wopu no hake some yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ mo dakisi mani mu haleme haliweki make mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homeleme tapekenaęž‰ yankeke halaęž‰me laa lememe
\v 35 laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ epeke hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki tolu haleme wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ haumaęž‰ kone mo hande hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epekeekie laa peneme yao halimikie leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Paęž‰tisi hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Saimononaęž‰ da peekeeki
\p 
\v 36 Kutupa nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu ne nolo epenaęž‰ yeke wi leeke handaa Yesutaęž‰ ne nolueke alo pua pitiekeme.
\v 37 Kutupa koto da teke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hali yolo hayeke wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekeme. Koto wandaęž‰maęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa ne no pilaęž‰me lemeeki opuaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰baęž‰setaęž‰ toopimaęž‰ wepiki kanakenaęž‰ mo totopo wotu piki oeta pambekeeki mea minaęž‰ mo da paęž‰taęž‰ epeekeme.
\v 38 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eĚ± tondaęž‰paęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ lopenaęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ itikimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ mo hande eĚ± tondaęž‰paęž‰ honia nunu peataęž‰ mo totopo wotu piki oetataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ holayekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Mo hande Paęž‰tisi halimaęž‰ kotoeki handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ potopede hali yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ do wandaęž‰maęž‰ wataasaęž‰me laa peneme handolo piaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto wandaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ hone ulu piaęž‰me laa hone wiekeme.
\p 
\v 40 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Saimonoo. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ lonoe leekeme. Mo halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi litolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe disao. La kie leekeme.
\v 41 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ dupa leekeme. Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ toopi tondiki halo hayeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hali yaapomaęž‰ toopi tondiki mipikime. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pa wieke tondikitaęž‰ 100 kina. Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ekitaęž‰ 10 kina pa wiekeme.
\v 42 Mo hande tondiki mipiki hali yaapomaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ ambulaęž‰peke na yeke handaa mo tondiki halo hayeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ tondikitaęž‰ pinaęž‰ pa paeyaeyekeme laataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Saimono paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto hali yaapo epimaęž‰ hondo mo tondiki halo hayeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ puki anekehapu haliaęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 43 Koto leeke Saimonomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pa mataęž‰laęž‰me. Ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ tondiki tieke kone pa paeyaeyeke hali yelieke leekeme. Koto leeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ aleme leekeme.
\p 
\v 44 Kutaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pa mo wandaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ Saimono paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do wandaęž‰taęž‰ handelepe. IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hondaęž‰ pamboaęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ya anke tandaęž‰paęž‰peke ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na kipate do wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eĚ± tondaęž‰paęž‰maęž‰ kone ya anke tandaęž‰pao ipikaęž‰ itikimaęž‰ pa mea honiaeyaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 45 Kutupa IĚ± do da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamboaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± nunu na pipate do wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ya anke nunu piaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hande IĚ± epoaęž‰ dinaęž‰ kini peaataęž‰ ame do make paa pitolo pilaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 46 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo olipi oetataęž‰ ya younaęž‰ na kitaepate do wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke totopo piki oeta yaka ankenaęž‰ kitawayaęž‰me.
\v 47 IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki tieke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wopu paęž‰laęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ do paetaęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰e laa walaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau hosikale siki kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paeyaowayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ puki hosikale siki halieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 48 Koto laa Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ pele hoke hau paeyaotaęž‰ paelaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 49 Pate mo teipolonaęž‰ tilao pitimiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi la alualu pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hoke hau kone tandaęž‰paasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe lemekeme.
\v 50 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hone tulale ekimaęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰me. Puki lopao pue leekeme.
\c 8
\s1 Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± pomimiki wandaęž‰weki
\p 
\v 1 Hosiki siki hao wetepe nanetaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo daoni paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make mo hosiki da sunu paęž‰taęž‰ make pominolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Pi Seliapo wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ la halaęž‰tiki pomiekeme. Kutupa make ipikaęž‰ 12 disaipolo haliweki make ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± pemekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ mo hande hoke temokomanu tolu lia make yenimanu pea mea epeaeyeke wandaęž‰weki make Yesu teliaęž‰ mea pomimikime. Metitaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ temoko watake hataęž‰ pitiekeeki tolu lieke wandaęž‰e. Ipikaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Maęž‰kadalawandaęž‰e.
\v 3 Kutupa mo Hetodinaęž‰ da handeteke hayeke ami you hali Tiusanaęž‰ weteke bikitaęž‰ Dioaęž‰na make Susaęž‰na make mandane wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ make yeekeme. Mo wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mani manutaęž‰ Yesu make ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ tambaęž‰ mutia pomu hatiki pimikime.
\s1 Wae ale manunaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰1-9, Maka 4ęž‰1-9)
\p 
\v 4 Wandaęž‰hali aneke hapumaęž‰ daoni maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa ipulu ipulu ombu hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tieke mombelemeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa la haleekeme.
\v 5 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e paęž‰taęž‰ wae alemanu aęž‰pa tandeleekeme. Tandelaęž‰tia pulu haenaęž‰ mandane wae ale manutaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ lopaęž‰ lopaęž‰ piekeme. Kutu pieke mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ankemaęž‰ tumba tumba piki hau make ba titimaęž‰ make aęž‰pa yataęž‰po nemekeme.
\v 6 Mandane wae ale manutaęž‰ toopimanu manda taĚ±leeke kenke sikinaęž‰ lopeekeme. Koto wae aletaęž‰ opeekepate koto toopi manda wieke kenketaęž‰ tenke tenke na leekeeki yaalo opuluekemaęž‰ piki nono peataęž‰ pa hapiekeme.
\v 7 Mandane wae ale manutaęž‰ tekeke hake alemanu paęž‰taęž‰manu lopeekeme. Kutupa mo tekeke hake alemanu opaęž‰liaaso hataęž‰ hande wae alemanu opolo pieke ekitaęž‰ tombuaeyekeme.
\v 8 Kutu piekepate mandane wae ale manutaęž‰ epeke kenkenaęž‰ lopaataęž‰ opaęž‰liao napeketaęž‰ 100manu wiekeme. Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi lo aęž‰mbolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Katake lombaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ wotu opinaęž‰e leekeme.
\s1 Onkolumaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teke
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰10-17, Maka 4ęž‰10-12)
\p 
\v 9 Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do onkolumaęž‰naęž‰ teke pi la kie lemekeme.
\v 10 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ aęž‰mbaalaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate mo mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi homekemaęž‰ la halolome. Pa ekipeke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handolo pelemepate na handenaęž‰ opulu pelemepate hone na winaęž‰e leekeme.
\s1 Wae alenaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi teke waleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰18-23, Maka 4ęž‰13-20)
\p 
\v 11 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do onkolumaęž‰ alo ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ dupae. Mo hande wae aletaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pie.
\v 12 Mo potaęž‰naęž‰ lopeaęž‰ wae ale manutaęž‰ pi opiteleme wandaęž‰hali anaęž‰naęž‰ halememe. Mo hoke Sadanimaęž‰ hande pi ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ yokaęž‰ mea ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto pi paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulao tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki na minaęž‰yeke do hau pu halaęž‰me.
\v 13 Mo toopi pankaęž‰ pankaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰ wae ale manutaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opua taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ minaęž‰lemepate otaęž‰ wopu na mendiki hosiki haotaęž‰ mo la handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu ipulaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ paa lopo halememe.
\v 14 Kutupa mo hande tekeke hake ale polu paęž‰taęž‰ lopeeke wae ale manutaęž‰ pi opu haleme wandaęž‰hali tupaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate do kenkenaęž‰ haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ hone eleke eleke wopu witaęž‰laęž‰meeki make hamoko hau make do kenke lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemanu tumbatiki pitaęž‰leke handaa daęž‰kaęž‰polo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiliki na potaęž‰lieke.
\v 15 Kutupa mo epeke kenkenaęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰ wae ale manutaęž‰ pi opua homu pu haleme wandaęž‰hali ikanaęž‰maęž‰ honkopu hao epeke tupaęž‰ minaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiliki aneke aęž‰eluekemaęž‰ pa putia pelimikie leekeme.
\s1 PaĚ±aĚ± aęž‰mbaasaęž‰ pi
\r (Maka 4ęž‰21-25)
\p 
\v 16 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ lamepa kaęž‰waataęž‰ sini tiekemaęž‰ na mea dopuaniao o bedi tokele paęž‰taęž‰ na u halaęž‰me. Koto hau na pikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali aęž‰pa hondaęž‰ pambetiki pitolo handenaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ mo lamepa u halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ u halaęž‰me.
\v 17 Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰mbao pankaęž‰ ulaęž‰ aletaęž‰ hama nane peneme yao mea aęž‰pa wilieke. Kutupa make alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ tote pealimi ekitaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ peneme yao mea ipilimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi opu haleme ekitaęž‰ wotu handeteke hao hapaęž‰peke. Ekipeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao otaęž‰ wotu milieke. Pate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hosikieki make ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ Ulume laa wiaęž‰eki kone yokaęž‰ mealieke leekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ inkiki hameketonu
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰46-50, Maka 3ęž‰31-35)
\p 
\v 19 Yesunaęž‰ amaęž‰ make hameke tonumaęž‰ ipiki handolo epemekepate Yesu teke paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yeekeme. Ekipeke wandaęž‰hali anekehapumaęž‰ Yesu mea hopaęž‰liao haemekeme.
\v 20 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ kame tonutaęž‰ neke handuluekemaęž‰ da hama do aęž‰pa halememe leekeme.
\v 21 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opua pu haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ yaka amaęž‰ kametonu halememe leekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ pimaęž‰ po tilipu tunkulaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰23-27, Maka 4ęž‰35-41)
\p 
\v 22 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pua kawaso maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pitulu pemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ do ikali tunkula mone teaęž‰naęž‰ bape leekeme. Kutupataęž‰ iki kini pea pulutaęž‰
\v 23 mo kawaso pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ u peliekeme. Kutupa koto kone po tilipu tieke epeeketaęž‰ mo ikalitaęž‰ kawaso tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ tumbieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo haliwekitaęž‰ paalaęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu aęž‰pa tiao alotaęž‰ Aneke halio. Aneke halio. Nikitaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ do homolomaęž‰ handaęž‰e lemekeme. Koto lemeke Yesu tiaotaęž‰ mo hande honkopu wopu hake po tilipu paęž‰taęž‰ make mo laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ piki honkopu hake ikali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Paae leeke handaa ipilikaęž‰ honkopu paeyao upa lopaataęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ na piki eĚ± pondo na lepekeme.
\v 25 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ hone tulaleme ekitaęž‰ hando kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme. Koto leekepate iki paeyaomaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo make paalaęž‰maęž‰ wotu homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Mo ikali pitaęž‰ po tilipu yaapomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi otaęž‰ opitelepeme lemekeme.
\s1 Kedasa halinaęž‰ hoke temokomanu tolu liekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰28-34, Maka 5ęž‰1-20)
\p 
\v 26 Koto hau pea paeyeketaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo Kedasa kenke paęž‰taęž‰ kawasonaęž‰ pua opaęž‰liaemekeme. Koto Kedasa kenketaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili kenke nanemaęž‰ hao mo ikali leke tunkula pua mone teaęž‰naęž‰ ulaęž‰me.
\v 27 Yesumaęž‰ mo kawaso minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu pitiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ mo daoni maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hao ipiki mandaęž‰hande pipikime. Otaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande hatiki aęž‰paataęž‰ ame make mo sometaęž‰ akaęž‰ na yameke make da paęž‰taęž‰ na hao polu make ipikitaęž‰ mo homo hayeke haliweki u haemeke tikene da paęž‰taęž‰manu hao hayekeme.
\v 28 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu handaataęž‰ wi tieke alo hataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ anke paęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰niao kenkenaęž‰ tu lopaataęž‰ wi anekemaęž‰ pa alo alotaęž‰ Yesuo. Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ Manda Halaęž‰ Tiekenaęž‰ Eiyekee. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± yaapo eki hau puluekemaęž‰ pitelepe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ tanda na kiaęž‰pee laa honke leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Koto leeke ekitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo hoke temoko paęž‰taęž‰ Pue leeke ekinaęž‰ leekeme. Nate paeyao mo hoke temokomaęž‰ mo hali wotu lu keatiki pomu hayekeme. Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰taęž‰ mo halitaęž‰ dipula pitao senipu manumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki anke mea tonkao u hatiki pimikipate kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo senipumanu tunkulaęž‰ lubepi piaęž‰tiki peaataęž‰ mo hoke temokomaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ lu mea puaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\p 
\v 30 Yesumaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pieke handaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka bikitaęž‰ Eleke elekee leekeme. Koto leeke ekitaęž‰ temoko eleke eleke wotu ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitieke ekinaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 31 Mo hoke temoko tonumaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ honke honke wotu alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki mo tanda mu halo polomaęž‰ naku kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ tieke paęž‰taęž‰ dipula pitulu pomono na tapaapeke lemekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Koto alenaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ titi monemaęž‰ hayeke peiyene teaęž‰naęž‰ ne nalo haenaęž‰ mo hoke temoko tonumaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ honke alotaęž‰ Mo maęž‰naęž‰ titinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitulu pomono lae lemeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honke lemeke tupaęž‰ pa pinaęž‰ la kiaeyekeme.
\v 33 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao maęž‰naęž‰ titinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitulu pemekeme. Kutu pimikitaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ mo peiyene paeleeke alenaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya pua holaęž‰paęž‰niao ikali paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ ikali naa honki lemekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Mo maęž‰naęž‰ titi handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mo pieke ekimanu handaataęž‰ pindipa puataęž‰ daoni nane haemeke wandaęž‰hali make koto daoni tekepaęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali make laęž‰tiki pomimikime.
\v 35 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hande pieke ekimanu handuluekemaęž‰ pua Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande weleke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temokomanu pitieke halitaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ dau yama epeke hone wia pitiekeeki handolo hataęž‰taęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 36 Mo hali mea epeaaso piekeeki handemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo piekeeki manutaęž‰ mo epemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ la halemekeme.
\v 37 Kutupa mo Kedasa kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki minaęž‰paęž‰lao pue lemekeme. Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ mo kawasonaęž‰ pitulu pua peekeme.
\v 38 Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu tolu lieke halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ honke alo alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ neke yaapo panaęž‰e leekeme. Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ mo hali paa tapaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 39 Neke nakaęž‰ da nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ piaęž‰ hande ekimanu paeyao wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pua la halaęž‰tiki pu hapeke leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ teke da nane puaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipiki tambaęž‰ miekeeki paeyaosiki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pua la hale hale piekeme.
\s1 Diaitusinaęž‰ wandiki pitaęž‰ yeni hao hayeke wandaęž‰ yaapo
\r (Maęž‰tiu 9ęž‰18-26, Maka 5ęž‰21-43)
\p 
\v 40 Yesu mo kawasonaęž‰ pita ikali leke mone teaęž‰naęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la peeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ opolo polo pieke ekinaęž‰ yu wia handeteke haemeke ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homemekeme.
\v 41 Koto tomonaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo pi hotu haemeke danaęž‰ you hali bikitaęž‰ Diaitusimaęž‰ aęž‰pa Yesunaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniao ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ honke leekeme.
\v 42 Pa ekipeke ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeke hayeke bapitaęž‰ 12 yeeke wandikitaęž‰ tekesiki paęž‰taęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ taapolo pitieke handaa leekeme. Koto leeke Yesu pulu haenaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali anekehapu mandane mandane yamaęž‰ aęž‰pa mombaęž‰laaso hataęž‰ Yesu mea dakaęž‰pa dakaęž‰pa puluekemaęž‰ taapemekeme.
\v 43 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ mo bapi 12 andusaęž‰naęž‰ we yopu hayeke wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ yeni tambaęž‰ minaęž‰yeke dokeda haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mani paeyao halaęž‰tiki piekepate ipikaęž‰ yenitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na epeaeyekeme.
\v 44 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ puataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ hoki nanemaęž‰ aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ dopieke dau honiki wataeyekeme. Koto tomonaęž‰ kone hande we yapeeke ekitaęž‰ paeyekeme.
\v 45 Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epimaęž‰ wataeyaęž‰pe leekeme. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na wataomaęž‰me lemeketaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ neke mea hopaęž‰liao dakaęž‰paasaęž‰ handaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 46 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke IĚ± tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ honkoputaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ puleke handaa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± otaęž‰ wataeyaęž‰me laa loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 47 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ puaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa pututumaęž‰ homaęž‰tia aęž‰pa Yesunaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pandaęž‰ puniaeyekeme. Wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ leke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau honiki wataeyeke ekinaęž‰ teke make mo ipikaęž‰ yeni koto kone paeyekeeki make laa haleekeme.
\p 
\v 48 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya wandikio. Nakaęž‰ hone tulale ekimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yeni ame do kone mea epeaasaęž‰me. Puki lopao pue leekeme.
\p 
\v 49 Yesumaęž‰ do pi alo haenaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo you halinaęž‰ da nane hao aęž‰pa Diaitusi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ wandikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeaęž‰me. Mo Disa paęž‰taęž‰ pinaęž‰ pa paenaęž‰ lae leekeme.
\v 50 Koto leekeeki opua Yesumaęž‰ Diaitusi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pee. Hone tulaase hau homeke pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandiki sikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ paa tialieke leekeme.
\v 51 Yesu mo da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pulu haenaęž‰ mo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na penaęž‰ leekepate pa Pida Dioni Diaęž‰mesi make mo wandikinaęž‰ ateke inkiki yaapo pea Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambemekeme.
\v 52 Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandikinaęž‰ eĚ± alo hataęž‰ homaęž‰ wia pitimikime. Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ EĚ± na lapepe. Do wandiki sikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na homaęž‰laęž‰pate pa u peliolo hataęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 53 Koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandiki siki otaęž‰ homeaęž‰eki handemeke ekinaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ kitaemekeme.
\v 54 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ mo wandiki sikinaęž‰ kiki mea wi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandiki sikio. Tiae leekeme.
\v 55 Koto alemaęž‰ kone mo wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki paa aęž‰pa ipiki paa tiaeyekeme. Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo ateke inkiki paęž‰taęž‰ Mo wandiki ne maęž‰ndaęž‰ halaęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 56 Kotoeki handaataęž‰ mo wandikinaęž‰ ateke inkiki yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ dotaęž‰ otaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰pe honemaęž‰ lapeke pi peaęž‰ mamataęž‰pa pekepate Yesumaęž‰ mo tooli paęž‰taęž‰ pi tanda pikimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ do pitoloeki na la halaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\c 9
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo 12 disaipolo haliweki tapaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 10ęž‰5-15, Maka 6ęž‰7-13)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ mo 12 disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Ipupaęž‰e laa homeke paęž‰taęž‰ mea mombaęž‰laotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yenimanu mea epeaenaęž‰ make hoke temokomanu paeyaosiki tolu linaęž‰yeke Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ biki pitaęž‰ honkopu yaapo hale hale piekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ yeni haleme wandaęž‰hali mea epeawaenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki tapaeyekeme.
\v 3 Tapaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme. Iki paeyao potaęž‰ poluekemaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mea minaęž‰paęž‰peke. Koto alo ale manutaęž‰ tumapu o nu o ne o mani o topo peaęž‰peke sedi homeke kone na mea minaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 4 Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ iki hatuku peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo daoni minaęž‰paęž‰lalueke hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pua hale da paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hao puaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 5 Daoni maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mandali epimaęž‰ iki na handaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto daoni minaęž‰paęž‰laaso hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali kinki pitolotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ taĚ±laĚ±ęž‰laĚ±ęž‰ dokolo tande lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 6 Koto ekimanu lo paeyaeyeketaęž‰ hande 12 disaipolo haliwekitaęž‰ Yesu minaęž‰paęž‰lao da halaęž‰ halaęž‰ pomu lopolo hataęž‰ hande Pi Seliapo walaęž‰tiki pominolo hataęž‰ iki pomimiki ale paęž‰taęž‰manu wandaęž‰hali mea epeatia pomimikime.
\s1 Hetodimaęž‰ pomomaęž‰ homeekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 14ęž‰1-12, Maka 6ęž‰14-29)
\p 
\v 7 Mo Kaęž‰lili da kenke paęž‰taęž‰ you hali Hetodimaęž‰ koto pieke ekinaęž‰ pi paeyao opieke ekimaęž‰ pomomaęž‰ homeekeme. Pa ekipeke mandane haliwekimaęž‰ dupiki pi la alualu pimikime. Mo bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionitaęž‰ paa tiao aęž‰pa halaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Elaidia peneme yao opolo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ambaęž‰ hande hayeke potopede hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paa tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Hetodimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ make mea tunkuluaęž‰pate pa do pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ opitolo halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu otaęž‰ handuluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ 5 daoseni wandaęž‰hali ne haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 14ęž‰13-21, Maka 6ęž‰30-44, Dioni 6ęž‰1-14)
\p 
\v 10 Mo aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ paa aęž‰pa ikaęž‰ pimiki ekimanu paeyaosiki Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ la halemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ikaęž‰ siki mo Betesaida teke da paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 11 Kutu pimikieki opitolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ mombaęž‰latia pulu hataęž‰ Yesu teli mea pemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo epemeke wandaęž‰hali handaataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi walolotaęž‰ yeni homemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mea epeaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Welealo nane nate pambolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo 12 disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Do niki halomaęž‰ alenaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali na hake alenaęž‰maęž‰ do wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo da sunu make mo napeke ne make peliaęž‰peke damanu weinaęž‰maęž‰ penaęž‰ tapae lemekeme.
\v 13 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone mo wandaęž‰hali ne halaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Koto leeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ palaowa walaęž‰ kiki homekenaęž‰ taęž‰peli yaapo pea homeke wia halomaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ ne paeyao hambalo pomonope laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 14 Ekipeke 5 daoseni haliweki koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hali tieke yaaponaęž‰ kiki yaapomanu tupaęž‰ mombaęž‰lao kenkenaęž‰ mea pitamaęž‰ pitamaęž‰ pipee leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ koto hau pimikitaęž‰
\v 16 Yesumaęž‰ mo hande kiki homeke palaowa walaęž‰ sunu make mo taęž‰peli yaapo pea meataęž‰ oli ya nane handaęž‰liao hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi leekeme. Koto laataęž‰ mo ne pindi pindi peaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ telipape laa haleekeme.
\v 17 Mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ne anaęž‰naęž‰ no tumba tumba peaataęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo putupiliki wiekeeki manutaęž‰ kiki yaapo paeya ankenaęž‰ yaapo wieke nunaęž‰ mondu tumba tumba pea wimikime.
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Ketisoe leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 16ęž‰13-19, Maka 8ęž‰27-29)
\p 
\v 18 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honumake hataęž‰ yeni pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki opolo epemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Epinaęž‰ biki lo halemepe leekeme.
\v 19 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ mo bapitaisi peao hayaęž‰ hali Dioni lo halememe. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Elaidia lo halememe. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ potopede hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande homeaęž‰pate ame dosiki paa tiao halaęž‰ halie lo halememe lemekeme.
\v 20 Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epi lo halemepe leeke handaa Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Ketisoe leekeme.
\v 21 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ loaęž‰maęž‰ do pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Tanda meaataęž‰ homolueke leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 16ęž‰20-28, Maka 8ęž‰30â€”9ęž‰1)
\p 
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ paa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ alo alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ tanda tieke otaęž‰ wotu meaataęž‰ mo Diu tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make yeni peao haleme you haliwekimaęž‰ make wape pea ulaęž‰ Lo Pimanu walaęž‰tiki pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ make ipiki kialimikie. Ipikitaęž‰ homenaęž‰ lulu pelemepate hoto tepo wiaataęž‰ paa tialieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Koto laataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea ipulueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone hone yonkaęž‰lao nate paeyao ipikaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki ti mea tia pominolo hataęž‰ IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea pomu haenaęž‰e.
\v 24 Pa ekipeke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki alupaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke hone wotu wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ alupalieke. Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki alu pinaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paa miniki halieke.
\v 25 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ honkopu hao do kenkenaęž‰ anemone ale paeyao minaęž‰laęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰eki kone alu pao o tondiki haleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto ale manumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ekipa tambaęž‰ miliaęž‰pe.
\v 26 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make yaka waloaęž‰ pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke make Ateke make yako piki enisolo tonu make iki paeyaonaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰paataęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ mo hande hali paęž‰taęž‰ make yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaalieke.
\v 27 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do haleme mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ambi na homeke hamenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki otaęž‰ handilimikie leekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ wonu piliekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 17ęž‰1-8, Maka 9ęž‰2-8)
\p 
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰ dupiki pi laa pula homekemanu paeyeketaęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ pote maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Pida Dioni Diaęž‰mesi hatuku opaęž‰liaemekeme.
\v 29 Yesumaęž‰ yeni pitolo pitinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pikieki hao make ipikaęž‰ pambaeyeke akaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hake wotu pea baeyeke ekimaęž‰ leke yale yale piki nono piekeme.
\v 30 Kutupa koto kone hali yaapotaęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ pi lemekeme. Mo hali yaapotaęž‰ Mosesi pitaęž‰ Elaidia yaapo yeekeme.
\v 31 Ipilikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pinaęž‰e hone ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ homolo pieke ekinaęž‰ pi hotiolo haemekeme.
\v 32 Pida pitaęž‰ mo hali yaapo peataęž‰ u yokaęž‰lupa pemekepate tiaotaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pikieki make mo Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± haepeke hali yaapo handemekeme.
\v 33 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ hali yaapotaęž‰ Yesu minaęž‰paęž‰lao poluekemaęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Niki do paęž‰taęž‰ halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke epomekeme. Topu da tepo aęž‰eyamono lae. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ nakaęž‰eki. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ Mosesinaęž‰eki. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ Elaidianaęž‰eki pea aęž‰eyamono lae leekeme. Pidamaęž‰ leeke pi manutaęž‰ hone wotu na wiki hataęž‰ leekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Pidamaęž‰ dupiki pi alo haenaęž‰taęž‰ koa aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ suĚ±aĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki mea tumbaeyekeme. Tumbaeyeke handaataęž‰ mo disaipolo haliweki tepomaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 35 Mo koa tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ laęž‰niaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do ya wekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kiki maĚ±leke lulu wekimaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰pe laa laęž‰niaeyekeme.
\v 36 Koto pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make laa paeyeke nanetaęž‰ Yesu homeke hapelia hayekeeki handemekeme. Mo hali tepomaęž‰ mo handemeke ekimanu wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na la haleke ikaęž‰ homeke hone wimikime.
\s1 Hoke temokomaęž‰ hoeyaeyeke weki epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 17ęž‰14-18, Maka 9ęž‰14-27)
\p 
\v 37 Da maęž‰ndaęž‰ kelepeeketaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo hali tepo ameĚ±leĚ± mo pote minaęž‰paęž‰lao holaęž‰paęž‰niaemekepate wandaęž‰hali aneke hapumaęž‰ Yesu aęž‰pa mandaęž‰hande pimikime.
\v 38 Mo wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ aęž‰pa hayeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ wi anekemaęž‰ alo alotaęž‰ Disao. IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ honke alomaęž‰ yaka weki aęž‰pa handaęž‰e. Ipikitaęž‰ yaka otaęž‰ homeke wekie.
\v 39 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ mo hoke temokomaęž‰ minaęž‰tiki pitaęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± wi tieke laęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo hoke temokomaęž‰ mo weki mea lu keao kake paęž‰taęž‰ dako hankolomaęž‰ lu halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo hoke temokomaęž‰ yombu moneatiki pu hataęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na minaęž‰paęž‰lalieke.
\v 40 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ tolu linaęž‰yeke honke loaęž‰pate mo haliwekimaęž‰ anaęž‰ na piaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 41 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ hone wopu na tulaake ataęž‰kaęž‰ peao haleme wandaęž‰halie. Nate ekipunaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± ombu hao hanope. Nate ekipunaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ kiteleme ekimanu meanope laataęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ weki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epoe leekeme.
\v 42 Mo weki ipulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hoke temokomaęž‰ mo weki kenkenaęž‰ mea lopao lu keayekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo hoke temoko hando laataęž‰ mo weki mea epeao ipikaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ paa halaęž‰ moneayekeme.
\v 43 Koto hau handemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ honkopu wotu halaęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime.
\s1 Ipikaęž‰ homa tiaalo piekeeki paa la haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 17ęž‰22-23, Maka 9ęž‰30-32)
\p Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ putia pomiekeeki handaataęž‰ pututu pieke pi pa alo alo haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 44 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ la kulu polo pi opua hone na yonkaęž‰lapaęž‰peke. Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo mandane haliwekinaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ monealieke leekeme.
\v 45 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ hone na wimikime. Mo pi teketaęž‰ iki aęž‰mbaeyeke handaa ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰peke na yeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pi tekenaęž‰ lotaęž‰ piaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ na lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\s1 Tumiki halitaęž‰ epipe
\r (Maęž‰tiu 18ęž‰1-5, Maka 9ęž‰33-37)
\p 
\v 46 Kutupa mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone tumiki halitaęž‰ epipe laa pi la alualu pimikime.
\v 47 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ wimiki ekimanu handaataęž‰ hosiki weki siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hatuku aęž‰pa tiao hataęž‰
\v 48 iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ yaka bikinaęž‰ dupiki weki siki handaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± kone handaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± handaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali make handaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ biki na wiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paeyaosiki lu ankulalaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ na liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ekie
\r (Maka 9ęž‰38-40)
\p 
\v 49 Dionimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ hoke temokomanu tolu baeyaęž‰pate mo halitaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± na tunaleke handaa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hau na piaęž‰pe laa saęž‰saęž‰ pumaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 50 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ na taapaęž‰peke. Ekipeke iki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ na litaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰nie leekeme.
\s1 Sametia da maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu meaęž‰peke kiaemekeeki
\p 
\v 51 Yesu oli hepeni nane mea polo pieke nate teke paęž‰taęž‰ yolo epeeketaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme teke da nane otaęž‰ polueke hone u paleke peekeme.
\v 52 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Sametia da maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane ipikaęž‰ da ne alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wamo peaenaęž‰ yeke kinki haliweki tapaeyekeme.
\v 53 Kutu pimikipate koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da nane yopulaęž‰me laataęž‰ ipiki na handaęž‰ mimikime.
\v 54 Kutu pimikieki mo disaipolo hali Diaęž‰mesi pitaęž‰ Dioni yaapomaęž‰ dupiki hau handaataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ dikanaęž‰maęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ ti uleke aęž‰pa do wandaęž‰hali mea hoeyaenaęž‰ wi loponope lepekeme.
\v 55 Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kutupiki pi na lapepee leekeme.
\v 56 Kutupa Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± da siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\s1 Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± ponope laa taapaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰19-22)
\p 
\v 57 Ikitaęž‰ mo potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ neke pomilipi ale paęž‰taęž‰manu taęž‰liaęž‰ mea ipulueke leekeme.
\v 58 Yesumaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tikene kika manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kenke kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ wiaataęž‰ ba manumaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ dakemanu halaęž‰pate pa mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoto minolo peliaęž‰peke da otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ siki make diaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 59 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea epoe leekepate mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la yaka apaęž‰ mea hoilu pono lae leekeme.
\v 60 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Homeeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali toko mea hoinaęž‰maęž‰ neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi pua walaęž‰tiki pu hae leekeme.
\p 
\v 61 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. IĚ±taęž‰ neke teliaęž‰ mea ipuluekemaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la yaka tapake paęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰taloe lolo ponoe leekeme.
\v 62 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kenke aowaęž‰ mea lopaasaęž‰ ale miniki hataęž‰ kenke aowaęž‰tia pulutaęž‰ hoki nane handaęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ e pokaapeke anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\c 10
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ 72 haliweki tapaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Do hande haumanu peaataęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ 72 haliweki mea yaapo yaapo pu mo ipiki polo pieke da paęž‰taęž‰manu tapa tapa piekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ne napeke wotu mo enaęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰laęž‰pate mo ne mombaęž‰laapeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ aneke hapu diaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo e teke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enaęž‰ ne mea mombaęž‰laalo peleme wandaęž‰hali anaęž‰naęž‰ tapaenaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni pu hapaęž‰peke.
\v 3 Pupaęž‰e IĚ±maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ ikikisunu mandane tikene kikamanu haleme ale paęž‰taęž‰manu taa tapaaso handaęž‰e.
\v 4 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mani pausa o nu sunu o anke dake maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mea puaęž‰paęž‰peke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± potaęž‰naęž‰ mandaęž‰hande pitolo hataęž‰ pi na lapaęž‰peke.
\v 5 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la koto da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰eki epenaęž‰e lapaęž‰peke.
\v 6 Kutupa koto da paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone wopu u halaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰ pi le ekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pa winaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hande aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaaso pitaęž‰ pao miaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 7 E pokao halaęž‰ hali ipikaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ otaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ da lumbu na likitaęž‰ homeke da paęž‰taęž‰ pa hao hataęž‰ ne ikali alekemanu kimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa napaęž‰peke.
\v 8 Kutupa ikitaęž‰ da yu maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ hatuku mea nemanu kimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa napaęž‰peke.
\v 9 Koto da yu paęž‰taęž‰ yeni haleme wandaęž‰hali wopu mea epeapaęž‰peke. Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki teke paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ opolo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lapaęž‰peke.
\v 10 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate da yu maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ na hatuku pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo potaęž‰ ninaęž‰ pua hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 11 Ikaęž‰ daoni tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ dokolotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ taĚ±laĚ±ęž‰laĚ±ęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kone koto tandelaęž‰neasomaęž‰pate doeki homeke hone wipee laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki teke siki paęž‰taęž‰ koto epeaęž‰me hone wotu wiaęž‰paęž‰peke lapaęž‰peke.
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ alome. Hande pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Sodomo halo paęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hande daoni paęž‰taęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao ankulao halieke alome leekeme.
\s1 Hone na tulaemeke daonimanu
\r (Maęž‰tiu 11ęž‰20-24)
\p 
\v 13 Aęž‰taęž‰ tieke Kotaasini daonio. Aęž‰taęž‰ tieke Betesaida daonio. IĚ±maęž‰ mo ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ na handeke haumanu paeyao aęž‰ndaęž‰ mo hande daoni yaapo Taiya Saidoni paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ puki lekelemekaęž‰taęž‰me laa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handenaęž‰taęž‰ busaęž‰ pitikimanu wepia yamaataęž‰ lankaęž‰ apolo kitulu pimime. IĚ±maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰
\v 14 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Taiya Saidoni yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo ipiliki Kotaasini Betesaida yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ kulu paęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao ankulao halieke.
\v 15 Kutupa Kapeneamio. Neketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ homeke oli ya nane mea aęž‰meiyalueke hone wipe. Neketaęž‰ oni ti to halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaalieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka pi kone opitaęž‰laęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ iki kiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ IĚ± kone kiaasaęž‰me. Kutupa make hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± kiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali kone kiaasaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Mo 72 haliweki paa laęž‰kaęž‰la epemekeeki
\p 
\v 17 Mo hande 72 haliwekitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ paa opolo epemekeme. Tekehalio. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ biki laaso hataęž‰ teliolo hamono kone mo hoke temoko manumaęž‰ nikaęž‰ pi otaęž‰ opimime lemekeme.
\v 18 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Sadani oli ya nane yamaęž‰ ti tekele mandaęž‰naęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ lopeaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handoaęž‰me.
\v 19 Opuaęž‰pe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ketomanu make tei halimanu make daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ tombuamenaęž‰ make mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki hoke temokonaęž‰ honkopu paeyao lu tombuao bepolaminaęž‰taęž‰ ya bikinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ iki handeteke halieke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na hoeyaalieke.
\v 20 Koto paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ mo hoke temoko manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi opua piliaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pate ikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hepeni nane wape pea ulaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 11ęž‰25-27, 13ęž‰16-17)
\p 
\v 21 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ epeke taęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ tumbieketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Oli ya do kenke yaaponaęž‰ Tekehalio. IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ Taęž‰naęž‰e alome. Ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande hone wotu u tekele peleme wandaęž‰hali make mo sukulu wotu peleme wandaęž‰hali ameda paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰mbao winaęž‰ le hau manutaęž‰ pa mo panake wekiwandiki sunu paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰leke handa alome. Aowe Apaęž‰o. Koto ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone pieke yekeeki yaenaęž‰yeke pinaęž‰ aleme leekeme.
\v 22 Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao sikitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo Eiyeketaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hone na ulaęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ Atekemaęž‰ homeke hone ulaęž‰me. Kutupa Ateketaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hone na ulaęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ homeke hone ulaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo Eiyekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone piliaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ateke waleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ homeke Ateke hone wilimikie leekeme.
\v 23 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honumake siki hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneaaso alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeleme ale handolo peleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 24 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰maęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ potopede haliweki wopu make kini haliweki make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeleme alemanu handuluekemaęž‰ taapemekepate handaęž‰peke na yaalo make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opitelemeeki opuluekemaęž‰ pimikipate opuaęž‰peke anaęž‰ na piekeme leekeme.
\s1 Epeke Sametia halinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ leekeeki
\p 
\v 25 Mo Lo Pi walo hayeke hali homekemaęž‰ Yesu tamuluekemaęž‰ la handolo alotaęž‰ Disao. Deto halaęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰ eki pionope laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 26 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo hande Baibolo pi manumaęž‰taęž‰ eki alaęž‰pe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ekipa hone wilipe leekeme.
\v 27 Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Baibolomaęž‰ dupa laęž‰laęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ puki paeyaomaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ temoko paeyaomaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ honkopu paeyaomaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ hone paeyaomaęž‰ make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo hapeke laęž‰laęž‰me laa make Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homele tupaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homo hapeke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 28 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ ale pitaęž‰ epeke aleme. Koto ale ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki milipikie laa leekeme.
\v 29 Koto leekepate hande Lo Pi walo hayeke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki kone epeaaluekemaęž‰ Yesu paa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Koto hali maęž‰ndaęž‰e laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ epipe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 30 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Diutuseleme da minaęž‰paęž‰lao oni Dietiko da nane pulu haenaęž‰ mo potaęž‰naęž‰ mandane pake naleme haliwekimaęž‰ mina ipikaęž‰ dau titipilaęž‰ minaęž‰ bepie yombua bao homuluekemaęž‰ taapolo pitinaęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 31 Kutupa koto natenaęž‰ kone mo yeni peao hayeke hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ koto potaęž‰naęž‰ peekepate hande yombua bao winaęž‰ lemeke some handeekepate pa winaęž‰ kone pakaęž‰lao potaęž‰ teaęž‰ nane peekeme.
\v 32 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Lipae tapake hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ peekepate mo hande yombua bao winaęž‰ lemeke hali pua handa kone pao pakaęž‰lao potaęž‰ teaęž‰naęž‰ peekeme.
\v 33 Pate Sametia hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ koto potaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ mo hali hando haotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 34 Kutupa mo hali wieke alenaęž‰ puaataęž‰ mo limiki ale ninaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ honku make waini ikali make holaotaęž‰ banisimaęž‰ tonkawayekeme. Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ hande sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ donki maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ hoki manda mea wiaataęž‰ hatuku pua hande kimisu haliwekimaęž‰ hamba polu haemeke da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ opolo puaataęž‰ koto da paęž‰taęž‰ mo hali handeteke hayekeme.
\v 35 Kutupa da kelepeeketaęž‰ mo Sametia halimaęž‰ hande da teke hali paęž‰taęž‰ 2 kina halaa alotaęž‰ Do hali wotu handeteke hapeke. IĚ± doane laęž‰kaęž‰la ipuluaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hali handeteke halenaęž‰ kitolo 2 kina anaęž‰ na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao aęž‰pa kulueke leekeme.
\v 36 Koto laa Yesumaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi paeyaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do tepo hali alomaęž‰pate mo pake nalaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ limiki some teke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ epimaęž‰ puki haleaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 37 Hande Lo Pi walo hayeke halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Hande aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeeke halie laa leekeme. Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ make kutu piki hau pu hapeke laa leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Mada Meti yaapo handolo peekeeki
\p 
\v 38 Yesutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ da yu siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemekeme. Koto da yu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Mada. Koto wandaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 39 Mada ipikaęž‰ hakepiki homeke Meti hayekeme. Metimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ anke lopao pitieke alenaęž‰ aęž‰pa pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi waleekeeki opu pitiekeme.
\v 40 Kutu piekepate Madataęž‰ ne aneke hapu wamo pieke ekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone kaęž‰ndaęž‰ wotu pieke aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Yaka asimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo emanu paeyao yaka honumake piono alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hone na witelepe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ mulu epenaęž‰ lae leekeme.
\v 41 Koto leeke Tekehalimaęž‰ Madanaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Madao. Madao. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wotu paęž‰taęž‰ hone u taapo make hone kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homelepate
\v 42 pa otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke hau homeke homeke na peleme. Metimaęž‰taęž‰ hone wia otaęž‰ hau maęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ pendilao meaęž‰peke na yaęž‰lieke leekeme.
\c 11
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ waleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 6ęž‰9-13, 7ęž‰7-11)
\p 
\v 1 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua yeni pu pitiekeme. Yeni pu paeyaeyeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio ambaęž‰ hande Dionimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki yeni pinaęž‰yeke waleeke tupaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ walaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 2 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ walolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ dupa piaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\q1 Apaęž‰o. Nakaęž‰ yako piki bikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ manda wia haenaęž‰e.
\q1 Nakaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Haleeki do ane opolo epenaęž‰e.
\q1 
\v 3 Nikaęž‰ ame nolo polomaęž‰ netaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kiaęž‰peke.
\q1 
\v 4 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pimieki nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa paeyaasomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰
\q1 nikaęž‰ hoke hau pumaęž‰eki make nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ pa paeyawapeke.
\q1 Kaęž‰ndaęž‰ piki la handaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ niki na hatuku aęž‰paęž‰peke laa lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ butaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yankekenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Kameo. Palaowa punka tepo taęž‰kaęž‰li kie.
\v 6 Ya yankeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ potaęž‰ pomulu yapuluekemaęž‰ ame do timba ya da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa pilaęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ halaęž‰peke ne diaęž‰yaęž‰leke handa loaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ kie laa lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 7 kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yankekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ± kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homake. Yaka potaęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ lokaęž‰ hao yaka weki wandiki ameĚ±leĚ± ambaęž‰ u paęž‰elomaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ honke ale alaęž‰taęž‰ ekipa tiao mea kionope laa leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 8 kotaęž‰ eki pilipikipe. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do pi alome. Mo da teke halimaęž‰ neketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke halenaęž‰ kone mo hande palaowa kuluekemaęž‰ na tialo paęž‰laęž‰patetaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke honke wotu lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ opua tiao nakaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu anaęž‰naęž‰ mea kilieke alome.
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi alome. Honke lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ kilieke. Weikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ wilipikie. Kilikili laekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ lombawalieke.
\v 10 Do ekinaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me. Honke laęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somemaęž‰ milieke. Kutaa make maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ weiyaęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ wilieke. Epimaęž‰ potaęž‰ liaęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo potaęž‰taęž‰ koto some paęž‰taęž‰ lombawalieke.
\v 11 Do pitaęž‰ weki wandiki halaęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Ikaęž‰ wekimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰peli teekeeki honke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoke keto mea halimikipe.
\v 12 O ba hapeke honke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ tei hali mea halimikipe.
\v 13 Ikitaęž‰ hoke haliweki halemepate kone ikaęž‰ weki wandiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ epeke epeke alemanu halo halememe. Koto hau otaęž‰ lombei peaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ oli ya nane halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi honke aleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ halieke laa leekeme.
\s1 Yesu pitaęž‰ Bielisibulu yaapo
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰22-30, Maka 3ęž‰20-27)
\p 
\v 14 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ pi na leke hoke temoko pitiki hali hayeke Yesumaęž‰ mo hoke temoko tolu lieke handa mo halimaęž‰ pi lombo leekeme. Kutu pieke handa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ tolaęž‰tia pomimikipate
\v 15 mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande hoke temoko manunaęž‰ you hali Bielisibulunaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki mea hoke temokomanu tolu litaęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 16 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu tamuluekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hepeni nanemaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ patehau maęž‰ndaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handomono pie lemekeme.
\v 17 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone teke ambaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiataęž‰ dupa leekeme. Kapomani homekenaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone tekilipaęž‰ alu alu pea aęž‰ndaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hande tapake au leleme ekitaęž‰ koto kone paelieke. Kutupa tapakesiki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone tekilipaęž‰ alu alu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto tapake sikinaęž‰ hao peliaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ hoelieke.
\v 18 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Sadaninaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ haleme tapakemaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ lo tekilipaęž‰ alu alu pea ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone aęž‰ndaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ekipa hao peliaęž‰tiki pu halimikipe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Bielisibulumaęž‰ IĚ± honkopu kitaęž‰leke handa hoke temokomanu tolu litaęž‰laęž‰me laa alemeeki
\v 19 otaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ ekipa hoke temoko tolu lu halemepe. Koto haliwekinaęž‰ piteleme haumaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ hau telipilimikie.
\v 20 Diaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ honkopu homekemaęž‰ mo hoke temoko tolu lu halome. Kutu pu halo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki teke paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ peneme yao walaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 21 Honkopu hake hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu tiki tiki yao wia hataęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ da handeteke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ pa wilieke.
\v 22 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate otaęž‰ honkopu wopu hake hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ koto da teke hali yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea mo da teke hali lu bepolaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ alemanu paeyao mea pelieke. Kutupa mo pake miaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ telipilieke.
\p 
\v 23 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ yaka yankeke na haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ yaka sipisipi mombaęž‰laaso hano IĚ± na tambaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ panane tolu litaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Hoke temoko paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰43-45)
\p 
\v 24 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ hoke temoko maęž‰ndaęž‰ hama opolu bao yapeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hapulaęž‰ alenaęž‰ pomu lopolo hataęž‰ hoto pitaęž‰peke da pandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ weitaęž‰laęž‰me. Hoto pitaęž‰peke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hoke temokomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Yaka hande minaęž‰paęž‰lao epoaęž‰ da nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la polueke laa
\v 25 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la pua mo da aęž‰pa handiliaęž‰pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hake wamo pea bao epeke tupaęž‰ haliaęž‰eki handilieke.
\v 26 Koto paęž‰leketaęž‰ mo hoke temoko pua pa mandane watake hataęž‰ hoke temokomanu paeyao hatuku milieke. Koto hoke temoko manunaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo ipiki make lu ankulalimikie. Iki paeyao mandake paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa halimikie. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo halitaęž‰ ambaęž‰taęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ hao peliaęž‰pate ametaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ hao pelieke laa leekeme.
\s1 Otaęž‰ epeke taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 27 Yesumaęž‰ koto pi lo paeyeketaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ pitieke wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neke maęž‰ndaęž‰laęž‰ make andu kaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 28 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opua pu haleme wandaęž‰hali ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wotu homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ honke lemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰38-42)
\p 
\v 29 Wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Yesu aęž‰pa mombaęž‰la hopaęž‰liao haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ame do natenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hoke wandaęž‰hali halememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo na handeke patehau maęž‰ndaęž‰ handuluekemaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ honke aleme patetaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰siki make na walo polopate mo hande Dionamaęž‰ patehau piekeeki homeke handilimikie.
\v 30 Mo hande potopede hali Dionamaęž‰ Ninipa wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ patehau pieke tupaęž‰ kone mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ make ame wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ patehau pilieke.
\v 31 Mo hande pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Siba da yu handeteke halaęž‰ kuini wandaęž‰maęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ ame do natenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau manunaęž‰ maĚ±leke lilieke. Ekipeke mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kini hali Solomononaęž‰ epeke hone wotu u tekelepea walaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu opuluekemaęž‰ yeke mo kenke honiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane hao epeekeme. Kutu piekepate IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Ametaęž‰ Solomono ankulalaęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 32 Mo hande pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Ninipa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haunaęž‰ maĚ±leke lilimikie. Ekipeke. Dionamaęž‰ pi waleeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hoke haumanu hoki walemekeme. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Ametaęž‰ Diona ankulalaęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Lokenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 5ęž‰15, 6ęž‰22-23)
\p 
\v 33 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ olaęž‰pake kaęž‰waataęž‰ na aęž‰mbao u halaęž‰ o mo disi kawaso tieke oto paęž‰taęž‰ na wilieke. Koto hau na pikitaęž‰ mo da paęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali aęž‰pa hondaęž‰ pambaęž‰tiki pitolo handenaęž‰ mo lamepa u halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ u halaęž‰me.
\v 34 Nakaęž‰ leketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ olaęž‰pakee. Nakaęž‰ leke aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ loke paeyaotaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±maęž‰ tumbilieke. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate nakaęž‰ leke aęž‰ndaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ loke paeyaotaęž‰ timbaęž‰laęž‰ pambilieke.
\v 35 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ timbaęž‰ na laęž‰naęž‰ leketaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu handeteke hapeke
\v 36 Kutupa nakaęž‰ loke paeyao aęž‰ndaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±maęž‰ tumba hataęž‰ pa timbaęž‰ timbaęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ olaęž‰pake paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ nakaęž‰ loke paeyao paĚ±aĚ± pu kimalieke leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ tapake yaaponaęž‰ haumanu lo kelaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 23ęž‰1-36, Maka 12ęž‰38-40)
\p 
\v 37 Yesumaęž‰ pimanu lo paeyeketaęž‰ Paęž‰tisi hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ne nolo panaęž‰e leeke handa ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua ne nolueke alo pitiekeme.
\v 38 Mo hande Paęž‰tisi halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ne noluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki ambaęž‰la na tandepeekeeki hando haotaęž‰ pututumaęž‰ homa tolaęž‰tia pomiekeme.
\v 39 Kutu piekeeki handaataęž‰ mo Teke Halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kapo make kawaso manutaęž‰ manda homeke tandepo halemepate tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pasaęž‰tei pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau make hoke hoke hau paeyaomaęž‰ iki tumba halememe.
\v 40 Ikitaęž‰ hone na wiki haliwekio. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hama nane waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ tukiki nane make na waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pe.
\v 41 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kapo make kawasomanu paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ mo nate hali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pa halaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu piki hau aęž‰ndaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki paeyao otaęž‰ hake wotu pilieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 42 Paęž‰tisi haliwekio. Ikaęž‰ hoke yenki tiekenaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hande enaęž‰ halaęž‰ ale tekiaęž‰ o totopo piki tanimaęž‰ handeke ale sunutaęž‰ kiki yaapo telipataęž‰ putupa homeke sikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halo halemepate mo Kodaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ puki halaęž‰pekeeki make epeke tikitiki piki hau manutaęž‰ hone yonkaęž‰lalememe. Dupiki hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ mo mandaneeki make na minaęž‰paęž‰lapeke.
\p 
\v 43 Paęž‰tisi haliwekio ikaęž‰ hoke yenki tiekenaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ oni yeni pu halaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mo you haliwekinaęž‰ wialaęž‰ sea manunaęž‰ pituluekemaęž‰ hone wotu u haleme make oni makedi hama haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ biki miniliaaso Epeke dakaęž‰laęž‰paasoęž‰e laęž‰tiki pinaęž‰ hone wopu u halememe.
\p 
\v 44 Ikaęž‰ hoke yenki tiekenaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo patehau na paęž‰laęž‰ hali lapaęž‰maęž‰ handeke nono pelemeke handa tumbao pomu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ lapaęž‰maęž‰ handelememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 45 Koto leeke mo Lo Pi walo haemeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Disao. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ kutupiki pi ale ekimaęž‰taęž‰ niki mandaęž‰ meake nono piteleme leekeme.
\v 46 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Lo Pi walo haleme haliwekio iki make ikaęž‰ hoke yenki tiekenaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoki mandataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ tiaęž‰peke na yeke kaęž‰ndaęž‰ piki alemanu mea tiao halemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiki maĚ±leke kone tindipao na tambaęž‰ mea tialimikie.
\p 
\v 47 Ikaęž‰ hoke yenki tiekenaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande potopede haliwekinaęž‰ toko ulaęž‰ apaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ wamo pea wiao halememe. Pate koto potopede haliwekitaęž‰ hande ikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei tonumaęž‰ kone liaęž‰tiki pimiki haliwekie.
\v 48 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰meimaęž‰ pimiki ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halomaęž‰me alememe. Pa ekipeke ikaęž‰ apaęž‰meimaęž‰taęž‰ mo potopede haliweki pa lu pitaemeke handa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ndaęž‰ manutaęž‰ wamo peao halememe.
\p 
\v 49 Doeki tekenaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ epeke hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do laęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka potopede haliweki make pi mea pomuao haleme haliweki tapaalo polopate mandanetaęž‰ lu baalimiki make mandanetaęž‰ tanda tanda wopu halimikie laa laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 50 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande do ya yu kini pea aęž‰pa ame do limiki potopede haliweki paeyao limiki ekinaęž‰ hoke yenkitaęž‰ ame do haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ milimikie.
\v 51 Mo hande Eipolo limikieki kini pea aęž‰pa mo hande oloda pitaęž‰ yako piki da yaapo tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰mbolo hataęž‰ limiki hali Sekataiya alome. Aowe. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ loaęž‰maęž‰ ame do wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ koto limikieki paeyaonaęž‰ hoke yenki milimikie.
\v 52 Mo Lo Pi walo haleme haliweki ikaęž‰ hoke yenki tiekenaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hone wotu miaęž‰peke da potaęž‰naęž‰ kitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wia halemepate konetaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone na hondaęž‰ pambeketaęž‰ mo hondaęž‰ pambuluekemaęž‰ taapeleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pu halememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 53 Yesumaęž‰ koto da minaęž‰paęž‰lao peeke nanetaęž‰ mo Lo Pi walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke tetopiki tupaęž‰ kitaaso hataęž‰ ane mone alenaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki wotu halemekeme.
\v 54 Kutu pimiki hautaęž‰ Yesu honaęž‰maĚ±oĚ± tamuluekemaęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ piki pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ minuluaęž‰ patemaęž‰ lemekeme.
\c 12
\s1 Makeaaso haunaęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 10ęž‰26-27)
\p 
\v 1 Wandaęž‰hali pisetekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone lu tumbapeke nono pea mombololo haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekinaęž‰ palaowa pombeiyaasaęž‰ ale yisiti wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Doeki alo ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yayapiki makeaaso haunaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 2 Pankaęž‰ wilimi ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ pa peneme yaalieke. Kutupa mo aęž‰mbao aleme pimanu paeyaotaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ peneme yaalieke.
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo timba aęž‰mbao leleme pi manutaęž‰ paa natenaęž‰ opinaęž‰ lelimikie. Kutupa potaęž‰ pokaęž‰laęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ haleke paęž‰taęž‰ tome pambele pitaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ opinaęž‰ yeke da holu manda ninaęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ pi anekemaęž‰ lelimikie.
\s1 Epi paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe
\r (Maęž‰tiu 10ęž‰28-31)
\p 
\v 4 Ya yankeke tonuo. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alomaęž‰ Mo ikaęž‰ manda loke lu homaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wetepe nane hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 5 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ liaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ temokotaęž‰ oni ti to halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ baapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ wele paęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ loaęž‰maęž‰ Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke aleo.
\p 
\v 6 Mo hande wesomaęž‰ handeke basunu yunki hataęž‰ 20 toeamaęž‰ hambo halemeke yekea. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto wesomaęž‰ handeke ba sikitaęž‰ homeke kone hone na yonkaęž‰lalaęž‰me.
\v 7 Koto tupaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ you itiki paeyao make ambaęž‰ yataęž‰paęž‰ taęž‰pao anaęž‰ lao ulaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homo hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ tombotaęž‰ koto hosiki ba sunu wopunaęž‰ yenki otaęž‰ lombei paęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ biki peneme yaasaęž‰eki make hoki walaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo
\r (Maęž‰tiu 10ęž‰32-33, 12ęž‰32, 10ęž‰19-20)
\p 
\v 8 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ peneme yaaso hataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ halie leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolo manunaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ make homeke hau kone pilieke.
\v 9 Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke pototonaęž‰ hataęž‰ yaka biki na leke kiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolo manunaęž‰ leke pototonaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki make na leke kiaalieke.
\p 
\v 10 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pimanu leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto ekitaęž‰ pa paeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi kitake hoke pimanu leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na paeyawalieke.
\p 
\v 11 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ iki pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hotu haleme da paęž‰taęž‰manu make o mo kapomani haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make o handeteke haleme haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ eki pi loluaęž‰pe o ekipa ya kone tambaęž‰ miki pi loluaęž‰pe laa kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homo taapaęž‰peke
\v 12 Pa ekipeke. Mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰taęž‰ koto nate leke sikinaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ lolo peleme pi manutaęž‰ walekenaęž‰ walieke.
\s1 Hone na wiki hamoko halinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 13 Wandaęž‰hali mombaęž‰la haemeke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke hali homekemaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Disao. Yaka kamemaęž‰ dikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ anke teketaęž‰ yakaeki telipa kinaęž‰ lawae leekeme.
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Someo. Ipilikaęž‰ alemanu telipaano make ipilikaęž‰ pi tikitiki yawaanotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epimaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 15 Koto laa Yesumaęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Hande pasaęž‰tei hau taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pikieki aęž‰paapaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone wopu handeteke hataęž‰ leke leke lo hapaęž‰peke. Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ hamoko tieke ekipa haenaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wia haleme alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Koto laa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi dupa leekeme. Ambaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo hamoko hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ e paęž‰taęž‰ ne napekemanu wotu wiekeme.
\v 17 Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Mo hande ne napekemanu pokaęž‰ mepi pea wiaęž‰peke alenaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ eki puluepe laa hone wiekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Dupulueke. Yaka ne napekemanu u halaęž‰ damanu londaęž‰la kutupa da tieke tiekemanu aęž‰eyaataęž‰ mo ne napekemanu make yaka mandane alemanu paeyao make koto da paęž‰taęž‰manu mu ulueke laataęž‰
\v 19 kotaęž‰ ya kone dupa lolueke. Nakaęž‰taęž‰ yolee. Nakaęž‰ wia hale ale manutaęž‰ bapi wotu kone anaęž‰naęž‰ wilieke laa Ametaęž‰ pa pitu hataęž‰ ne ikali nalo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo hapeke lolueke leekepate
\v 20 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hone na wiki halio. Ame do timba kone nakaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki pao yokulueke. Kutu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰eki laa wia hale ale manutaęž‰ epimaęž‰ miliaęž‰pe laa leekeme.
\v 21 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ pi paeyaaso alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ yakaeki homekee laa alemanu wopu mu mombaęž‰laęž‰tiki pitaęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰taęž‰ pa natehali halaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ dupiki some aęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande titinaęž‰ loaęž‰ haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ opolo ipilieke leekeme.
\s1 Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone ti lao haasaęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 6ęž‰25-34)
\p 
\v 22 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do alo ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki pa hapeke ekinaęž‰ nemanu make lokenaęž‰ yamaęž‰peke alemanu koto alemanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homo hapaęž‰peke.
\v 23 Pa ekipeke. Daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ne otaęž‰ lombei paęž‰laęž‰ make mo lokemaęž‰taęž‰ dau make otaęž‰ lombei pu paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 24 Ba manunaęž‰ hau handaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ e wae alemanu na nokopataęž‰ na mondu no halememe. Ikaęž‰ sidowa o ne amu pu u haleme da maęž‰ndaęž‰ na halaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taa halo halaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ba manutaęž‰ taa lu ankulalemetaa.
\v 25 Iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone wopu witaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰ nate leke manutaęž‰ mu moneao ulu puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe.
\v 26 Kotaęž‰ koto hosiki ale siki kone na peaęž‰peke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa ekipeke mo mandane ale paęž‰taęž‰ manutaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homo halemepe.
\p 
\v 27 Mo hapeke paęž‰taęž‰manu pa opaęž‰laęž‰ moma sununaęž‰ opaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ e na poko make akaęž‰manu na tombulu yamo halememe. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Kini Solomonomaęž‰taęž‰ hamoko alemanu wotu wiekepate kone do moma manunaęž‰ loke hake dau epeke epeke ekimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na wia hayekeme.
\v 28 Mo ame homeke opa haenaęž‰ laa beliataęž‰ tunkula hapuao tinaęž‰ yankaęž‰peke yeke ambu manunaęž‰ au kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ lawao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pei kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaaseme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hodiki ale siki yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Koto alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kutu pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki make dau otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kone yamatiki pilieke.
\v 29 Kutu piliekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Ya nolo polo ne ikali hanemaęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ muluaęž‰pe laa kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homo hapaęž‰peke.
\v 30 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki na opeleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao koto alemanu hone wopu u halememe. Pate ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto alemanu nate paeyao ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mu halo peleme ekitaęž‰ hone ulaęž‰me.
\v 31 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki ambaęž‰la weiyu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo koto ale manutaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao ku halieke.
\s1 Hepeni nane hamoko hapekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 6ęž‰19-21)
\p 
\v 32 Yaka sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ tapake sikio. Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ oli hande Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halaęž‰me.
\v 33 Ikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ tapao mani meaataęž‰ mo natehali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa na kukutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ mani pausa meaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hamoko ale manutaęž‰ oli ya nane na paeyaęž‰niake pa wia halo pelemeeki homeke amu pu hapaęž‰peke. Ekipeke koto nanetaęž‰ mo pake no haleme haliwekimaęž‰ make bisapu inkikimaęž‰ make na hoeyaalimikie.
\v 34 Ikaęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ epeke epeke alemanu u haleme ale paęž‰taęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ u pelia halimikie.
\s1 Lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ pea e pokaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 35-36 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki tupaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ you halitaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰ panake mea ne pambaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ paęž‰leke handaa paa epenaęž‰ yu wia haleme tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu wotu soto laęž‰tia haenaęž‰ yama ikaęž‰ olaęž‰pakemanu kaęž‰watia hataęž‰taęž‰ anemone ipiliaęž‰ ekimanu lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ hao hapaęž‰peke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo you halimaęž‰ aęž‰pa potaęž‰ liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto kone lombilimikie.
\v 37 Kutupa mo you hali paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa mo ipikaęž‰ e pokaaseme hali wekitaęž‰ uĚ± na polu pitiki aęž‰ndaęž‰ pa ipiki yu wia pilimieki aęž‰pa handeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halimikie. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alomaęž‰ Mo haliwekimaęž‰ koto hau pimiki yeke handaa ikaęž‰ you halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ manda akaęž‰ hola wiaataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ Ne no halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ aęž‰pa pitaęž‰pe laa ne panaęž‰ pu kilieke.
\v 38 Kutupa make mo you halitaęž‰ butaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ o hoki nane kone epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tiki tiki yao ipiki yu wia pilimieki handeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halimikie.
\v 39 Kutupa make doeki hone wotu wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Mo da teke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo pake nalaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki ambaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ oni ipikaęž‰ da yambaęž‰la na yapenaęž‰ lelieke.
\v 40 Iki make otaęž‰ tikitiki yao hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Mo hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ ipilieke hone na witolo halimi di ninaęž‰ ipilieke laa loaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Mo epeke e pokaasaęž‰ hali pitaęž‰ hoke e pokaasaęž‰ hali yaapo
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰45-51)
\p 
\v 41 Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do ale onkolumaęž‰ pitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke alepe o mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ alepe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 42 Koto leeke mo Tekehalimaęž‰ Pidanaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kimaęž‰ na homeke make otaęž‰ epeke hone wotu u lenkene pu wia e poko haliaęž‰ halitaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Koto halitaęž‰ mo da teke halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da handeteke haenaęž‰yeke make mo ipikaęž‰ mandane e pokao haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne no haleme di miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne nenaęž‰ teli teli peao halieke leekeme.
\v 43 Ipikaęž‰ you hali paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ e pokao halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ mo hande emanu otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ pitolo pitiliaęž‰eki aęž‰pa handaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto e pokao halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halieke.
\v 44 Otaęž‰ alome. Mo you halimaęž‰taęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao handeteke haenaęž‰ laęž‰lieke.
\v 45 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate mo e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Yaka you sometaęž‰ di hokulu hokulu pitolo hataęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na ipulaęž‰me laa mo mandane e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ pitaęž‰ hali yaapo kini pea hali lu yombitolo hataęž‰ ikali ne nalo keaaso hataęž‰
\v 46 ipikaęž‰ you halitaęž‰ Do natenaęž‰ ipilieke hone na witolo haliaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ koto kone opolo ipilieke. Aęž‰paataęž‰ mo e pokaasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ homenaęž‰ liaataęž‰ pa pi na opiki wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± haenaęž‰ laęž‰lieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 47 Mo e pokaasaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ peaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰ haumanu hone wia ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone anaęž‰ lao na piki ipikaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ peaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰ haumanu na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ mo you halimaęž‰ dopitamaęž‰ podelaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ tanda tieke nelieke.
\v 48 Pate e pokaasaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki hone na witolo kone tanda napekeeki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ aeĚ±yaĚ±piki dopitamaęž‰ hosiki podelaęž‰ milieke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mandane alemanu handeteke haenaęž‰ yeke anekemaęž‰ haleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ anekemaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wilieke. Koto tupaęž‰ kone hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ wopu handeteke haenaęž‰ yeke haleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ankulao anekemaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wilieke leekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ tapake tekili paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teke
\r (Maęž‰tiu 10ęž‰34-36)
\p 
\v 49 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± epolo ekitaęž‰ ti ulekemaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ mo yaaluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰pate ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone talo hapeke alee.
\v 50 IĚ±taęž‰ bapitaisi peaęž‰peke hau homeke mulueke hone ulupate pa aĚ±iĚ± na pu paeyaaso ekinaęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka weleke pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke minolome.
\v 51 Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ piteleme ekimanu homu pealo epoaęž‰me hone wi witelemepe. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tapake tekili pawaluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰me.
\v 52 Ame do hao kini peaataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ make tapakesiki yunki hataęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone tekilipa tepomaęž‰taęž‰ yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ litolo hataęž‰ yaapo sikimaęž‰taęž‰ pa tepo paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ liaęž‰tiki pu halimikie leekeme.
\v 53 Ateke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ pa eiyeke ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ lualu peaataęž‰ eiyeke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ ateke tonu ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ lualu pilimikie. Inkiki tonumaęž‰taęž‰ waneke tonu ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ lualu peaataęž‰ waneke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ inkiki tonu ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ lualu pilimikie. Halikinaęž‰ inkiki tonumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aeyaęž‰ tonu ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ lualu peaataęž‰ mo aeyeke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ halikinaęž‰ inkiki tonu ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ lualu pilimikie leekeme.
\s1 Wetepenaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 16ęž‰2-3)
\p 
\v 54 Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ oni nate pambaęž‰laęž‰ nane yamaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ koa handolotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Lako ipilieke lo halemeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ ipu halaęž‰me.
\v 55 Kutupa oni kaęž‰waęž‰naęž‰ yu nanemaęž‰ tilao po ipulaęž‰eki handolotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto kone alotaęž‰ Nate tieke talo hataęž‰ titipu tieke pilieke lo halemeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ titipu tieke pu halaęž‰me.
\v 56 Makeaasaęž‰ hau pu haleme haliwekio. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do ya yu nane pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu handolo hataęž‰ dupilieke aleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yao halaęž‰pate pa ekipeke ame do natenaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ hau manunaęž‰ teketaęž‰ na handaęž‰ witolo pimipe leekeme.
\s1 Pi yokaalu peaamaęž‰naęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± tiki tiki yaasaęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 5ęž‰25-26)
\p 
\v 57 Ekipeke handaa ikaęž‰ kone mo epeke hau piaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ na teli pitolo pimipe.
\v 58 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ neketaęž‰ pi yokaalunaęž‰ hatuku poluekemaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na peke hataęž‰ kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰ tiki tiki yaaluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰peke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hau na pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ neketaęž‰ oli pi yokaalu pu halaęž‰ hali teke paęž‰taęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea puaataęž‰ pa koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo polisi haliwekinaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ mea halaataęž‰ neketaęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ mea pitalieke.
\v 59 Kutupa neke paęž‰taęž‰ Mo opisi hambaęž‰e leliaęž‰ tupaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na hambo paeyaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ pa pitaęž‰ pelia halipikie leekeme.
\c 13
\s1 Iki homiliminaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau hoki wala kiaape
\p 
\v 1 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke mandane haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mo Pailedimaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili mandane haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hotekemanu lia Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halolo haenaęž‰ kone lieke ekinaęž‰ pi la halemekeme.
\v 2 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo Kaęž‰lili haliweki paeyaotaęž‰ hoke hau pu halemepate ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande limiki haliwekimaęž‰ hoke hau otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao pimiki yeke handa liekeme hone witelemepe.
\v 3 Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Iki make ikaęž‰ piteleme hoke haumanu na kiaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki make mo hande Kaęž‰lili haliweki homemeke tupaęž‰ kone homilimikie.
\v 4 Kutupa make mo hande Sailoaęž‰me da paęž‰taęž‰ haliao aęž‰emeke da hokulu tieke lombolo hataęž‰ lu sesape pieke 18 wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki hone witelemepe. Mo hande damaęž‰ lieke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ pimiki hoke hau otaęž‰ lombei peake tupaęž‰ pimikieki peneme yaasaęž‰pe.
\v 5 Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Iki make ikaęž‰ piteleme hoke haumanu na kiaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto tapake homemeke tupaęž‰ kone homilimikie leekeme.
\s1 Nose timaęž‰ kiliki na aęž‰eyeke ekinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 6 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa leekeme. Ambaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e tukikinaęž‰taęž‰ nose ti maęž‰ndaęž‰ nokopeekeeki hayekeme. Mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo nose kiliki aęž‰elaęž‰ patemaęž‰ handolo endi pu hayekepate homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na aęž‰eyekeme.
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokao hayeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰e. Bapi tepo tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do nose tinaęž‰ kiliki aęž‰elaęž‰pe laa handolo endi pu halopate homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na aęž‰elaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ do hoke timaęž‰ mo epeke kenke pa hameke naataęž‰ paamaęž‰naęž‰ poko bae leekeme.
\v 8 Koto leekepate mo e pokaeyeke halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka tiekeo. Bapi homekenaęž‰ pa haenaęž‰ lae. IĚ±maęž‰ do ti teke hopaęž‰liao yu lia kao imanu lekeluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 9 Yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ mone mo bapinaęž‰ kiliki aęž‰eyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰pate na aęž‰eyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pao poko baenaęž‰ lolenaęž‰e laa leekeme.
\s1 Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ kone wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epeaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 10 Mo hoto pilaęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo pi hotu haemeke da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi walo hayekeme.
\v 11 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitieke wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pitiekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ kone mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ 18 bapinaęž‰ yeni mea hao hayeke ekimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ hoki hoi peaotaęž‰ tindipapeke na yeekeme.
\v 12 Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ hando hao wi laęž‰moneaso alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰o. Neketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yeni ta paetolo hataęž‰ neketaęž‰ walekenaęž‰ ta hale handaęž‰e.
\v 13 Koto laa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ loke manda wieke dinaęž‰ koto kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki tindi paeyekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea miniliaeyekeme.
\v 14 Kutu pieke handaa mo pi hotu haemeke da handeteke hayeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ kone epeaeyeke handa Yesu yaapo mineke pankeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ E pokaęž‰peke nate manutaęž‰ yunki mindiki hataęž‰ taamaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yenimanu epeaenaęž‰ hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto nate ninaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa do Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ diaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 15 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Makeaasaęž‰ hau pu haleme haliwekio. Iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondomaęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kao o donki maęž‰naęž‰ make mo hoĚ±lindaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea hama lombaęž‰ taęž‰pao ikali naęž‰naęž‰yeke mea pelimikie.
\v 16 Koto tupaęž‰ kone do Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰taęž‰ hoke temokomaęž‰ 18 bapinaęž‰ tonkao ulaęž‰ putaęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰taęž‰ na kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaenaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 17 Koto hombo peayeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliwekimaęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke haumanu piekeeki handolo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wotu homemekeme.
\s1 Masidadi waenaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰31-32, Maka 4ęž‰30-32)
\p 
\v 18 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ alekemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰pe laa mandaęž‰ meanope.
\v 19 Mo Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo (kiĚ±miĚ±leĚ±maęž‰ handeke) masidadi wae ale sikitaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mea ipikaęž‰ enaęž‰ tande leekeeki opaataęž‰ otaęž‰ aneke ti hombeleke hao paleke palekenaęž‰ ba titimaęž‰ dake hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Palaowa pombei yaasaęž‰ yisitinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰33)
\p 
\v 20 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ paa make lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ alekemaęž‰ mandaęž‰ mealuaęž‰pe.
\v 21 Dupa mandaęž‰ meanoe. Wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo palaowa pombei yaasaęž‰ yisitisiki mea palaowa nu homeke mea apaęž‰tao kawasonaęž‰ dakole dakole pealieke. Kutu piliaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ koto palaowa paeyao pombei ya halieke leekeme.
\s1 Dekepeke potaęž‰siki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 7ęž‰13-14,21-23)
\p 
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da nane opolo poluekemaęž‰ yeke handaa hosiki da sunu make daoni paęž‰taęž‰manu ambaęž‰la pominolo hataęž‰ pi walaęž‰tiki pomiekeme.
\v 23 Kutupieke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pa tepo tepo wandaęž‰hali homeke detenaęž‰ yeke peteliaęž‰pe laa leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰
\v 24 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo dekepeke potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambuluekemaęž‰ honkopu hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Wandaęž‰hali wotumaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambuluekemaęž‰ taapolo pelemepate hondaęž‰ pambolo puaęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰lieke.
\v 25 Mo da teke halimaęž‰taęž‰ tiao potaęž‰ pokilieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki hama hataęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ kake kilikili laaso alotaęž‰ Tiekeo. Niki epomono potaęž‰ lombaęž‰e lelimipate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ IĚ± na handolomaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ hanemaęž‰ epelemepe laa lelieke.
\v 26 Koto leliepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso dupa lelimikie. Nikitaęž‰ neke ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ne ikali nomaęž‰ hande make nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ da sunu paęž‰taęž‰ pimanu walaęž‰tiki pomime laa lelimikie.
\v 27 Koto lemekenaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa do tupaęž‰ lelieke. Ikitaęž‰ hane wandaęž‰halipaęž‰ IĚ± minaęž‰paęž‰lao pupaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halie lelieke.
\v 28 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke Dieikope make mo potopede haliweki paeyao make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ eki paęž‰taęž‰ halimieki handolo hataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ hama tolu liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ eĚ± tieke alo hataęž‰ kake lenkene lo halimikie.
\v 29 Wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo nate pambaęž‰laęž‰ nane make nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nane make mo nepoko yaapo nane make opolo endi peaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ ne pambaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ aęž‰pa pitilimikie.
\v 30 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ame do wetepenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali mandanetaęž‰ titinaęž‰ halimikie. Kutupa titinaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ halimikie leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme danaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 23ęž‰37-39)
\p 
\v 31 Koto dinaęž‰ kone mandane Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Kini Hetodimaęž‰ neke luekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰laęž‰me. Neketaęž‰ do da yu minaęž‰paęž‰lao otaęž‰ ame do kone puaęž‰peke lemekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Iki puataęž‰ koto hande tikene kika paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lapaęž‰peke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu tolu lia make yenimanu epeaasomaęž‰ laataęž‰ belia make kutupataęž‰ tuneketaęž‰ ya e paeyaalueke laa lapaęž‰peke.
\v 33 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ame belia tuneketaęž‰ ya potaęž‰naęž‰ pa yopu pitulueke. Pa ekipeke. Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ potopede halitaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰manu litaęž‰laęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pate pa Diutuseleme da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Diutuseleme Diutuselemeo. Aęž‰taęž‰ tiekee. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo potopede haliwekitaęž‰ liki hau ombu peaataęž‰ toopimaęž‰ lu homao haleme. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰ kokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ikiki sunu ipikaęž‰ popake itiki oto paęž‰taęž‰ mea mombaęž‰lao halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ kone nakaęž‰ wekiwandiki ya kikimaęž‰ hapisaęž‰ pu halopate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ kiao haleme.
\v 35 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ yeni pu haleme dataęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa taake halieke. IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi do la kitolo handaęž‰e. Ame do ane kini pea pua nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ biki mea ipulaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ Taęž‰naęž‰e pi loluekemaęž‰ tiki tiki yao aĚ±iĚ± na haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na handilimikie alome leekeme.
\c 14
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ yeni homeeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea epeaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande hoto pilaęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Paęž‰tisi haliwekinaęž‰ you hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ ne noluekemaęž‰ peekeme. Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ wopu handaake wimikime.
\v 2 Pa koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kiki anke pambeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ epeekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Kutu pieke Yesumaęž‰ mo hande Lo Pi walo haemeke haliweki make mo mandane Paęž‰tisi haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ hande Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ hoto pilaęž‰ nate ninaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mea epeamonotaęž‰ waleke ku halaęž‰pe o diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 4 Koto leekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ pi siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ make otaęž‰ na hondomu lemekeme. Kotaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande yeni hayeke hali mea epeao tapaeyekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo ikaęž‰ weki o maęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ oni naku paęž‰taęž‰ mo hoto pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰ kone lopa wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Mo hoto pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰e laa aĚ±iĚ± na kiki yolaęž‰ milimikipe leekeme.
\v 6 Koto leekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peapeketaęž‰ anaęž‰ na piekeme.
\s1 Ikaęž‰ kone homu pea hasaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 7 Mo hande wi leeke epemeke haliwekimaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ da pandaęž‰ handaa mu tia pomimikieki hando hao Yesumaęž‰ dupiki onkolumaęž‰ pi la haleekeme.
\v 8 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ wandaęž‰ panake mea ne pambolo hataęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ epoe pi aęž‰ndaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pua mo hande hamoko haliweki pitu halaęž‰ epeke alenaęž‰ ambaęž‰la na pua pitaęž‰peke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ neke lu ankulao halaęž‰ hamoko hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ make Epoe alo paęž‰laęž‰me laa loaęž‰me.
\v 9 Kutupa mo hande iki ipupaęž‰ leaęž‰ halimaęž‰ mo hali tieke epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Do hali pitinaęž‰ koto da pandaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao pue laa neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa lelieke. Koto leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ yaalaęž‰ tieke minolo hataęž‰ hoki nane pitulu pelipiki yeke loaęž‰me.
\v 10 Koto hau na pikitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ Ne nolo epoe pi aęž‰ndaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hoki nanemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pitaęž‰peke. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande neke wi leaęž‰ somemaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Yaka yankekeo. Do epeke alenaęž‰ aęž‰pa pitie lelieke. Kutu piki hau piliaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ minaęž‰lialieke leekeme.
\v 11 Ekipeke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ aneke hali au leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mininialieke. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone pandaęž‰ puniayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tieke au lalieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipiki wi leaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ natenaęž‰ o timba ne nolo epenaęž‰ yeke wi lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ yankeke sunu o nakaęž‰ kame tonu o nakaęž‰ tapake make nakaęž‰ hamoko yankeke tonu wi na lapeke. Ekipeke. Wetepe ninaęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ kone neke wi lelimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ paa koto anaęž‰naęž‰ kone milipikie.
\v 13 Kutu pulu pelepate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ne maęž‰ndaęž‰ pambekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ natehali wandaęž‰hali sunu paęž‰taęž‰ make dolaęž‰pake piki kiki anke hoelaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make leke holu piki wandaęž‰hali sunu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ipupe lapeke.
\v 14 Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone neke yenki kilieke. Ekipeke. Kutupiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenki kiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ pi opua peaęž‰tiki pimi wandaęž‰hali homa tialimi natenaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenki kilieke leekeme.
\s1 Ne tieke pambeeke ekinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ laa leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 22ęž‰1-10)
\p 
\v 15 Mo ne no pitimiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pitieke hali homekemaęž‰taęž‰ koto pi opua Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ne pambiliaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitulu paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilieke laa leekepate
\v 16 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ne tieke pambolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu epenaęž‰ wi laęž‰ mepi piekeme.
\v 17 Kutupa mo ne nolo pimiki nate teke paęž‰taęž‰ yeeke handaataęž‰ mo hande wi laęž‰ mepi pieke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali homekemaęž‰ lolo penaęž‰ tapaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao ambaęž‰ anaęž‰ lao ulumaęž‰maęž‰ ipupe laa lolo pue leekeme.
\v 18 Mo halimaęž‰ lolo peekepate haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ homeke homeke lo kiaemeke ekinaęž‰ tekemanu weitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ dupa lemekeme. Titinaęž‰ halimaęž‰ hande e pokaeyeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yaka hambolo kenke handolo polueke. Koto ekinaęž‰ pilisi IĚ±taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa lawaapeke leekeme.
\v 19 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hande e pokaeyeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ kao kiki yaapo hambolo ekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hau handuluekemaęž‰ yeke puluekemaęž‰ pilisi IĚ±taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa lawaapeke leekeme.
\v 20 Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ame do siki wandaęž‰ panake molo ekimaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa lawaapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande e pokaeyeke halimaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua hande haliwekimaęž‰ lemeke pi paeyao ipikaęž‰ teke hali paęž‰taęž‰ la haleekeme. Koto leeke opuaataęž‰ mo teke halimaęž‰ mineke tieke pankolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ AĚ±iĚ±ya puaataęž‰ mo daoninaęž‰ potaęž‰ tieke paęž‰taęž‰manu make hosiki potaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰manu make mo natehali wandaęž‰hali make kiki anke hoeke dolaęž‰pake wandaęž‰hali make leke holu piki wandaęž‰hali make ankemaęž‰ pomuaęž‰peke na yeke wandaęž‰hali make koto wandaęž‰hali paeyaosiki hatuku mea aęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 22 Kutupa mo e pokao hayeke halimaęž‰ kotoeki pea aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nakaęž‰ hande le ekitaęž‰ puaęž‰pate nakaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ waleke pa ulaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo teke halimaęž‰ hande e pokao hayeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Papate paęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰manu puaataęž‰ yaka da tumbinaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao handaęž‰ mea aęž‰pawapeke.
\v 24 Pa ekipeke. Ambaęž‰ hande titinaęž‰ wi loaęž‰ haliweki homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yaka ne aęž‰pa napenaęž‰ yeke handa loaęž‰me leekeme laa leekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo hali haluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ yopu hau diaęž‰me
\r (Maęž‰tiu 10ęž‰37-38)
\p 
\v 25 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± pulu haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneaso hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme.
\v 26 IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea ipuluekemaęž‰ ipilimi wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondomaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± pominolotaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ puki kuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ make wekiwandiki make ipikaęž‰ kame anaęž‰ tonu make ipiki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ kiaotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ puki tiekemaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutu piliaęž‰ sometaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 27 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti ipikaęž‰ kone na mea tia yaka hoki nane na teliaęž‰ mea ipu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ yaka disaipolo hali hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 28 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ oli ya nane aęž‰eyo aęž‰meiyake hokulu paęž‰laęž‰ da tieke aęž‰eyo paeyaaluekemaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ honemaęž‰ ambaęž‰lataęž‰ tumao toopi dupa baalueke o toopi anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pe laa yataęž‰pilieke.
\v 29 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kotoeki na piki pa ambaęž‰la aęž‰eyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo dataęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na paeyaake pa kaęž‰taęž‰manu homeke nokopaęž‰ wia pa kapaęž‰lalieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ moeki handolotaęž‰ mo some kitaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 30 Do halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da aęž‰eyaęž‰pate paeyaapeke anaęž‰ na pea piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lelimikie.
\p 
\v 31 Kini hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ 10 daoseni haliweki aęž‰ndaęž‰ mea kini hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ polo paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo kini hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ haliwekitaęž‰ 20 daoseni haliweki yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo titinaęž‰ kinimaęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ tumaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ Mo kini yaapotaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ anaęž‰ polopemaęž‰ hone wilieke.
\v 32 Ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ anaęž‰ na polome hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hande kini halitaęž‰ papate haenaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ kinki haliweki tapaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰ndaęž‰ pao polupanaęž‰ pi minalu pupanaęž‰e laa pi tapaalieke.
\p 
\v 33 Yesumaęž‰ aęž‰mbolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto tupaęž‰ kone iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ yaka hoki nane teliaęž‰ mea ipulueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ale paeyao minaęž‰paęž‰lao IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea ipilieke leekeme.
\s1 Hoelaęž‰ epi
\r (Maęž‰tiu 5ęž‰13, Maka 9ęž‰50)
\p 
\v 34 Epitaęž‰ epeke tendepiki ale yaęž‰laęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ tende paęž‰laęž‰eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ alu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo epinaęž‰ tende paa mea peapeke potaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wilieke.
\v 35 Kutupa koto hoelaęž‰ epimaęž‰taęž‰ mo e ninaęž‰ o mini ambuku bao haleme alenaęž‰ make na epeaalieke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ pa bao bao pu halememe. Katake lombaęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰taęž‰ do pimanu opinaęž‰e leekeme.
\c 15
\s1 Alu pieke sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Maęž‰tiu 18ęž‰12-14)
\p 
\v 1 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mo hande dakisi mani mu haemeke haliweki make mo hoke haliweki make paeyaomaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leeke pimanu opuluekemaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mombelemekepate
\v 2 hande Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ make mo hande Lo Pi walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make kotoeki handaataęž‰ pi la la pitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke haliweki handaęž‰ meaęž‰tiki pea ne kone homeke paęž‰taęž‰ netiki pitelememe laa lemeke handa
\v 3 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso onkolumaęž‰ dupa leekeme.
\v 4 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ titi 100 haliaęž‰pate homeke alu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa eki piliaęž‰pe. Mo pa halaęž‰ 99 sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ manutaęž‰ ambu nalo haenaęž‰ mo hande alupiaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ handaęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ weilu pelieke leekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa handaęž‰ wiataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ hande sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ hopulaęž‰ mea
\v 6 peiyokonaęž‰ tia da pelieke. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ yankeke titi make ipikaęž‰ da wandaęž‰hali make paeyao ipupe laa wi alotaęž‰ Hande alupiaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ homeketaęž‰ handaęž‰ uaęž‰maęž‰ niki paeyaomaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homomanaęž‰e laa lelieke.
\v 7 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Koto tupaęž‰ kone oli hepeni nanetaęž‰ pa mandane 99 hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na laęž‰kaęž‰lapeke epeke tupaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ make homelemepate pa mo hoke hali homekemaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ oli hepeni nanetaęž‰ otaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homilimikie laa leekeme.
\s1 Alu pieke mani toopi kiliki homeke
\p 
\v 8 Kutupa make wandaęž‰ homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ silipa mani kiki yaapo wia haliaęž‰pate homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ alu paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ eki piliepe laa leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ ulueke alo olaęž‰pake kaęž‰wataęž‰ sisimei mea da pandaęž‰ kila bao weilieke.
\v 9 Kutupa hande mani siki handaęž‰ wiataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke make ipikaęž‰ da wandaęž‰hali make paeyao ipupe laa wi alotaęž‰ Hande alupiaęž‰ mani homeketaęž‰ handaęž‰ uaęž‰maęž‰ niki paeyaomaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homomanaęž‰ pipe laa lelieke. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi dupa alome.
\v 10 Koto tupaęž‰ kone hoke hali homekemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ oli Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolo manumaęž‰ koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homilimikie laa leekeme.
\s1 Alu pieke weki
\p 
\v 11 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± haemekepate
\v 12 mo wetepe wekimaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o IĚ±maęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke teke mulu polo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ ame do kone telipa kuelenaęž‰e laa honke leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ hande atekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ mo weki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ teli paeyekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa mo wetepe wekimaęž‰taęž‰ nate tepomanu haotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mieke ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambenaęž‰ laataęž‰ koto mani mea da minaęž‰paęž‰lao da yu maęž‰ndaęž‰ papate hayeke da nane peekeme. Koto nane puataęž‰ na tiaake haumanu pitolo hataęž‰
\v 14 ipikaęž‰ mani paeyao batiki pu hayekeme. Kotoeki pu paeyao haenaęž‰taęž‰ koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰ ki tieke epeeketaęž‰ mo wekitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na miniki pa hayekeme.
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo da nane hayeke hamoko hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ti lao haluekemaęž‰ peekepate mo hali tiekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e poko hayeke yu nane ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke halo penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa mo wekitaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰ nemeke pato ambuku manutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weleke haenaęž‰yeke noluekemaęž‰ taapeekepate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ne maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ na haleekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Kotoeki puoopu hao wetepenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone lumba witolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya apaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaaseme haliwekimaęž‰ ne anaęž‰naęž‰ nalo hataęž‰ mandaneeki pa winaęž‰ lo halemepate IĚ±taęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homoluekemaęž‰ taapolome hone wiekeme.
\v 18 IĚ± tiao puaataęž‰ yaka apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua dupa lolueke. Apaęž‰o. Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make neke paęž‰taęž‰ make hoke hau polome.
\v 19 Koto polo ekimaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki au lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokalo polo hali hano lolenaęž‰e laa lolueke hone wiekeme.
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo wekitaęž‰ koto da yu minaęž‰paęž‰lao atekenaęž‰ da poluekemaęž‰ peekeme. Da aĚ±iĚ± na opolo peeke potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰ kone atekemaęž‰ eiyeke epeekeeki handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya puaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki hopulaęž‰ mea nunu piekeme.
\v 21 Hande eiyekemaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make hoke hau polome. Koto polo ekimaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki au lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me leekepate
\v 22 pa atekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokao haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ wi la alotaęž‰ AĚ±iĚ± pua hande otaęž‰ epeke dau mea aęž‰pa yamaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ lini pitao ankedake make pambawapaęž‰peke.
\v 23 Kutupa hande imeke wotu piki kao ikiki mulu pua liataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ne pambomanaęž‰ loaęž‰me laataęž‰
\v 24 Pa ekipeke. Do yaka wekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ homeaęž‰pate kone ametaęž‰ paa tialaęž‰me. Alu piaęž‰pate kone ametaęž‰ handaęž‰ ulaęž‰me leekeme. Kutupa koto kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo ne pambaęž‰laęž‰eki kini pimikime.
\p 
\v 25 Koto hau paeyao pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ hande mupeke wekitaęž‰ e maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua paa da laęž‰kaęž‰la teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipulu haenaęž‰ hande taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ dupale emelimanu lemekeeki opiekeme.
\v 26 Kutupa mo e pokao hayeke hali homeke wi laęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ Motaęž‰ eki pitolo hataęž‰ alemepe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 27 Mo e pokao hayeke halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hande kame da laęž‰kaęž‰la epeeke handa nakaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki epeke tupaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la da aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ mo hande imeke wopu piki kao ikiki lia ne pambolo alaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 28 Hande mupeke wekimaęž‰ koto leekeeki opuataęž‰ mineke wopu pankolo hataęž‰ da puaęž‰peketaęž‰ kiaeyekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ hama opolu bao pua mo hande mupeke weki da tukiki nane epenaęž‰ yeke honke leekeme.
\v 29 Kutu piekepate mo hande wekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Opima. Bapi paeyao IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokao halaęž‰ hali leke hataęž‰ e pokaęž‰tiki pu hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na tunkuluaęž‰pate pa nanikosi homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ kone yaka yankeke titi ameĚ±leĚ± nomono yeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lia kime.
\v 30 Pate koto hande nakaęž‰ wekimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mani mea puataęž‰ mo hambo haleme wandiki titi paęž‰taęž‰ ba tapao pua paa da aęž‰paęž‰leke kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hande imeke wotu piki kao ikiki liaaleme leekeme.
\p 
\v 31-32 Koto leeke handa atekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka wekio. Neketaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ diki mandake hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ wia halo alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ ekie. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate nakaęž‰ kametaęž‰ ambaęž‰ homeaęž‰pate kone ametaęž‰ paa tiaalaęž‰me. Alupiaęž‰pate kone ametaęž‰ paa handaęž‰ ulume. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ne pambolo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ pumaęž‰me laa leekeme leekeme.
\c 16
\s1 Anaęž‰ lao hone wotu wiki hali
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme. Ambaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ hamoko hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa koto mieke halimaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ teke halinaęž‰ mani mea bepolaasaęž‰me laa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo teke hali paęž‰taęž‰ la haleekeme.
\v 2 Koto leeke mo teke halimaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ e pokao hayeke hali wi laęž‰mea alotaęž‰ Do nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pitelemaęž‰ aleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ alemepe laataęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ handeteke hawale alemanu paeyao sikitaęž‰ wapenaęž‰ mu wia yaka kikinaęž‰ u neae. Pa ekipeke. Ametaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ handeteke hawapeke na yaęž‰leke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ Yaka tiekemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ do paeyaaluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ eki puluaęž‰pe laataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo hombomanu awapeke make honkopu na halome. Kutupa make honke lapeketaęž‰ yaalaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pulu polo ekitaęž‰ hone witolome. Kutu pulu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka e paeliaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu ipupe lenaęž‰yeke yaka yankeke tonu halueke leekeme.
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ teke hali teke paęž‰taęž‰ tondiki wimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ wi laęž‰ mepi piekeme. Kutupa mo titinaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka teke hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ tondiki ekipu melepe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 6 IĚ±maęž‰ tondiki molo tupaęž‰taęž‰ honku kanake 100 molome laa leekeme. Koto leeketaęž‰ mo e handeteke hayeke halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ tondiki meleke wape pea ulaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰taęž‰ domaęž‰ pao honia pa 50 homeke wape lao wie leekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ tondikitaęž‰ ekipu melepe leeke handa mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Palaowa nu 100 molome laa leekeme. Koto leeke handa mo hande e handeteke hayeke halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ tondiki meleke wape pea ulaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰taęž‰ domaęž‰ pao honia pa 80 homeke wape lao wie leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Kutu pieke handa wetepenaęž‰ mo hande you hali tiekemaęž‰ mo hande e handeteke hayeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ hone wotu wiki halinaęž‰ hau tupaęž‰ pieke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki anekemaęž‰ minaęž‰liaeyekeme. Pa ekipeke. Do kenkenaęž‰ hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ e pokuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ hone wotu wia pokolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± piki hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ lu ankulao halememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ laęž‰tia pulu hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Do kenkenaęž‰ hamoko ale manumaęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali nakaęž‰ yankeke halenaęž‰ lenaęž‰ lapeke. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hamoko alemanu paeliaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ pa hao halaęž‰ da nane handaęž‰ milieke.
\p 
\v 10 Kutupa hali epimaęž‰ hosiki e sunu epeke tupaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ handeteke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ aneke emanu make epeke tupaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ handeteke halieke. Kutupa make hali epimaęž‰ hosiki e sunu aęž‰mba aęž‰mba pea poko pu hoeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ aneke e make aęž‰mba aęž‰mba pea poko pu hoeyaalieke.
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ hamoko alemanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ na handeteke haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hamoko alemanu epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hapeke laa hone tulao kiliaęž‰pe.
\v 12 Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ alemanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ na handeteke hawaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ ekie laęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ epimaęž‰ kiliaęž‰pe.
\p 
\v 13 E pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ you hali yaaponaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Puluekemaęž‰ taapo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ puki halolo hataęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ honditi pilieke o hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homu wopu pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ kiaalieke. Kutupa make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mani yaapo ikaęž‰ you hali yaapo haenaęž‰ laa ipilikaęž‰ e yaapotaęž‰ homeke dinaęž‰ pokaapeke anaęž‰ na pelememe leekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ mandane pimanu leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 11ęž‰12-13, 5ęž‰31-32, Maka 10ęž‰11-12)
\p 
\v 14 Mo hande Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leekeeki opuaataęž‰ ipiki kitaemekeme. Pa ekipeke ikitaęž‰ mani paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ puki wotu wimikimaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ haleme tapakemaęž‰ handolo pelemepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki hone paeyaotaęž‰ hone ulaęž‰me. Do kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Otaęž‰ hau tieke ale manue laa hone witeleme ale manutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰taęž‰ pa pa alee hone ulaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Mo Lo Pi wieke ekimanu make mo hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape pimiki ekimanu make laęž‰tia aęž‰pa hande bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionimaęž‰ walo paeyaeyekeme. Koto natenaęž‰ kini pu mea aęž‰pa ame do natenaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Pi Seliapotaęž‰ walaęž‰tia pu haleketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali aneke hapumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ ipuluekemaęž‰ honkopu wotu halememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Kutupa oli ya do kenke yaapo alupeaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ tanda tieke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tombo hosiki siki kone alupeaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tanda tieke paęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 18 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kiao wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ tooli kaęž‰taasaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo kialaęž‰ wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ make hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ hakopu tunku laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Hamoko hali pitaęž‰ Laęž‰satesi yaapo
\p 
\v 19 Ambaęž‰ hamoko hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yenki tiekemaęž‰ hambeeke dau seliapo pikieki pambatiki peataęž‰ nate paeyao epeke epeke nemanu naęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.
\v 20 Kutupa mo hamoko halinaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo natehali hayeke hali homeke Laęž‰satesi mea pua wiaęž‰tiki pu haemekeme. Mo halitaęž‰ tete tete pambeekeme.
\v 21 Ipikitaęž‰ hande hamoko halinaęž‰ ne u hayeke teipolo tokele paęž‰taęž‰ lopaęž‰tiki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ batiki pilimi ne popusunu nolueke hone u hayekeme. Kutu piekepate ipikaęž‰ tete manutaęž‰ kika titimaęž‰ aęž‰pa pende pende naęž‰tiki pu haemekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Kutu peaęž‰tiki pu hao mo hande natehalitaęž‰ homeekeme. Kutupa mo hande enisolo manumaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo lopulao pitinaęž‰ mea pemekeme. Kutupa mo hande hamoko hali make homeeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ toko mea hoimikime.
\v 23 Hande hamoko halitaęž‰ oni ti to halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ tanda tieke minolo hataęž‰ handaęž‰liaeyekepate Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ Laęž‰satesi yaapo lopula alu pea pitipikieki papate haepekeeki handeekeme.
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰o. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e. Do ti to halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ IĚ± tanda tieke peaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Laęž‰satesimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki maĚ±lekemaęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰ tenke lao yaka kekeke kosaęž‰ pinaęž‰yeke wataenaęž‰ tapae laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Koto leekepate Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya wekio. Hone niminae. Neketaęž‰ hande kenkenaęž‰ hae natenaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epeke alemanu wotu wia haepate Laęž‰satesitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke alemanu homeke miaęž‰me. Kutu piekepate ametaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo haenaęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ tanda naleme.
\v 26 Kotoeki manutaęž‰ koto yaęž‰laęž‰pate maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ halomaęž‰eki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hombo tieke ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ do diki halopaęž‰ nane halomaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ ta neke hale nane ipuluekemaęž‰ taapelemepate aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰lieke. Kutupa neke hale nane haleme wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ doane ipuluekemaęž‰ taapeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰lieke leekeme.
\v 27 Koto leeke mo hamoko halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke honke alomaęž‰ yaka apaęž‰naęž‰ da nane Laęž‰satesi penaęž‰ tapae.
\v 28 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ yaka kame tonu yunki hataęž‰ halememaęž‰ iki make do tanda pu halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ aęž‰paamaęž‰naęž‰yeke Laęž‰satesimaęž‰ kinki pulu penaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Koto leeke handa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kame tonunaęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ make potopede haliwekimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ lao ulaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰ mo haliwekinaęž‰ pi opinaęž‰e laa leekeme.
\v 30 Hande hamoko halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aęž‰pa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰o. Kototaęž‰ anaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Pate ambaęž‰ homeeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ paa tiao lolo peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu hoki walimikie laa leekeme.
\v 31 Koto leekepate Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande Mosesimaęž‰ make potopede haliwekimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ lao ulaęž‰ ekimanu na opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo homaęž‰laęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paa tiao epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la na wilimikie leekeme.
\c 17
\s1 Hoke hau pinaęž‰ pu tiaasaęž‰ hau
\r (Maęž‰tiu 18ęž‰6-7,21-22, Maka 9ęž‰42)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali hoke hau paęž‰taęž‰ penaęž‰ yeke pu tiaasaęž‰ haumanu opolo epolo paęž‰laęž‰pate kutu piki haumanu pinaęž‰ pu tiaasaęž‰ sometaęž‰ paalaęž‰e. Hoke yenki milieke.
\v 2 Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ make paęž‰taęž‰ toopi tieke aneke mea endiao oni dawala ikali paęž‰taęž‰ lopaaso yolutaęž‰ epolo piaęž‰me. Ekipeke. Ipiki pa hataęž‰taęž‰ do hosiki wekiwandiki sunu maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo hoke hau pinaęž‰ pu tialieke.
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ piteleme haumanu wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p Nakaęž‰ kamemaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ honkopu hake manaęž‰ pimanu la halaęž‰peke. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ paa hande ipikaęž‰ piaęž‰ hoke hau manunaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰la minaęž‰paęž‰laeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki paa paeyaapeke.
\v 4 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ nate homekenaęž‰ kone hoto watake hataęž‰ hoke hau pea paa hoto watake hataęž‰ kone neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰e lolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki ipikaęž‰ hoke hau paa paeyaapeke leekeme.
\s1 Hone tulaasaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 5 Aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ hone tulaalomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mea daeyawae lemekeme.
\v 6 Tekehalimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ hone tulaalemeeki aęž‰ndaęž‰ mo (kiĚ±miĚ±leĚ±maęž‰ handeke ale) masidadi kiliki sikimaęž‰ handenaęž‰ yeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ daenaęž‰ lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do kiliki nalaęž‰ ti hombeleke biki molobeti paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kone nakaęž‰ piki yokaataęž‰ oni dawalanaęž‰ pua nokaęž‰pee lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi otaęž‰ opua pilieke leekeme.
\s1 E pokaasaęž‰ halinaęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki
\p 
\v 7 Iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondomaęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ enaęž‰ kenke lu wiaenaęž‰ o nakaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto some paa laęž‰kaęž‰la nakaęž‰ da aęž‰paęž‰tiki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± ne aęž‰pa nae pitaęž‰ lo halepe.
\v 8 Diaęž‰me. Kotoeki na leketaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ dupa lo haleme. Yaka ne ambi wamo peaotaęž‰ ne panaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ yamo halaęž‰ akaęž‰ mea pambaotaęž‰ yaka ne ikali nono yu wia pitaataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ ne nelipikie lo haleme leekeme.
\v 9 Mo e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aneke halimaęž‰ peaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰eki opua paeyao piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aneke halimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo keiyae lenaęž‰ yu wia hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Diaęž‰me.
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ iki make koto tupaęž‰ konee. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke lelimi ekimanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ pu paeyaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do tupaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Nikitaęž‰ epeke e pokaasomaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali diaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰ haumanu homeke pu paeyaalomaęž‰me lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ kiki yaapo halinaęž‰ kindi yeni mea epeaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 11 Yesutaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane poluekemaęž‰ yeke Kaęž‰lili make Sametia kenke yaapo tombonaęž‰ peekeme.
\v 12 Ipikitaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ polueke alo pulu haenaęž‰ kiki yaapo haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ kindi yeni hayeke haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu aęž‰pa mandaęž‰hande pimikime. Ikitaęž‰ hosiki siki papate hataęž‰
\v 13 Yesu wi la do lemekeme. Yesu Aneke Halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e lemekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ iki handa alotaęž‰ mo yeni peao halaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ iki handenaęž‰ pupe leekeme. Kutupa mo haliwekitaęž‰ mo potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰ kone mea epeaeyekeme.
\v 15 Koto haliweki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki mea epeaeyekeeki hando haotaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulu hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ bikitaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyatia
\v 16 aęž‰pa Yesunaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ puki yama peliolo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰e pi leekeme. Kutu pieke halitaęž‰ Sametia hali yeekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Kotoeki handaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ dupa leekeme. IĚ±maęž‰ mea epeaowaęž‰ haliwekitaęž‰ kiki yaapo mea epeaowaęž‰me. Mo mandane kiki paeya mandane kikinaęž‰ tonkopu haliwekitaęž‰ ekipeke na laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa pelemepe.
\v 18 Pa ekipeke do da yu maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali ipiki homeke laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰e lolo epeekepe
\v 19 laataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hone tulale ekimaęž‰ neke mea epeaalaęž‰me. Tiao pue leekeme.
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰23-28,37-41)
\p 
\v 20 Mandane Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handimaęž‰pe lemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handolo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ na ipilieke leekeme.
\v 21 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do paęž‰taęž‰ do handaęž‰e o Mokoto paęž‰taęž‰ mokoto handaęž‰e pi na lelieke. Pa ekipeke. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± haleke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ nate homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ handuluekemaęž‰ hone wopu ulu pelemepate otaęž‰ na handilimikie.
\v 23 Mandane tapakemaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lelimikie. Mo nane handaęž‰pe o Doane handaęž‰pe laa lolo pelemepate na weiyaęž‰ mea puaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke.
\v 24 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo ti tekele pitolo hataęž‰ mo ya honiki honiki paeyaonaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peao halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone pilieke.
\v 25 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate titinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tanda aneke hapu milieke. Kutupa ame do haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make ipiki kialimikie.
\p 
\v 26 Hande Noa hayeke natenaęž‰ pu haemeke tupaęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke ipikaęž‰ nate manunaęž‰ make mandake haumanu pilimikie.
\v 27 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne ikali naęž‰tiki wandaęž‰ meaęž‰tiki halinaęž‰ da puaęž‰tiki putia aęž‰pa Noa kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambeeke nate opolo epeekeme. Kutu piki haumanu pu haemekepate koto tomonaęž‰ kone ikali talo hataęž‰ iki paeyao lu homaeyekeme.
\v 28 Koto mandake tupaęž‰ kone hande Loda ipikaęž‰ hayeke natenaęž‰ pieke tupaęž‰ kone pilimikie. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ne ikali nalo anemone ale hambolo tapaaso pitolo wae alemanu pokolo hataęž‰ damanu aęž‰eyaęž‰tiki pu haemekeme.
\v 29 Kutu pimikipate Lodamaęž‰ mo Sodomo da minaęž‰paęž‰layeke natenaęž‰taęž‰ ti uleke make talo talo hake lankaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki solopa oli ya paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ lopaęž‰niaeyeke ekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaosiki lu homaeyekeme.
\v 30 Mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke peneme yao waliaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ homeke tupaęž‰ kone ipilieke.
\p 
\v 31 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ da holunaęž‰ pitiliaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yelieke. Mandake tupaęž‰ kone hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi enaęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipiki pa laęž‰kaęž‰la da puaęž‰peke na yelieke.
\v 32 Lodanaęž‰ weteke niminaapaęž‰peke.
\v 33 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki miniki hao haluekemaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone alu palieke. Kutu piliaęž‰pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki alu paenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paa wia halieke.
\p 
\v 34 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolome. Koto timbaataęž‰ hali yaapo pelipipate homeke hali minolotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ pa peli pelia halieke.
\v 35-36 Wandaęž‰ yaapotaęž‰ palaowa yumbuolo pitinaęž‰ homeke wandaęž‰ hondo minolotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lalieke leekeme.
\v 37 Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Koto ale ekitaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ piliaęž‰pe lemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ hoteke lupa ulaęž‰ ale ninaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ wapukini mombolo halaęž‰me leekeme.
\c 18
\s1 Kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰maęž‰ honke laęž‰tiki piekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homeke hoto paeyao yeni peaęž‰tiki pinaęž‰yeke onkolumaęž‰ laa dupa leekeme.
\v 2 Da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke make wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make hone wotu na wiekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa koto da paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke kineke wandaęž‰ homekemaęž‰ mo hande hali paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ mie laęž‰tiki piekeme.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo pi yokaalu peao hayeke halimaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ potaęž‰ epeaapeketaęž‰ kiatiki piekepate pa hosiki hao hao pea ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homolopate wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make hone na witolopate
\v 5 pa do hande kineke wandaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ potaęž‰ epeaalueke. Kotoeki na puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ hoto paeyao aęž‰paęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ IĚ± sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homaapaęž‰naęž‰ hone wiekeme leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ paa pi alo alotaęž‰ Hande hoke pi yokaalu peayeke halimaęž‰ leeke ekitaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 7 Kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ alo timba natenaęž‰ wi alo honke laęž‰tiki pu haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ potaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tikitiki na yaaliaęž‰pe. Tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ kese kese piliaęž‰pe. Diaęž‰me.
\v 8 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto kone ikaęž‰ potaęž‰ epeaalieke. Kutu piliaęž‰pate Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipiliaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paa hone tulaleme tapaketaęž‰ handiliaęž‰pe o na handiliaęž‰pe laa leekeme.
\s1 Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pipiki hali yaaponaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 9 IĚ±taęž‰ epeke hali seliapo yaęž‰laęž‰pate iki paeyaotaęž‰ hoke wandaęž‰halie hone u haleme tapake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa leekeme.
\v 10 Ambaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ hali yaapo oli tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pulupeke alo pepekeme. Mo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Paęž‰tisi halie. Maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dakisi mu hayeke hali yeekeme.
\v 11 Mo Paęž‰tisi halitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali na hayeke paęž‰taęž‰ leke yolaęž‰ moneao hataęž‰ yeni dupa piekeme. Kodaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ keiyae alome. IĚ±taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ piteleme tupaęž‰ pasaęž‰tei na pu o yayapiki pi na lo o suseke na hao halome. IĚ±taęž‰ mo koto dakisi mu halaęž‰ hali tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me.
\v 12 IĚ±taęž‰ pula homeke homeke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hoto yaapomaęž‰ nee pi wiaataęž‰ kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ yaka mu halo alaęž‰taęž‰manu paeyao putupa kiki yaaponaęž‰ homeketaęž‰ neke ku halome.
\p 
\v 13 Koto leekepate mo dakisi mu hayeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ siki mo pate leke hataęž‰taęž‰ oli ya nane kone na handaęž‰liake pandaęž‰ puniao hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hakokonaęž‰ litolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰o. IĚ±taęž‰ hoke hau polo somemaęž‰ IĚ± aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa la kitolome. Mo hande Paęž‰tisi halitaęž‰ da laęž‰kaęž‰la peeketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo halepe ekitaęž‰ tikitiki na paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo dakisi mu halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ tikitiki paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ aneke hali au leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ minaęž‰nialieke. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone pandaęž‰ puniayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tieke au lalieke leekeme.
\s1 Wekiwandiki sunu wamo pumaęž‰ pumaęž‰ piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 19ęž‰13-15, Maka 10ęž‰13-16)
\p 
\v 15 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hosiki wekiwandiki sunu Yesunaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ wataenaęž‰ yeke hatuku epemekeme. Kutu pimikieki handolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali hando lemekeme.
\v 16 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ mo wekiwandiki wi laęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ Mo wekiwandiki sunumaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰maęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ na peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Do wekiwandikimaęž‰ handeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ekie.
\v 17 Doeki hone wopu u hapaęž‰peke. Wekiwandiki sunumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki minolo piteleme tupaęž‰ na mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ na hondo pambilimikie leekeme.
\s1 Hamoko hali
\r (Maęž‰tiu 19ęž‰16-30, Maka 10ęž‰17-31)
\p 
\v 18 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ you hali homekemaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epeke Disao. IĚ±maęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰taęž‰ eki hau peonope laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 19 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epeke halie pitaęž‰ ekipeke alo alepe. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali aęž‰ndaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ na halaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰ homeke epeke tupaęž‰ halaęž‰me.
\v 20 Hande Lo Pi Ulaęž‰eki paeyao hone wilime. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ homenaęž‰ na liaęž‰peke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ hakopu na tunkulaęž‰peke. Pake na napeke. Yayapiki pi na lapeke. Makeaaso kone maęž‰ndaęž‰ maĚ±leke na liaęž‰peke. Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ apaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰eki hone wilime leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Mo halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ± hosiki weki siki hatia aęž‰paataęž‰ koto ale pi ulaęž‰eki paeyaotaęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na tunkuliki opua telia pu halome leekeme.
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ do pi opuaataęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pulu pele hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ pa ulaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ wia hale alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hambenaęž‰ laa mo milipi manitaęž‰ mandane natehali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hale hale peaęž‰peke. Kutu pikinaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ oli hepeni da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke epeke ale wopu mu halipikie. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ yaka hoki nane teliaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 23 Hande halimaęž‰ koto leekeeki opitolotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme. Pa ekipeke ipikitaęž‰ hamoko tieke hayeke ekimaęž‰ piekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Yesumaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ puki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeeki handa alotaęž‰ Mo hamoko wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaęž‰peketaęž‰ tanda wopu paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 25 Mo kemolo maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ mo noĚ±iĚ± kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba yopuaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ pa mo hamoko halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ miaęž‰peke kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tupaęž‰ na milieke alome leekeme.
\v 26 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ do leekeeki opuaataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epimaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.
\v 27 Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Kutupa Pidamaęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme. Handaęž‰e. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ damanu make kiao neke teliaęž‰ mea epomaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 29 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰e. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone witolo ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ o da o hameke titi o apaęž‰ amaęž‰ o wekiwandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo minaęž‰paęž‰lao epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 30 kotaęž‰ ame do kenkenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ kone alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao hakaęž‰taęž‰pao meaataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ ipiliaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ milieke leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homa paa tiaapeke ekinaęž‰ tanaęž‰ tepo la haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 20ęž‰17-19, Maka 10ęž‰32-34)
\p 
\v 31 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki talo pu mea mo pateleke pulu hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opuaęž‰pe. Nikitaęž‰ Diutuseleme da teke paęž‰taęž‰ pulumaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu lao wilimi ekitaęž‰ peneme yaalimikie.
\v 32 Ipikitaęž‰ Diendaili haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ mea halimikie. Koto haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki kitao laa mandaęž‰ mandaęž‰ meaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ dopi taalimikie.
\v 33 Ipiki yombua baotaęž‰ homenaęž‰ lilimikie. Kutu pilimipate ipikitaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ nate teponaęž‰ paa tiao daęž‰ta halieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Koto leekepate mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo pinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeke siki make na handaęž‰ wimikime. Ekipeke koto leeke pi manunaęž‰ teke paeyaotaęž‰ aęž‰mbao wiekeeki yaalo otaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wimikime.
\s1 Leke holu pea honke lo hayeke hali
\r (Maęž‰tiu 20ęž‰29-34, Maka 10ęž‰46-52)
\p 
\v 35 Yesutaęž‰ mo Dietiko da paęž‰taęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ yeke pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ pitieke leke holu piki halimaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ honke alo pitiekeme.
\v 36 Ipikitaęž‰ pitu hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali tieke yopulu leekeeki opuaataęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ aleke yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 37 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesu yopu alaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 38 Koto lemeke mo halimaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ eĚ± wi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesuo. Deipidinaęž‰ Eiyekeo. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 39 Mo titinaęž‰ yapemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Pi na lapema laa saęž‰saęž‰ pimikipate mo halimaęž‰ otaęž‰ wi aneke hapu paa alo alotaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ Eiyekeo. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 40 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ pua yolaęž‰ mea hataęž‰ mo hali ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea ipupee leekeme. Mo hande hali teke paęž‰taęž‰ epeeke handa Yesumaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰
\v 41 IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ eki peaano hone paęž‰laęž‰pe leeke handaa mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ paa handuluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 42 Yesumaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Handaęž‰e. Nakaęž‰ hone tulale ekimaęž‰ neke epeaalaęž‰me.
\v 43 Koto kone mo halimaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ handaęž‰peke yeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu teliaęž‰ mea pulu hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae laęž‰tia peekeme. Mo hande wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ doeki hando haotaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki tieke laemekeme.
\c 19
\s1 Yesu pitaęž‰ Saęž‰kiasi yaapo
\p 
\v 1 Yesutaęž‰ mo Dietiko daoni monemaęž‰ tilao polueke alo oni daoni paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambeekeme.
\v 2 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ dakisi mu hayeke hamoko hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Saęž‰kiasi hayekeme.
\v 3 Ipikitaęž‰ mo Yesu lo haemeke hali handulueke alo epeekepate dokaęž‰tiki yeke ekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tieke mombaęž‰la haemekeeki yaalo hataęž‰ Yesu handaęž‰peke anaęž‰ na piekeme.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ ipiki ambaęž‰la pototo laa pua nose ti maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰meiya pitaęž‰ Yesu kotoeki mea wendiao yapiliaęž‰ alenaęž‰ handulueke hone wiekeme.
\v 5 Yesu koto alenaęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa oli ti nane handaęž‰liaaso Saęž‰kiasi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neke otaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± holaęž‰paęž‰e. Pa ekipeke. IĚ±taęž‰ ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰leke loaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 6 Saęž‰kiasi koto kone holaęž‰paęž‰niaotaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ handaęž‰ miekeme.
\v 7 Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Kutu piekeeki hando haotaęž‰ hambilikimaęž‰ hambilikimaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ mo hande hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ kimisu pulaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 8 Kutu pimikipate Saęž‰kiasi tiao hataęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Opie. IĚ±maęž‰ yaka alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ tukikinaęž‰ telipa mandane ekitaęž‰ mo natehali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ halueke. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali aęž‰ndaęž‰ makeao pake aęž‰ndaęž‰ noaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hoto tonkopunaęž‰ pakaęž‰lao paa halaęž‰tiki pulueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Yesumaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ame do da paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke do halitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ mondu tankaęž‰laęž‰ pealaęž‰ tapake hali yeke loaęž‰me.
\v 10 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo alu paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali handaęž‰ wia peteluekemaęž‰ yeke aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Manimaęž‰ e pokolo hataęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao minaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 25ęž‰14-30)
\p 
\v 11 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi opitolo haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ la haleekeme. Koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Diutuseleme nane teke paęž‰taęž‰ polukumaęž‰ peeke handaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ koto kone ipulaęž‰me hone wimikime.
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali tieke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane pua ipikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kini hali pituluekemaęž‰ peekepate kone paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipuluekemaęž‰ peekeme.
\v 13 Poluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokao haemeke kiki yaapo haliweki wi laęž‰ meaataęž‰ iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ 20 kina hale hale pea iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± poluaęž‰ hoki nane do kitolo manimaęž‰ bisinisi pea ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ekipa hakaęž‰taęž‰pao milimio laa e pokaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Koto laa peekepate mo hande halinaęž‰ da haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki honditi pitolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ peeke hoki nane mandane haliwekimaęž‰ pua lenaęž‰ tapaaso alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kini hali pitaapeketaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ ki paęž‰laęž‰me laa lolo penaęž‰ tapaemekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Kutu pimikipate hande halitaęž‰ kini hali anaęž‰naęž‰ pitataęž‰ paa ipikaęž‰ da nane laęž‰kaęž‰la epeekeme. Koto kone ipikaęž‰ e pokao haenaęž‰ mani halaa peeke haliweki wi laęž‰ mipi peaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao mimiki ekitaęž‰ ekipupe laa handuluekemaęž‰ piekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Titinaęž‰ halimaęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Hande 20 kina ki manimaęž‰taęž‰ pa mandane 200 kinamanu make hakaęž‰taęž‰pao mealome laa leekeme.
\v 17 Hande kinimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epeke tupaęž‰ peleme. Neketaęž‰ e epeke tupaęž‰ pokale halie. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hosiki e kone epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke haeke handa loaęž‰maęž‰ ametaęž‰ teke damanu kiki yaapo handeteke halenaęž‰yeke kitolome leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ hoki nane epeeke halimaęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Hande 20 kina ki manimaęž‰ pa mandane 100 kinamanu make hakaęž‰taęž‰pao mealome laa leekeme.
\v 19 Hande kinimaęž‰ koto some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ teke damanu kiki homeke handeteke halenaęž‰yeke kitolome leekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Kutupa koto hoki nane e pokao hayeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Hande nakaęž‰ 20 kina doe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ dau siki paęž‰taęž‰ pankaęž‰ uaęž‰me.
\v 21 Neketaęž‰ takaęž‰lake hali hale ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ na nokopekeeki kone mondu no hale make na tandelekeeki kone tulu no haleme leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Hande kinimaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hoke e pokao hale halie. Nakaęž‰ ale pimaęž‰ kone nakaęž‰ hoke hau peleeki peneme yaalueke. Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ takaęž‰lake hali halomaęž‰ hone ta wikaęž‰taęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ na nokopekeeki no halo make na tandelekeeki tulu no halome hone witele yekea.
\v 23 Kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Yaka manitaęž‰ baęž‰nkaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wia wetepenaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao muluekemaęž‰ ekipeke na wiaepe. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ IĚ± ipuluaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ handeeki make hakaęž‰taęž‰pao wilieeki apaęž‰tao mulu puaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 24 Kotoeki laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halinaęž‰ 20 kina meaataęž‰ hande 200 kina wia halaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰pe laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Pa ekipeke. Mo halitaęž‰ 200 kina ambaęž‰ wia halaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 26 Mo kini halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ambaęž‰ wia halaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ mandaneeki make hakaęž‰taęž‰pao milieke. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate na wia halaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wia halaęž‰eki siki kone yokaęž‰ milieke.
\v 27 Kutupa ametaęž‰ hande IĚ±taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kini hamenaęž‰ kiaemeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliweki ikitaęž‰ hatuku aęž‰pa yaka leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ liaęž‰paęž‰peke laa leekeme leekeme.
\s1 Kini hali tupaęž‰ Diutuseleme daoni paęž‰taęž‰ opolo peekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰1-11, Maka 11ęž‰1-11, Dioni 12ęž‰12-19)
\p 
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰ koto pimanu laataęž‰ ipiki ambaęž‰la titinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali mea wetepe yao mo Diutuseleme da teke paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.
\v 29-30 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ oli Olipi peiyene teaęž‰naęž‰ hayeke Betepeisi make Bedani da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali yaapo ambaęž‰la tapaaluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme. Oni halaęž‰ da nane opolo puaęž‰paęž‰peke. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pepekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ donki ikiki hali maęž‰naęž‰ endi balaęž‰eki handilipipikie. Mo donkitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na pita pomu halemeekie. Holaęž‰ tapao mea aęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 31 Kutu pipikinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki lotaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Kutupa mo hande hali yaapo pua Yesumaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ kone otaęž‰ pua handepepekeme.
\v 33 Mo hande donki ikiki hali maęž‰naęž‰siki hololo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo teke haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke holaęž‰ minaęž‰lepepe lemeke handaa mo hali yaapomaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰
\v 34 Tekehalimaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me lepekeme.
\v 35 Kutupa mo hande hali yaapomaęž‰ mo donki ikiki hali maęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ mea pepekeme. Kutupa mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ daumanu mo donkinaęž‰ hoki manda wiataęž‰ Yesu pitulu aęž‰meinaęž‰ tambaęž‰ mimikime.
\p 
\v 36 Yesumaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pita ipulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ daumanu lepolonaęž‰ peolao yamomaęž‰ yamomaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 37 Kutupa ipiki mo Diutuseleme teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo poluekemaęž‰ yeke mo Olipi pote teaęž‰ nane u niayeke potaęž‰naęž‰ holaęž‰pa pulu haenaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimea pemeke wandaęž‰hali aneke hapumaęž‰ kini pea Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Keiyae laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki anekemaęž‰ mea minaęž‰liaemekeme. Pa ekipeke Yesumaęž‰ hau tieke tieke maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pieke ekimanu otaęž‰ aneke hapu handemekeme.
\p 
\v 38 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ laęž‰tia pulu alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ kini halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeaenaęž‰e. Hepeni nane haleme tapakemaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaaso hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki tieke miniliaenaęž‰e laęž‰tia pemekeme.
\v 39 Koto lemeke handaa koto wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ haemeke Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Disao. Nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Kutupiki pi na lapepe laa lae lemekeme.
\v 40 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ Pi na lapaęž‰pee loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do toopimanu ikaęž‰ kone eĚ± alo hataęž‰ poyaęž‰ tieke lelimikie leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Diutuseleme daoninaęž‰ eĚ± leekeeki
\p 
\v 41 Yesu mo Diutuseleme da teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa mo da handolo hataęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± alo alotaęž‰
\v 42 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ame aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki hone witolo yolutaęž‰ epolo piaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ametaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 43 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliweki aęž‰pa aęž‰ndaęž‰ pape tieke tieke hopaęž‰liao pokaataęž‰ nakaęž‰ potaęž‰ pokaęž‰niao pitilimikie. Aęž‰ndaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ mandane mandane aęž‰pa dupalimikie.
\v 44 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke make nakaęž‰ pape tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ lia paeyaalimikie. Kutupa nakaęž‰ toopi maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alenaęž‰ otaęž‰ na winaęž‰ lelimikie. Pa ekipeketaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke peteluekemaęž‰ peneme yao epenaęž‰ leaęž‰ nate leketaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wimaęž‰e leekeme.
\s1 Yesu tembolo da peekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰12-17, Maka 11ęž‰15-19, Dioni 2ęž‰13-22)
\p 
\v 45 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua ne anemone alemanu tapaaso pitimiki haliweki tolu litolo alotaęž‰
\v 46 Mo Baibolonaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka dataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ yeni peaęž‰tiki pulu paęž‰laęž‰ dae lolo paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo pake no halaęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ aęž‰mbalo peleme da haenaęž‰ alememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 47 Kutupa hoto paeyao Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ pi walaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme. Pate mo hande yeni peao haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ make pi ulaęž‰eki walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesu luekemaęž‰ hone wimikime.
\v 48 Kutu pimikipate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wimikime. Pa ekipeke. Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi pa oputia pulu hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ hosiki siki make minaęž‰paęž‰laluekemaęž‰ na taapemekeme.
\c 20
\s1 Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰23-27, Maka 11ęž‰27-33)
\p 
\v 1 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali Kodaęž‰naęž‰ manaęž‰ pi alo make mo Pi Seliapo walo hayekeme. Kutupa mo yeni peao haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ you haliweki make mo Lo Pi walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make mandane da handeteke haemeke you haliweki paeyao aęž‰pa
\v 2 Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do pu haleeki manutaęž‰ epinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ pie alaęž‰eki pu halepe. Kutupa make neketaęž‰ epimaęž‰ honkopu ku haleke pipe laa niki opuomono aĚ±iĚ± la kie lemekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pionoe.
\v 4 Dionimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali bapitaisi peayeke ekinaęž‰ honkoputaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ haleekepe o Kodaęž‰maęž‰ haleekepe laa leekeme.
\v 5 Koto pi opuataęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alo alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ekipa hombo peamanaęž‰pe. Hepeni nane ekie lomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ lo hayeke pi manutaęž‰ ekipeke na miniki haemepe laa lelieke.
\v 6 Pate nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ekie lomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ niki toopimaęž‰ lilimikie. Pa ekipeke iki paeyaomaęž‰ Dionitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halo hayeke halie lo halememe.
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki na handolomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 8 Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make yaka pu halo hau manunaęž‰ wele peao halaęž‰ halinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ na la kulueke leekeme.
\s1 Hoke haliwekimaęž‰ e handeteke haemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰33-46, Maka 12ęž‰1-12)
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ la halolo alotaęž‰ Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ waini pu e pokaataęž‰ mo etaęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰taęž‰ yenki mulu pimiki ekitaęž‰ hosikimaęž‰ putupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰tiki pinaęž‰yeke halaataęž‰ nate hokulunaęž‰ papate peekeme.
\v 10 Wetepenaęž‰ mo waini kiliki talemeke nate opolo epeeketaęž‰ mo hande haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ putu piliki wiaemekeeki meaenaęž‰yeke ipikaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Kutu piekepate hande halitaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ yombua bao alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ siki make na haleke pa tapaemekeme.
\v 11 Kutu pimiki handaataęž‰ paa ipikaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Kutu piekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo halitaęž‰ yaalaęž‰ meao yombua bao ombu alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ make na haleke pa tapaemekeme.
\v 12 Kutu pimiki ombu paa tepo peao ipikaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapaeyekepate mo hande haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ koto some make lia yombua bao tete tete mea pitao mo e paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mea baemekeme.
\v 13 Kotoeki ombu pimiki mo hande waini enaęž‰ teke somemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ eki puluaęž‰pe hone wiaataęž‰ Yaka pukimaęž‰ na kepeleke weki kone tapalueke hone wiekeme. Ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka wekinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ opua pilimikie laa leekeme.
\v 14 Kutu piekepate mo hande e handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo weki epeekeeki handaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ lombolo alotaęž‰ Hande e teke halinaęž‰ anke teke mulu paęž‰laęž‰ wekitaęž‰ koto ipulaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Otaęž‰ lumanaęž‰e la alotaęž‰ Lumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo etaęž‰ otaęž‰ nikaęž‰ eki wilieke lemekeme.
\v 15 Koto laataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo sometaęž‰ e tikene nane yolaęž‰ mea puaataęž‰ lia homaemekeme leekeme.
\p Koto pimanu la paeyeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do enaęž‰ tekehali opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo e handeteke haleme haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki haumanu piliaęž‰pe.
\v 16 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰pa mo haliweki liaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ etaęž‰ mo mandane e handeteke halo paęž‰laęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ monealieke leekeme.
\p Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ doeki opu hao alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ kutupa diaęž‰me lemekepate
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ iki handake witolo hataęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me alemepate mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pimaęž‰taęž‰ Mo da aęž‰eyo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Hoelaęž‰me laa kiaemeke toopi kone ametaęž‰ keneme paęž‰taęž‰ danaęž‰ teke toopi ulaęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ alekepe la loaęž‰me.
\v 18 Mo koto toopi manda lopiliaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pindi pindi pilieke. Kutupa make mo toopimaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ manda lopeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo sometaęž‰ yombua bao dokolo au lalieke leekeme.
\s1 Sisanaęž‰ dakisi mani
\r (Maęž‰tiu 22ęž‰15-22, Maka 12ęž‰13-17)
\p 
\v 19 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ you haliweki make hande pi ulaęž‰eki walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesu koto kone minuluekemaęž‰ yeke taapemekeme. Ekipeke ikaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kone leaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ pimikime. Kutu puluekemaęž‰ pimikipate mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ paalaęž‰ pieke handa paemekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ weitolo hataęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ Yesu tamenaęž‰yeke maęž‰naęž‰ yapaęž‰ pimikime. Mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Makeaaso hataęž‰ kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ homu piki pimanu alememe hone winaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pulu pupe lemekeme. Ikaęž‰ hone tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Koto lotaęž‰ pilimi ekimaęž‰ pa makeaaso hataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ kiki tondoliki hondaęž‰ lia mo Lomaęž‰naęž‰ Kapomani You halinaęž‰ kiki nane halaęž‰ monealumeke laa honemaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 21 Koto hambemeke maęž‰naęž‰ ikiki haliwekimaęž‰ pua lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ lo hale pi make walo hale pi make otaęž‰ pi lo haleme hone witolomaęž‰me. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo biki ulaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na u hake iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ mandake hau piki wandaęž‰halie laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi homeke walo haleme laa alotaęž‰
\v 22 Niki la kie. Mo Kapomani tieke Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ dakisi mani halaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pe o hoelaęž‰pe. Halomonope o na halomonope lemekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ makeaaso pimikieki ambaęž‰ handaataęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 24 Mo toopi kiliki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ iĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰pe. Do aĚ±oĚ±aĚ±oĚ± pitaęž‰ biki yaapotaęž‰ epinaęž‰eki yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Sisanaęž‰ ekie lemekeme.
\v 25 Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Sisanaęž‰ alemanu meatiki pitolotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ kone mea halaęž‰tiki pu hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ alemanu yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kone pa halaęž‰tiki pu hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 26 Mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ Yesu mea lopapeke tupaęž‰ mateeke handaa mo hande haliwekimaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na leke ipikaęž‰ hombo peayeke ekinaęž‰ pututumaęž‰ homa pitatia yapemekeme.
\s1 Homa paa tiaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ lotaęž‰ piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 22ęž‰23-33, Maka 12ęž‰18-27)
\p 
\v 27 Kutupa mandane Saęž‰dusi haliwekitaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa na tialieke lo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu ombu lotaęž‰ pulu aęž‰pa alotaęž‰
\v 28 Walaęž‰laęž‰ halio. Mosesimaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Lo Pi dupa lao wialaęž‰me. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ wekiwandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mondu wiki weteke homeke minaęž‰paęž‰lao homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo kosaęž‰ piki wandaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hamekemaęž‰ meaataęž‰ mo mendilipi wekiwandikitaęž‰ mo homeaęž‰ somenaęž‰eki mendiaenaęž‰ laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 29 Kotaęž‰ ambaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ watake hataęž‰ haemekeme. Kutupa mupeke halitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ mea hao kone wekiwandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mondu wiki pa homeekeme.
\v 30 Kutu pieke handaa mo hoki paęž‰taęž‰ halimaęž‰ mo kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ miekepate homeke tupaęž‰ kone homeekeme.
\v 31 Kutu pieketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ tepo peao halimaęž‰ mea ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make homeke hau piekeme. Kutupa mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hau ombu piekeme.
\v 32 Kutu puaęž‰tiki pua paelo pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰ make homeekeme.
\v 33 Kutu pimikipate mo wandaęž‰hali paa tialimi natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ haliepe. Pa ekipeke mo hande watake hataęž‰ hali paeyaomaęž‰ mo homeke wandaęž‰ kone mimiki ekinaęž‰ lomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ame do kenkenaęž‰ hatia ipulaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mu alualu pea tooli hao halemepate
\v 35 pa mo homa paa tiao mo wetepe nane ipiliaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ paa hao haenaęž‰ anaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ tooli au na lelimikie.
\v 36 Ikitaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ handaa paa na homeke hao halimikie. Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki halimikie. Pa ekipeke ikitaęž‰ homa paa tialememe.
\v 37 Kutupa Mosesimaęž‰taęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ paa tiaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ peneme yao walaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ tunkula ulaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ mo ti talo halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ neketaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make Dieikopenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ haleme laa leekeme.
\v 38 Kotaęž‰ koto Kodaęž‰taęž‰ paa hao halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halaęž‰me. Homeleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Ekipeke. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paa hao halememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Mandane Lo Pi walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la laęž‰neaseme lemekeme.
\v 40 Koto lemeke ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ lapeke anaęž‰ na polomaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ lemekeme.
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ tapake apaęž‰taęž‰ epipe
\r (Maęž‰tiu 22ęž‰41-46, Maka 12ęž‰35-37)
\p 
\v 41 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ hande Deipidinaęž‰ tapake weki yelieke lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe.
\v 42 Pa ekipeke Deipidimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone mo Emeli manunaęž‰ buka paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ yaka Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme.
\q1 
\v 43 Nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki haliwekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke oto paęž‰taęž‰ mea pitaluekemaęž‰ neketaęž‰ yaka popeke nane kikinaęž‰ pitaęž‰pekee laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 44 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Deipidimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Yaka Tekehalie laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ ekipa ipikaęž‰ tapake weki haliaęž‰pe laa leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo Lo Pi walo haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ kinki piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 23ęž‰1-36, Maka 12ęž‰38-40)
\p 
\v 45 Mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alo pitieke pi opitolo haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 46 Mo Lo Pi walo haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ hau wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hokulupiki daumanu pambao pomu hataęž‰taęž‰ makedinaęž‰ hatiki pitaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ homu pitolo pi la halenaęž‰ hone wotu u halememe. Mo yeni damanu tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pituluekemaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki handenaęž‰ hone wia mo you haliweki pitinaęž‰ wepia wialaęž‰ epeke seamanu yataęž‰pa pitu halememe. Ne pambaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make epeke haupiki seanaęž‰ pituluekemaęž‰ hone u halememe.
\v 47 Kutupa kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰wekinaęž‰ damanu makea makea pea minolotaęž‰ handaenaęž‰ hau pea yeni pu hokulu peao halememe. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mulu peleme hoke yenkitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao tieke milimikie leekeme.
\c 21
\s1 Kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰naęž‰ haleekeeki
\r (Maka 12ęž‰41-44)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ handaęž‰ moneayekepate mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ mani pambo haemeke bokosinaęž‰ hamoko haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pa hameke halemeke manimanu pamboloendi pimikieki handeekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa make natehali kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ sikimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ manisiki toea yaapomaęž‰ handekeeki aęž‰pa lopaeyekeeki handeekeme.
\v 3 Kotoeki handolo Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do natehali kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ sikimaęž‰ lopaasaęž‰eki sikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke alo hataęž‰ mo mandane wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ wieke ekitaęž‰ lu ankulalaęž‰me.
\v 4 Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ mani tieke putupu mea putupiliki wimiki ekimanu kone mea lopaemepate do wandaęž‰taęž‰ natehali hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wia hayekeeki paeyao mea lopaeyaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ ne hambaęž‰pekeeki kone mea lopaeyaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo danaęž‰ pulu pieke ekimanu la haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰1-2, Maka 13ęž‰1-2)
\p 
\v 5 Mandane disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo dataęž‰ Epekee laa ipikaęž‰ epeke toopimanu pitaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke halemeke alemanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ Handaęž‰e laa pi alo pitimikime. Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 6 Do handeleme alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ toopi manda maęž‰ndaęž‰ na tapaęž‰ pelia hataęž‰ paeyao mea lopaalieke leekeme.
\s1 Kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰3-14, Maka 13ęž‰3-13)
\p 
\v 7 Koto leekeeki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opua alotaęž‰ Disao. Do aleeki manutaęž‰ handimaęž‰ ipiliepe. Kutupa ipuluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰taęž‰ eki hau pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki handulumaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 8 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki makeaamaęž‰naęž‰ wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Hali wopumaęž‰ ya biki laęž‰paleke ipulu alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ipikie alo hataęž‰ hande nate aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰mee lolo pelemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki na taęž‰liaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 9 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me o Homeke tapakemaęž‰ kone aęž‰ndaęž‰ pu alu alu pitaęž‰laęž‰me pi opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homu hapaęž‰peke. Dupiki haumanu ambaęž‰la aęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo hande paetolo natetaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ laa na pitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ ombu alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kenke homekenaęž‰ amitonu tiao pua kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ami tapu aęž‰ndaęž‰ pilimikie. Kini hali homekenaęž‰ amitonu tiao kini hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ami tapu aęž‰ndaęž‰ pilimikie.
\v 11 Kutu piliaęž‰ tomonaęž‰taęž‰ kenke yu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰ piki yu momeni tiekemanu pea make teaęž‰ ki pambo pea make yeni ki tieke make ipilieke. Kutupataęž‰ oli ya nane na handeke haumanu make peaataęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea paalaęž‰ wopupiki aneke haumanu wotu handilimikie.
\p 
\v 12 Dupiki haumanu puluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰taęž‰ niki ambaęž‰la minaęž‰ yombuataęž‰ oni pi hotu haleme da paęž‰taęž‰ niki pi yokaalu puemenaęž‰ halaęž‰ moneaotaęž‰ dipula mea pitalimikie. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ yaka bikinaęž‰ kone mo kini haliwekimanu make handeteke pilimi haliwekinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hatuku ipilimikie.
\v 13 Koto natetaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Pi Seliapo la halo peleme ekinaęž‰ waleke witaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 14 Mo nate aĚ±iĚ± na miki haenaęž‰ kone titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la ikaęž‰ lolo polome pinaęž‰ hone ti na yokulueke laa aĚ±iĚ± telipeaęž‰peke.
\v 15 Pa ekipeke IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kutupiki pimanu make epeke hone make kuaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliweki homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make na tumbalimikie. Kutupa ikaęž‰ pi na yoko baalimikie.
\v 16 Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰maęž‰ make ikaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ tapake tonumaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ yankeke tonumaęž‰ make iki halaęž‰ moneayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mandanetaęž‰ otaęž‰ homomenaęž‰ limikie.
\v 17 Yaka biki melemeke handaa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ iki otaęž‰ kiaalimikie.
\v 18 Kutu pulu pelemepate ikaęž‰ amboke itiki homeke kone na alupilieke.
\v 19 Honkopu hao hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke dupiteleme hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone petelimikie leekeme.
\s1 Mo Diutuseleme hoeyaaso pulu piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰15-21, Maka 13ęž‰14-19)
\p 
\v 20 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da aęž‰ndaęž‰ ami titimaęž‰ dupasaęž‰eki handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki hoeyaalieke hone wilipikie.
\v 21 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diudia nane halo peleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo potemanu paęž‰taęž‰ pindipa penaęž‰e. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi mo daonimanu paęž‰taęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laenaęž‰e. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi mo da kenke teaęž‰naęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na penaęž‰e.
\v 22 Pa ekipeke do hau paeyaotaęž‰ hande Baibolomaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ Mo tanda miaęž‰peke natemanu laęž‰laęž‰ nate peneme yaaluekemaęž‰ pilieke.
\v 23 Koto nate ninaęž‰taęž‰ mo weki weleke haleme wandaęž‰weki o weki panake hopulu wia haleme wandaęž‰weki ikaęž‰ mulu peleme tandanaęž‰ paalaęž‰e. Otaęž‰ hoke paalaęž‰ piki haumanu make do kenkenaęž‰ ipilieke. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tanda peaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke.
\v 24 Mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ kepete dolo manumaęž‰ lu homao mandanetaęž‰ mandane kenke yu maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane dipula leke mea pua kutupa mo Diendaili wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Diutuseleme tumbuatia pua ikaęž‰ nate mulu epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lalimikie.
\s1 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰29-31, Maka 13ęž‰24-27)
\p 
\v 25 Oli ya nanetaęž‰ oli natenaęž‰ kaiseponaęž‰ hombulankaęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ pate haumanu pilieke. Do kenke nanetaęž‰ mandane da kenke paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ Eki pumanaęž‰pe laa hone mataaso hataęž‰ mo dawalanaęž‰ ho tiekemaęž‰ eĚ± lelieke make dawala teliaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make paalaęž‰maęž‰ homo halimikie.
\v 26 Wandaęž‰hali paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ eki hau opolo ipulaęž‰pe laa laęž‰maęž‰ lulu pitolo hataęž‰ homilimikie. Mo ya nane halaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hao haleme tupaęž‰ na hake pa nane wato baalieke.
\v 27 Koto tomonaęž‰ kone Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ oli koa paęž‰taęž‰ honkopu tieke make paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰eki ameĚ±leĚ± opolo ipilieke.
\v 28 Kutupiki haumanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ kini pea piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ambokemanu minaęž‰liapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke ikaęž‰ deto hao hamenaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰leke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Nose mandaęž‰ mu onkolumaęž‰ pi alaęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰32-35, Maka 13ęž‰28-31)
\p 
\v 29 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ dupiki onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ leekeme. Mo hande nose ti pitaęž‰ mandane timanu make hone wotu wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 30 Mo hande ikaęž‰ katakemanu kini pea tindiki liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hatuhama ti talaęž‰ nate ipuluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me hone u halememe.
\v 31 Kotaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ kone hande loaęž‰ alemanu ipulaęž‰eki kini pea handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ Ekitaęž‰ ipuluekemaęž‰ halaęž‰me hone wilimikie.
\p 
\v 32 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do haleme tapake paeyao aĚ±iĚ± na homeke halimi pitaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ loaęž‰ alemanu paeyao ambaęž‰ ipilieke.
\v 33 Oli ya do kenke yaapotaęž‰ paelo paęž‰laęž‰pate yaka pi lo haloeki manutaęž‰ na paelieke leekeme.
\s1 Wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke leekeeki
\p 
\v 34 Ikaęž‰ kone wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Ne tieke pamba make honkopu hake hoke ikali wopu na make do kenkenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ we pambaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki otaęž‰ na tumbaenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo Tekehalinaęž‰ Natemaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ wisakemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ koto kone
\v 35 tamilieke la loaęž‰me. Koto Natetaęž‰ do kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke.
\v 36 Koto ekinaęž‰ leke leke lo hataęž‰ hoto paeyao yeni pu hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupiki haumanu tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ kone honkopu hau epeke tupaęž‰ opolo pua mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hamenaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 37 Yesumaęž‰ koto nate manutaęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ pi walaataęž‰ welealo nane ninaęž‰taęž‰ mo Olipi Potenaęž‰ pua pitu timbaęž‰ latiki pu hayekeme.
\v 38 Kutupa wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opulueke alo timba tiao da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pimikime.
\c 22
\s1 Yesu luluekemaęž‰ hone ambaęž‰ pambao wimikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰1-5, Maka 14ęž‰1-2, Dioni 11ęž‰45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande Na Pombeiyaake Palaowa Nalaęž‰ Di ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke Natetaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yolo epeekeme.
\v 2 Mo yeni peao haemeke teke haliwekimaęž‰ make mo Lo Pi walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesu aęž‰mbao luekemaęž‰ yeke mandane potaęž‰manu wopu weimikime. Pa ekipeke. Ikitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ pimikime.
\s1 Diudasimaęž‰ Yesu linaęž‰ yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lomba wiekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰14-16, Maka 14ęž‰10-11)
\p 
\v 3 Isekatioti hali Diudasimaęž‰ mo hande 12 disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekepate kone Sadani hondaęž‰ pambeekeme.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ Diudasimaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke teke haliweki make mo tembolo da handeteke haemeke you haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ ekipa iki paęž‰taęž‰ mea halaęž‰ monealuaęž‰pe laa hotulu peekeme.
\v 5 Mo haliwekitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mani haluekemaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wimikime.
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ Diudasimaęž‰ mo ekinaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ na handolo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ Yesu linaęž‰ yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke potaęž‰manu kini pea weiyekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo Lombei Pupa Yapeeke ne noluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰17-25, Maka 14ęž‰12-21, Dioni 13ęž‰21-30)
\p 
\v 7 Mo hande Na Pombeiyaake Palaowa Nalaęž‰ natenaęž‰ mo Lombei Pupa Yapeeke yawenaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ ikiki sunu lulu pimiki nate opolo epeekeme.
\v 8 Yesumaęž‰ Pida pitaęž‰ Dioni yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi mea penaęž‰ lo tapaaso alotaęž‰ Pua nikaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke Natenaęž‰ ne nolo polome alenaęž‰ tikitiki yaalo pupaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 9 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hando paęž‰taęž‰ pua wamo peoponope lepekeme.
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opuaęž‰pe. Ipiliki mo daoni nane pulu hapenaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikali kanake homeke tia ipulutaęž‰ ipiliki mandaęž‰hande pilieke. Kutupa mo hali teli mea pua ipiki hondaęž‰ pambiliaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 11 Kutupa mo da teke hali paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lapaęž‰peke. Mo Disamaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka disaipolo haliweki IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± Lombei Pupa Yapeeke Natenaęž‰ ne nolo polomaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰pe laa lapaęž‰peke.
\v 12 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ manda nane ulaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰lao wiki da pandaęž‰ tieke walieke. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yaalipipikie leekeme.
\v 13 Mo hali yaapo puaataęž‰ hande Yesumaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaeyekeme. Kutupa mo hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke Natenaęž‰ ne wamo pipikime.
\s1 Teke Halinaęž‰ ne ikali telipeayekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰26-30, Maka 14ęž‰22-26, 1 Kotindi 11ęž‰23-25)
\p 
\v 14 Mo hande nate opolo epeeketaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰peke da pandaęž‰ mea mo ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± teipolonaęž‰ pitimikime.
\v 15 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± yaka hone tiekemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± tanda noluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ do Lombei Pupa Yapeeke Natenaęž‰ netaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± noluekemaęž‰ hone wotu paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 16 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ame doeki pea hoki nanetaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke do haunaęž‰ teke peneme yaenaęž‰ yeke paa na nolueke laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo kapo mea Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae alo hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone telipa nape laataęž‰
\v 18 IĚ±maęž‰ do waini ikalitaęž‰ ame do kini pea pua na neke hao mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao halaęž‰eki ipiliaęž‰ dinaęž‰ paa nolueke leekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo betedi mea Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae laa pindi pindi pea iki paęž‰taęž‰ halolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ yaka lokee laataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ ekie. Dupiki hautaęž‰ IĚ± hone niminaaso hataęž‰ peaęž‰tiki pu hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 20 Koto tupaęž‰ make ne naa paeyeketaęž‰ hande kapo mea mina hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do kapotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ panake pi laęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ yaka wemaęž‰ wiaasaęž‰me laataęž‰ Ikinaęž‰ holao paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate handaęž‰e. Mo hande IĚ± mininaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombolo paęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ kikitaęž‰ yakaeki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ do teipolonaęž‰ wia pilumaęž‰ handaęž‰e.
\v 22 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone homenaęž‰yeke paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ paalaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 23 Koto leekeeki opitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone lotaęž‰ pu alualu pitolo alotaęž‰ Niki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo epimaęž‰ dupiki hau pulu polome ekinaęž‰ alaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\s1 Tieke haasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ape ape lemekeeki
\p 
\v 24 Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tiekee hone winaęž‰taęž‰ epi kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa ape lemekeme.
\v 25 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Diendaili wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honkopu oto paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ lo halememe. Kutupa mo you haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰nie lo halememe.
\v 26 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate iki ameĚ±leĚ±taęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ tumiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ pao wetepenaęž‰ weki au lenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Kutupa mo you halitaęž‰ pao e pokaasaęž‰ hali au lenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke.
\v 27 Epitaęž‰ tiekepe. Mo ne noluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pilaęž‰ halipe o mo ne panaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ halipe. Otaęž‰ mo pilaęž‰ hali lataa. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ±taęž‰ ne panaęž‰ peaaso somemaęž‰ handolome.
\p 
\v 28 Ikitaęž‰ yaka kaęž‰ndaęž‰ pikieki tapu ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ hatia epememe.
\v 29 Kutupa yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handeteke hano maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone IĚ±maęž‰ make iki ameĚ±leĚ± homeke hau kone pulueke.
\v 30 Ikitaęž‰ yaka Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ yaka teipolonaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ne ikali nolumeke. Kutupa make ikitaęž‰ oli you halinaęž‰ sea manunaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo Isulainaęž‰ 12 tapake teli pilimikie leekeme.
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesu na handolome lolo piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰31-35, Maka 14ęž‰27-31, Dioni 13ęž‰36-38)
\p 
\v 31 Saimono Saimonoo. Opie. Sadanimaęž‰ iki la handenaęž‰ yeke waleke halaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo hande e poko halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ widi napeke yataęž‰pa ambuku winaęž‰ alaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pilimi hau manumaęž‰ kone hokeeki o epekeeki make teli pealieke.
\v 32 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ Saimono neke paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pealo ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone tulale ekitaęž‰ na lopenaęž‰yeke polome. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la epekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kametonu wele pu tiaapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Pidamaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. IĚ±taęž‰ neke yaapo mandakenaęž‰ dipula pulueke make homekaęž‰naęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ make tikitiki yao halome leekeme.
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pidao. IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ame timba kone kokaęž‰laęž‰ eĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na leke haenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto tepo yaka biki ambaęž‰la hoeyaaso hataęž‰ IĚ± na handolome lelipikie leekeme.
\s1 Pausa nu kepete dolo minaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 35 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande IĚ±maęž‰ iki tapawaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ pausa o nu o anke dake na kiki pa tapawaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ weimipe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ homekesiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ kone diaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 36 Kotaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kutu pimipate ametaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ pausa o nu wia haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ mea puaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi aęž‰ndaęž‰ kepete dolo diaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ sedi tapao mani mea kepete dolo maęž‰ndaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± hambaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 37 Pa ekipeke. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ alome. Mo hande Baibolomaęž‰ lao witolotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰eki yambeleme haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ apaęž‰tao yataęž‰pilimikie laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±naęž‰ otaęž‰ peneme yaenaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke. Mo hande IĚ±naęž‰ lao wiekeeki paeyaotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ otaęž‰ peneme yao ipulaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 38 Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Handaęž‰e. Kepete dolo yaapo do handaęž‰e lemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kototaęž‰ anaęž‰e leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Olipi Potenaęž‰ pitaęž‰ yeni piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰36-46, Maka 14ęž‰32-42)
\p 
\v 39 Yesutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ peaęž‰tiki pu hayeke tupaęž‰ mo da teke minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Olipi Potenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± peekeme.
\v 40 Koto alenaęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ La handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki mea lopaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeni wopu piaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 41 Koto laa Yesutaęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo toopi baasaęž‰ tupaęž‰ leke mopate pua tumiki yotuao pitaęž‰ yeni piekeme.
\v 42 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Anaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ipulaęž‰ kapo IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na epenaęž‰ lapeke. Kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ homeke pinaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 43 Oli ya nanemaęž‰ hayeke enisolo homeke opolo aęž‰pa Yesu honkopu haleekeme.
\v 44 Kutupa pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke pieketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ otaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ yeni piekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰li tieketaęž‰ wemaęž‰ handekeeki oni kenkenaęž‰ lopeekeme.
\p 
\v 45 Oni yeni pu pitieke alenaęž‰ tialiaotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki puki tandamaęž‰ kone sokaęž‰laęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ u paęž‰liake wimikieki pua handaęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 46 Kutupa mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke u paęž‰liake wilimipe. Tiao. La handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki mea lopaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeni wopu pu hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Yesu minimikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰47-56, Maka 14ęž‰43-50, Dioni 18ęž‰3-11)
\p 
\v 47 Koto kone Yesumaęž‰ koto pi alo haenaęž‰ hande disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Diudasimaęž‰ mo haliweki wopu hatuku Yesu hayeke alenaęž‰ opolo epemekeme. Diudasimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu nunu puluekemaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ leke peekeme.
\v 48 Kutu piekepate Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diudasio. Mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke linaęž‰ halaęž‰ monealuekemaęž‰taęž‰ nunu pitele ekimaęž‰ walelepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 49 Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo pulu piekeeki hando hao alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nikaęž‰ kepete dolomaęž‰ liomonope lemekeme.
\v 50 Koto kone mo hande disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo kepete dolomaęž‰ mo yeni peao hayeke teke halinaęž‰ e pokao hayeke halinaęž‰ popeke nane katake tunkulu poka lopaeyekeme.
\v 51 Kutu piekepate Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hautaęž‰ anaęž‰ma laataęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ katake watao paa epeaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 52 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo yeni peao hayeke teke haliweki make mo tembolo handeteke haemeke you haliweki make tondiki haliweki ipiki minuluekemaęž‰ epemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ kini pitolo hali patemaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ kepete make baĚ±iĚ± make miniki aęž‰pa pimipe.
\v 53 IĚ±taęž‰ nate wopu oni tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± haowaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minuluekemaęž‰ na taapememe. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate do timbataęž‰ nakaęž‰ natee. Mo hande timbaęž‰ leke ekinaęž‰ honkopumaęž‰ handeteke halo paęž‰laęž‰ natee leekeme.
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ IĚ± na handolome leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰57-58,69-75, Maka 14ęž‰53-54,66-72, Dioni 18ęž‰12-18,25-27)
\p 
\v 54 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu mina mo yeni peao hayeke teke halinaęž‰ da nane hatuku mea pemekeme. Kutupa Pidataęž‰ mopate leke hataęž‰ teliaęž‰ mea peekeme.
\v 55 Mo da hama tukikinaęž‰taęž‰ ti yankemekeme. Kutupa Pidataęž‰ mo tinaęž‰ pitu dupaemeke wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰taeyekeme.
\v 56 Koto pitinaęž‰taęž‰ mo e pokao hayeke wandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Pida mo tinaęž‰ pitiekeeki handaataęž‰ Pida handake witolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hali make Yesu yaapo hayaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 57 Koto leekepate Pidamaęž‰ Diaęž‰me laa honi mea baaso alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰o. Ipikitaęž‰ IĚ± na handolome leekeme.
\v 58 Pa hosiki siki hao hao pea hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Pida handaęž‰ u haotaęž‰. Neke make ipikaęž‰ tapake lataa leekeme. Koto leekepate Pidamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Someo IĚ± diaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 59 Kutupa nate leke homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ paeyeketaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ombu honkopu hao maĚ±leke litolo alotaęž‰ Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na aęž‰mbalaęž‰me. Do halitaęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± hayaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke ipiki make Kaęž‰lili hali yekeme.
\v 60 Koto leeke handaa Pidamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Someo. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto ale ekitaęž‰ IĚ± mataęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Kutupa koto tomonaęž‰ kone pi pa alo haenaęž‰ mo kokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ tiao eĚ± leekeme.
\v 61 Koto kone mo Tekehalimaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneao Pida handake wiekeme. Kutu pieke Pidamaęž‰taęž‰ hande Tekehalinaęž‰ pimanu dupa leaęž‰me laa niminaeyekeme. Mo kokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ eĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na leke haenaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la hoto tepo ya biki aęž‰mbao lo hoeyaasotaęž‰ IĚ± na handolome laa lelipikie leekeeki hone wiekeme.
\v 62 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pida hama opolu bao otaęž‰ puki teto tiekemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ kaęž‰paęž‰puki yoka eĚ± tieke leekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ kitata pea yombua baemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰67-68, Maka 14ęž‰65)
\p 
\v 63 Mo hande Yesu handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu kitata pea yombua baemekeme.
\v 64 Kutupa make mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ leke popeleke aęž‰mbao lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neke liaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki lakie lemekeme.
\v 65 Kutupa make Yesu yaalaęž‰meake pimanu wotu lemekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ mo KaĚ±leĚ±sete paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰59-66, Maka 14ęž‰55-64, Dioni 18ęž‰19-24)
\p 
\v 66 Da kelepeeketaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekinaęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete mombuluekemaęž‰ mo tondiki haliweki make yeni peao haemeke teke haliweki make Lo Pi walo haemeke haliweki paeyao mombololo hataęž‰ Yesu hatuku epemekeme.
\v 67 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki lakie. Neketaęž‰ hande Ketiso yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe lemekeme. Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kuaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± hone na tulalimikie.
\v 68 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ iki lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na yoka la kilimikie.
\v 69 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ame do kini pea puaataęž‰ hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ oli wele wotu piki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ pua pitu halieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 70 Mo hali paeyaomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime. Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ kone IĚ±e laataęž‰ koto alemetaa leekeme.
\p 
\v 71 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wekitisimanu weiyaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Nikaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ pi koto opumaęž‰taa lemekeme.
\c 23
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰1-2,11-14, Maka 15ęž‰1-5, Dioni 18ęž‰28-38)
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande tapake paeyao tiao Yesutaęž‰ mo Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku puaataęž‰
\v 2 ipiki maĚ±leke litolo alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do halitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hatuku pu hoeyaaso hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mo Sisanaęž‰ dakisi mani na halaęž‰paęž‰pe laataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone Ketiso laa Kini hali halome la alaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 3 Mo Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini hali halepe leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ Pailedinaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Koto aletaa leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Kutupa Pailedimaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke teke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make mo mombelemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do hali hoeyaapeke potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ witolome leekeme.
\v 5 Koto leekepate mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ honkopu hao hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ta hali ipikaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ pimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diudia da yu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hoke hone mea wiatia pominaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane kini pea aęž‰paataęž‰ ametaęž‰ do opolo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰e lemekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ Hetodi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 6 Pailedimaęž‰ koto lemekeeki opua mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 7 Koto laataęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Hetodimaęž‰ handeteke hayeke da yu nane yamaęž‰ aęž‰pa piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Hetodi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Ekipeke koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ Hetoditaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane aęž‰pa hayeke handa piekeme.
\v 8 Hetodimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu hando haotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homeekeme. Pa ekipeke. Hetodimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekimanu opu haotaęž‰ Yesu handulueke laa nate hokulunaęž‰ yu wia hatia peekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ na handeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ pinaęž‰e hone wia hayekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ Hetodimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ anemone lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu wotu lotaęž‰ piekepate Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaasaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na piekeme.
\v 10 Kutupa mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki make mo Lo Pi walo haemeke haliweki paeyao teke paęž‰taęž‰ leke aęž‰pa honkopu tieke haaso hataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ maĚ±leke limikime.
\v 11 Kutupa Hetodi make ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndeli minimiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± Yesu eto eto lao pa ale au laemekeme. Kutupa otaęž‰ epeke au leke dau hokulu mea yamao paa Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaa moneayekeme.
\v 12 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ Hetodi pitaęž‰ Pailedi yaapotaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkula alu pea haepekepate koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pipikime.
\s1 Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu linaęž‰ leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰15-26, Maka 15ęž‰6-15, Dioni 18ęž‰39â€”19ęž‰16)
\p 
\v 13 Pailedimaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wandaęž‰hali
\v 14 paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ do hali hatuku ipulutaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hatuku pu hoeyaasaęž‰me lemepate ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ teke weitolopate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo mandane pimanu yambaęž‰laęž‰me laa maĚ±leke limipate homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ yambaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki na handolome.
\v 15 Kutupa Hetodimaęž‰ make do halimaęž‰ pu hoeyaalaęž‰ hau homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na handolo hataęž‰ niki teke paęž‰taęž‰ pa do tapaalaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Ipiki lia homamonotaęž‰ hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ dopitamaęž‰ yombinaęž‰ laa pao penaęž‰ lolueke leekeme.
\v 17 []
\p 
\v 18 Mo mombelemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ eĚ± wi tieke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ homenaęž‰ liae. Mo Batabasitaęž‰ penaęž‰ tapawae lemekeme.
\v 19 Koto Batabasitaęž‰ dipula pitieke ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ kapomani ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ lia make mandane wandaęž‰hali lieke ekinaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 20 Pailedinaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu tapaaluekemaęž‰ yeke mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paa opolo peekeme.
\v 21 Kutu piekepate mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ paa pi tanda pu alualu pitolo alotaęž‰ Aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ homenaęž‰e. Aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ homenaęž‰e lemekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Pailedimaęž‰ paa hoto tepo peao alo alotaęž‰ Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ekipiki pi ataęž‰kaęž‰ pealaęž‰pe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ pa dopitamaęž‰ yombinaęž‰ laa paa tapalueke leekeme.
\v 23 Koto leekepate mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ poyaęž‰ tieke wotu alo hataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ endinaęž‰ laa lemeke eĚ± wi otaęž‰ yaeyekeme.
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu homenaęž‰e lemekeeki telia piekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ penaęž‰e lemeke halitaęž‰ penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Mo hande kapomani paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lia make mandane wandaęž‰hali lieke some kone penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki pinaęž‰yeke halaęž‰ moneayekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ ta mea endiao limikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰32-44, Maka 15ęž‰21-32, Dioni 19ęž‰17-27)
\p 
\v 26 Mo hande dolo miniki haemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu hatuku pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ Saitini da hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Saimono mandaęž‰hande pimikime. Ipikitaęž‰ mo kenke honiki nane hao oni daoni tieke aneke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo ipulu haenaęž‰ pimikime. Mo dolo miniki haemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Saimono yolaęž‰ meataęž‰ mo Yesunaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti mea tiawao Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane teliaęž‰ mea epenaęž‰ lemekeme.
\p 
\v 27 Wandaęž‰hali tiekemaęž‰ Yesu teliaęž‰ mea pemekeme. Koto wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ±taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰ sunutaęž‰ puki yoka hataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ eĚ± wopu lemekeme.
\v 28 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diutuseleme da wandaęž‰sunuo. IĚ±naęž‰ eĚ± na leketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone make ikaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ eĚ± lapaęž‰peke.
\v 29 Pa ekipeke mo wetepenaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupiki pi lelimikie. Mo kenohali wandaęž‰weki make hololuku hake piki wandaęž‰weki make andu liki na sinkipaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homelememe lelimikie.
\v 30 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ oli potemanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Niki manda lopaęž‰e laataęž‰ mo yu elimanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Niki mea aęž‰mbae lelimikie.
\v 31 Pa ekipeke dupiki haumanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ piliaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ti aęž‰ndaęž‰ tanisoĚ± kiki pinaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hapinaęž‰taęž‰ eki piliaęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Hali yaapo maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ hoke hau pipiki some yaapo make Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ lu endialuekemaęž‰ yeke hatuku pemekeme.
\v 33 Kutupa mo hande haliwekitaęž‰ mo yueli maęž‰ndaęž‰ wiekeeki ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Hali You Holiki lemeke alenaęž‰ aęž‰pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ lu endiaemekeme. Kutupa mo hande hoke hau pipiki some yaapo make homeke tupaęž‰ lu endiaemekeme. Maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ endiao maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ hoe nane kikinaęž‰ endiaemekeme.
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ piteleme hautaęž‰ iki hone na witolo pitelememaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pa paeyawapeke leekeme.
\p Kutupa mo dolo miniki haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ daumanu telipaaluekemaęž‰ kase tupaęž‰ telepo laemekeme.
\v 35 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handolo haenaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu kitaaso hataęž‰ dupa lemekeme. Mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰tiki piekepate ipikitaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ Ketiso hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone petelenaęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 36 Mo aęž‰ndeli dolo miniki haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesu makeaaso hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hoke waini ikali halolo hataęž‰
\v 37 alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini hali yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 38 Kutupa Yesunaęž‰ amboke mandataęž‰ dupa laemekeme. Dotaęž‰ Diu Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kinie Halie laa wape pea endiaemekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Mo hande pi yambeleeke some maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ tetopiki pimanu laęž‰ moneaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hande Ketiso diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Neke make diki make paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰taa leekeme.
\v 40 Koto leekepate mo hande pi yambeleeke some maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo some kake nalo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kutupiki pi na lapee laataęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paalaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pe. Neke make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ tanda kone mineleme.
\v 41 Dikitaęž‰ dikaęž‰ pupaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yenki anaęž‰naęž‰ minolopaęž‰pate ipiki homeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me laa
\v 42 mo halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesuo. Neke Kini hali ipilipi dinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± hone wiaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 43 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolome. Ame do natenaęž‰ kone IĚ± yaapo oli Paęž‰taęž‰daisi nane mandakenaęž‰ halupeke leekeme.
\s1 Yesu otaęž‰ homeekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰45-56, Maka 15ęž‰33-41, Dioni 19ęž‰28-30)
\p 
\v 44 Nate you tikeke nate ninaęž‰taęž‰ hande nate talaęž‰eki aęž‰mbaotaęž‰ timbaęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ da yu honiki paeyao tumbaotaęž‰ nate leke tepo ninaęž‰taęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± paa piekeme.
\v 45 Kutupa mo hande tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ endiaemeke dautaęž‰ tekilipualu pea yaapo wiekeme.
\p 
\v 46 Yesumaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ eĚ± wi alo alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Yaka temokotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ koto witolo handaęž‰e laataęž‰ otaęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 47 Mo hande ami haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ mo piekeeki hando haotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea miniliaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hali yekeme leekeme.
\p 
\v 48 Kutupa mo hande hau handuluekemaęž‰ mombelemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo piekeeki hando haotaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hakoko lutia pulu hataęž‰ pao da laęž‰kaęž‰la pemekeme.
\p 
\v 49 Yesu otaęž‰ handaa hone wimiki wandaęž‰hali make ipiki Kaęž‰lili nane kini pea teliaęž‰ mea epemeke wandaęž‰ sunumaęž‰ make mo pate leke hataęž‰ do hau paeyao handemekeme.
\s1 Yesu toko mea hoimikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰57-61, Maka 15ęž‰42-47, Dioni 19ęž‰38-42)
\p 
\v 50-51 Mo Diudia nane wieke daoni maęž‰ndaęž‰ Aęž‰taęž‰matia da hali Diosepe hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke tiki tiki hau pu hake hali hao hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki ipulaęž‰eki yu wia hao hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo KaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo hayekepate kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao pimanu make hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ make na piekeme.
\v 52 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Pailedinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ pua Yesunaęž‰ toko honke leekeme.
\v 53 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ toko hondaataęž‰ hakepiki daumaęž‰ tonkao mea tia puaataęž‰ toopi anekemaęž‰ peiyekeeki awa wimiki tikene damaęž‰ handeke ale paęž‰taęž‰ lapaęž‰ piekeme. Mo koto lapaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ make na hoimikieki yekeme.
\v 54 Mo natetaęž‰ Palaide yaalo mo hande Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate ambaęž‰ kini puluekemaęž‰ pitiekeme.
\p 
\v 55 Kutupa mo hande Kaęž‰lili kini pea Yesu teliaęž‰ mea epemeke wandaęž‰ sunumaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepe ameĚ±leĚ± pua mo Yesu lapaęž‰ piekeeki handemekeme.
\v 56 Kutupa paa laęž‰kaęž‰la da puaataęž‰ mo Yesunaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ holo pimiki totopo piki honkumanu amu pimikime. Kutupataęž‰ mo Lo Pimaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ hande hoto pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰ yaalo hoto pitimikime.
\c 24
\s1 Yesu paa tiaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 28ęž‰1-10, Maka 16ęž‰1-8, Dioni 20ęž‰1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Sande da panake kaęž‰laęž‰ polo nate epolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ sunumaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ lapaęž‰ nane mo hande tiki tiki yaemeke totopo wopu piki honkumanu miniki pemekeme.
\v 2 Mo alenaęž‰ opolo pemekepate mo hande potaęž‰ pokeeke toopi tieketaęž‰ pete pete yao wiekeeki handaataęž‰
\v 3 hondaęž‰ pambemekepate mo Tekehali Yesunaęž‰ loketaęž‰ na wiekeme.
\v 4 Mo wandaęž‰ sunutaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ hone ti yokolo haenaęž‰ koto kone hake pupapeke leke yalaęž‰ yalaęž‰ piki akaęž‰ yamaęž‰ mea hali yaapo aęž‰pa haepekeme.
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰ otaęž‰ paalaęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ sunutaęž‰ kenke nane you minaęž‰niao haenaęž‰ mo hali yaapomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke mo ambaęž‰ daęž‰ta halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ mo hali toko u halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ weitelemepe.
\v 6 Ipikitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ tiao paęž‰laęž‰me. Mo hande ipiki Kaęž‰lili hataęž‰ leaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ niminaasemepe.
\v 7 Dupa leaęž‰me. Mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo hoke hau pu haleme haliwekinaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ halaęž‰ moneaotaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ tame mea endiao liaataęž‰ kutupa hoto tepo peao natenaęž‰taęž‰ paa tialieke laa leaęž‰me lepekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi leekeeki niminaotaęž‰
\v 9 mo lapaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaataęž‰ hande handemekeeki paeyao mo 11 disaipolo haliweki make mandane disaipolo wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ lemekeme.
\v 10 Koto wandaęž‰ sunutaęž‰ Meti Maęž‰kadala make Dioaęž‰na make Diaęž‰mesinaęž‰ inkiki Meti make iki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke mandane wandaęž‰ sunumaęž‰ mo pieke haumanu mo aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ la halemekeme.
\v 11 Kutu lemekepate mo aposolo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ sunumaęž‰ lemeke pitaęž‰ apaęž‰ta apaęž‰ta piki pi alememe laa hone na wimikime.
\v 12 Kutu piekepate Pidamaęž‰taęž‰ mo lapaęž‰ handulueke alo pototo laa mo toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua pandaęž‰ puniao alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handeekepate mo tonkaeyeke akaęž‰ hake piki homeke handeekeme. Kutupa moeki handolo hataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la da peekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ mo Emeiase potaęž‰naęž‰ handepekeeki
\r (Maka 16ęž‰12-13)
\p 
\v 13 Koto homeke natenaęž‰ kone Yesu teliaęž‰ mea pomu haepeke hali yaapo maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ oni Emeiase leeke da siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ polueke alo pepekeme. Mo da sikitaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme daoni minaęž‰paęž‰lao 3 aowa tupaęž‰ opolo pulaęž‰ da yekeme.
\v 14 Kutupa mo hali yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ hande piekeeki manunaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ kone pi hotipipikime.
\v 15 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi laa hotitia pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ ipiliki teke paęž‰taęž‰ leke pua mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 16 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ handepepekepate Yesue laa na handaęž‰ wipikime.
\p 
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ mo hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ aleke pi hotiaęž‰lepepe leekeme. Mo hali yaapotaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ piki leke popeleke hataęž‰ poneke ale haepekeme.
\v 18 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo Keliopasi leeke halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo Diutuseleme daoni paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa haleme kimisu wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ±taęž‰ hande ambaneke numaneke piaęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ neke homeke na opelepe leekeme.
\v 19 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Eki hau manupe leekeme.
\p Kutupa mo hali yaapomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ piaęž‰ hau manunaęž‰ lopaęž‰me. Do halitaęž‰ potopede yaalo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ piaęž‰ hau manumaęž‰ make leeke pimanu make honkopu wele paęž‰laęž‰ halie lememe.
\v 20 Kutupa nikaęž‰ yeni peao haleme you haliwekimaęž‰ make handeteke haleme haliwekimaęž‰ make ipikitaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ tame mea endiao lu homaenaęž‰ yeke halaęž‰ moneaemekeme.
\v 21 Kutupa nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰hali lombo tapaalo paęž‰laęž‰ halie hone umaęž‰me. Koto haumanu paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ tepo peao natee.
\v 22 Kutupataęž‰ mandane nikaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰ sunumaęž‰ niki penkilipaememe. Ikitaęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso siki mo lapaęž‰naęž‰ pemekepate
\v 23 ipikaęž‰ loke na handaęž‰ wimikime. Mo wandaęž‰weki paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ UĚ± leme leme leke enisolo manumaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ tiao daęž‰ta halaęž‰me laa lemekeeki niki aęž‰pa la kimime.
\v 24 Koto lemeke nikaęž‰ mandane tapake pua mo lapaęž‰ pemekepate pa mo hande wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ lemeke tupaęž‰ kone pua handa alotaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ na handomaęž‰me lememe lepekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Meimei liake some yaapoo. Mo hande potopede halimaęž‰ leeke pimanu homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ hone aĚ±iĚ± na tulao pipikaęž‰taęž‰me.
\v 26 Mo Ketisomaęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la tanda meaataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ oli ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambolotaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pe laa leekeme.
\v 27 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo Baibolo paeyaonaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi lao ulaęž‰eki paeyao la haleekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Mosesinaęž‰ buka manunaęž‰ kini pea aęž‰pa mo potopede manumaęž‰ lao wieke ekimanu lo paeyaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Kutupataęž‰ iki paeyao mo polo pimiki da siki teke paęž‰taęž‰ yeketaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo pateleke peke nono piekeme.
\v 29 Pate mo hali yaapomaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Timbaęž‰ ambaęž‰ alaęž‰me. Diki ameĚ±leĚ± hae lepekeme. Koto lepeke Yesutaęž‰ mo hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± haluekemaęž‰ da peekeme.
\v 30 Kutupa mo hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± ne nolueke alo pitiniaotaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo betedi mea keiyae laataęž‰ pindipa mo hali yaapo haleekeme.
\v 31 Kutu pitolo pitinaęž‰ mo hali yaapomaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ hone lombolo Yesu yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa handaęž‰ wipiki dinaęž‰ kone Yesutaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ pitiki nono pea alu paeyekeme.
\v 32 Mo hali yaapomaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Mo hande potaęž‰naęž‰ hande Baibolonaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu laa kieketaęž‰ dikaęž‰ tukiki nanetaęž‰ ti uleke leke na teekea lepekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Kutupa koto kone mo hali yaapotaęž‰ tiao paa Diutuseleme nane pua mo 11 disaipolo haliweki make mandane disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mombaęž‰la pitaęž‰
\v 34 hande Tekehalitaęž‰ otaęž‰ daęž‰ta hataęž‰ Saimono paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki peneme yaalaęž‰me laa hotiolo pitimiki ale paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pepekeme.
\v 35 Kutupa ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande potaęž‰naęž‰ pieke ekimanu make Yesumaęž‰ betedi pindipinaęž‰ handaęž‰peke ekimanu make mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ la halepekeme.
\s1 Disaipolo haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ Yesu handemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 28ęž‰16-20, Maka 16ęž‰14-18, Dioni 20ęž‰19-23, Aposolo 1ęž‰6-8)
\p 
\v 36 Mo hande hali yaapomaęž‰ moeki alo haenaęž‰taęž‰ koto kone mo Tekehali ipikaęž‰ kone iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ peneme yao hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Puki lopaasaęž‰eki iki paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 37 Mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao pututu tiekemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ temoko handolomaęž‰me hone wimikime.
\v 38 Pate Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke paalaęž‰maęž‰ homelemepe. Ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hone yaapo yaapo ekipeke witelemepe.
\v 39 Yaka kiki anke handolotaęž‰ otaęž‰ IĚ± yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lapaęž‰peke. IĚ± wataemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ IĚ±e hone wilimikie. Watae. IĚ±taęž‰ temoko yolutaęž‰ loke make holiki make na halo puaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ holiki hao loke haloeki handaęž‰pe laa leekeme.
\v 40 Yesumaęž‰ doeki laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki anke waleekeme.
\v 41 Kutu piekepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ tumbitolo hataęž‰ hone ti yokolo hataęž‰ hone na tulaemeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Napeke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ wia pilimipe leekeme.
\v 42 Koto leeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰peli teekeeki siki halemeke handaa
\v 43 mea ikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ neekeme.
\p 
\v 44 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hau manutaęž‰ hande IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± haeme dinaęž‰ la kuaęž‰ ekimanue. Mo hande Mosesinaęž‰ Lo Pi wape pea ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make hande Emeli bukanaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make IĚ±naęž‰ lao ulaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 45 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ honemanu lumbao mo Baibolomaęž‰ leeke ekimanu opinaęž‰ laa
\v 46 iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dupa wape pea ulaęž‰me. Hande Ketisotaęž‰ tanda ambaęž‰la otaęž‰ mea homaataęž‰ hoto tepo peaasotaęž‰ otaęž‰ paa tialieke laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make
\v 47 ipikaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ mo hoke haunaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki make pa paeyaasaęž‰eki make mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ kini pea pua mo kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ walotia puaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 48 Ikitaęž‰ do hau manunaęž‰ wekitisie.
\v 49 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ale iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapalueke. Pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do daoni tieke paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande wele paęž‰laęž‰eki tieke oli ya nane iki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ yu wia pitaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesu oli ya nane mea peekeeki
\r (Maka 16ęž‰19-20, Aposolo 1ęž‰9-11)
\p 
\v 50 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali hatuku mo daoni tieke minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Bedani puaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki minaęž‰liao mo wandaęž‰hali epeaeyekeme.
\v 51 Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao oli hepeni nane hatuku peekeme.
\v 52 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki miniliaaso hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ tumbitolo hataęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da nane laęž‰kaęž‰la paa pemekeme.
\v 53 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae alo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ nate lekemanu paeyaemekeme. 
